  <head>
    <title>设计前期场地与建筑设计（知识）  第三章  建筑设计原理</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <outline text="设计前期场地与建筑设计（知识）" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%89%8D%E6%9C%9F%E5%9C%BA%E5%9C%B0%E4%B8%8E%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%EF%BC%88%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86%EF%BC%89%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="第三章    建筑设计原理" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%89%E7%AB%A0%20%20%20%20%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%8E%9F%E7%90%86%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="考试大纲对本专题的考核要求是：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%80%83%E8%AF%95%E5%A4%A7%E7%BA%B2%E5%AF%B9%E6%9C%AC%E4%B8%93%E9%A2%98%E7%9A%84%E8%80%83%E6%A0%B8%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E6%98%AF%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="系统掌握建筑设计的各项基础理论、公共建筑和居住建筑设计原理；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E6%8E%8C%E6%8F%A1%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E7%9A%84%E5%90%84%E9%A1%B9%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA%E3%80%81%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%92%8C%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%8E%9F%E7%90%86%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="掌握建筑类别等级的划分及各阶段的设计深度要求（详见本书第七章第一节）；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%8E%8C%E6%8F%A1%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%B1%BB%E5%88%AB%E7%AD%89%E7%BA%A7%E7%9A%84%E5%88%92%E5%88%86%E5%8F%8A%E5%90%84%E9%98%B6%E6%AE%B5%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E6%B7%B1%E5%BA%A6%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%EF%BC%88%E8%AF%A6%E8%A7%81%E6%9C%AC%E4%B9%A6%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%83%E7%AB%A0%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E8%8A%82%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="掌握技术经济综合评价标准（详见本套教材第五分册第二十五章建筑经济）；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%8E%8C%E6%8F%A1%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E7%BB%BC%E5%90%88%E8%AF%84%E4%BB%B7%E6%A0%87%E5%87%86%EF%BC%88%E8%AF%A6%E8%A7%81%E6%9C%AC%E5%A5%97%E6%95%99%E6%9D%90%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%94%E5%88%86%E5%86%8C%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E5%8D%81%E4%BA%94%E7%AB%A0%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="理解建筑与室内外环境、建筑与技术、建筑与人的行为方式的关系”。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%90%86%E8%A7%A3%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E4%B8%8E%E5%AE%A4%E5%86%85%E5%A4%96%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E3%80%81%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E4%B8%8E%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E3%80%81%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E4%B8%8E%E4%BA%BA%E7%9A%84%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%BA%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%E7%9A%84%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%E2%80%9D%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="第一节    公共建筑设计原理" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E8%8A%82%20%20%20%20%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%8E%9F%E7%90%86%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="建筑师要处理好公共建筑的总体环境布局、功能关系与空间组合、造型艺术、技术经济等问题。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%88%E8%A6%81%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86%E5%A5%BD%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%9A%84%E6%80%BB%E4%BD%93%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E3%80%81%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%E4%B8%8E%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E7%BB%84%E5%90%88%E3%80%81%E9%80%A0%E5%9E%8B%E8%89%BA%E6%9C%AF%E3%80%81%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E7%AD%89%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="一、公共建筑的总体环境布局" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%80%E3%80%81%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%9A%84%E6%80%BB%E4%BD%93%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="1.总体环境布局的基本组成" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1.%E6%80%BB%E4%BD%93%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E7%BB%84%E6%88%90%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="创造室外空间环境时，主要考虑公共建筑的内在因素和外在因素。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%88%9B%E9%80%A0%E5%AE%A4%E5%A4%96%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E6%97%B6%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E8%80%83%E8%99%91%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%9A%84%E5%86%85%E5%9C%A8%E5%9B%A0%E7%B4%A0%E5%92%8C%E5%A4%96%E5%9C%A8%E5%9B%A0%E7%B4%A0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="公共建筑自身的功能、经济及美观属于内在因素，而城市规划、周围环境、地段状况等属于外在因素。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%87%AA%E8%BA%AB%E7%9A%84%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E3%80%81%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E5%8F%8A%E7%BE%8E%E8%A7%82%E5%B1%9E%E4%BA%8E%E5%86%85%E5%9C%A8%E5%9B%A0%E7%B4%A0%EF%BC%8C%E8%80%8C%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E3%80%81%E5%91%A8%E5%9B%B4%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E3%80%81%E5%9C%B0%E6%AE%B5%E7%8A%B6%E5%86%B5%E7%AD%89%E5%B1%9E%E4%BA%8E%E5%A4%96%E5%9C%A8%E5%9B%A0%E7%B4%A0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="室外空间环境包括下列几个基本组成部分：建筑群体、广场道路、绿化设施、雕塑壁画、建筑小品、灯光造型的艺术效果等。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%AE%A4%E5%A4%96%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E4%B8%8B%E5%88%97%E5%87%A0%E4%B8%AA%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E7%BB%84%E6%88%90%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%EF%BC%9A%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%BE%A4%E4%BD%93%E3%80%81%E5%B9%BF%E5%9C%BA%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E3%80%81%E7%BB%BF%E5%8C%96%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E3%80%81%E9%9B%95%E5%A1%91%E5%A3%81%E7%94%BB%E3%80%81%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B0%8F%E5%93%81%E3%80%81%E7%81%AF%E5%85%89%E9%80%A0%E5%9E%8B%E7%9A%84%E8%89%BA%E6%9C%AF%E6%95%88%E6%9E%9C%E7%AD%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="此外，建筑师还应处理好室外环境空间与建筑、场所、绿地的关系。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%AD%A4%E5%A4%96%EF%BC%8C%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%88%E8%BF%98%E5%BA%94%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86%E5%A5%BD%E5%AE%A4%E5%A4%96%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E4%B8%8E%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E3%80%81%E5%9C%BA%E6%89%80%E3%80%81%E7%BB%BF%E5%9C%B0%E7%9A%84%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="2.总体环境布局的空间与环境" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2.%E6%80%BB%E4%BD%93%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E7%9A%84%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E4%B8%8E%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="勒·柯布西耶认为“……对空间的占有是存在之第一表征；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%8B%92%C2%B7%E6%9F%AF%E5%B8%83%E8%A5%BF%E8%80%B6%E8%AE%A4%E4%B8%BA%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6%E2%80%A6%E5%AF%B9%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%A0%E6%9C%89%E6%98%AF%E5%AD%98%E5%9C%A8%E4%B9%8B%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E8%A1%A8%E5%BE%81%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="然而任何空间都存在于环境之中，故提高人造环境的物理素质及其艺术性，就必然成为提高现代生活质量的重要构成因素”。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%84%B6%E8%80%8C%E4%BB%BB%E4%BD%95%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E9%83%BD%E5%AD%98%E5%9C%A8%E4%BA%8E%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E4%B9%8B%E4%B8%AD%EF%BC%8C%E6%95%85%E6%8F%90%E9%AB%98%E4%BA%BA%E9%80%A0%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E7%9A%84%E7%89%A9%E7%90%86%E7%B4%A0%E8%B4%A8%E5%8F%8A%E5%85%B6%E8%89%BA%E6%9C%AF%E6%80%A7%EF%BC%8C%E5%B0%B1%E5%BF%85%E7%84%B6%E6%88%90%E4%B8%BA%E6%8F%90%E9%AB%98%E7%8E%B0%E4%BB%A3%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E8%B4%A8%E9%87%8F%E7%9A%84%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81%E6%9E%84%E6%88%90%E5%9B%A0%E7%B4%A0%E2%80%9D%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="在设计公共建筑时，其空间组合不能脱离总体环境孤立地进行，而应把它放在特定的环境之中，即考虑自然环境与人工环境的结合。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9C%A8%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E6%97%B6%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%B6%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E7%BB%84%E5%90%88%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E8%84%B1%E7%A6%BB%E6%80%BB%E4%BD%93%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%AD%A4%E7%AB%8B%E5%9C%B0%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%EF%BC%8C%E8%80%8C%E5%BA%94%E6%8A%8A%E5%AE%83%E6%94%BE%E5%9C%A8%E7%89%B9%E5%AE%9A%E7%9A%84%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E4%B9%8B%E4%B8%AD%EF%BC%8C%E5%8D%B3%E8%80%83%E8%99%91%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E4%B8%8E%E4%BA%BA%E5%B7%A5%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%93%E5%90%88%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="3.群体建筑环境的空间组合" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E3.%E7%BE%A4%E4%BD%93%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E7%9A%84%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E7%BB%84%E5%90%88%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="公共建筑群体空间组合，一般包含两个方面：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%BE%A4%E4%BD%93%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E7%BB%84%E5%90%88%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%80%E8%88%AC%E5%8C%85%E5%90%AB%E4%B8%A4%E4%B8%AA%E6%96%B9%E9%9D%A2%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="一是在特定的条件下，需要采用比较分散的布局，而产生群体空间组合；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%80%E6%98%AF%E5%9C%A8%E7%89%B9%E5%AE%9A%E7%9A%84%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%E4%B8%8B%EF%BC%8C%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E9%87%87%E7%94%A8%E6%AF%94%E8%BE%83%E5%88%86%E6%95%A3%E7%9A%84%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%EF%BC%8C%E8%80%8C%E4%BA%A7%E7%94%9F%E7%BE%A4%E4%BD%93%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E7%BB%84%E5%90%88%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="二是以公共建筑群组成各种形式的组团或中心，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BA%8C%E6%98%AF%E4%BB%A5%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%BE%A4%E7%BB%84%E6%88%90%E5%90%84%E7%A7%8D%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%84%E5%9B%A2%E6%88%96%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
          <outline text="如市政中心（加拿大多伦多市政厅、巴西的巴西利亚三权广场）、" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%A6%82%E5%B8%82%E6%94%BF%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%EF%BC%88%E5%8A%A0%E6%8B%BF%E5%A4%A7%E5%A4%9A%E4%BC%A6%E5%A4%9A%E5%B8%82%E6%94%BF%E5%8E%85%E3%80%81%E5%B7%B4%E8%A5%BF%E7%9A%84%E5%B7%B4%E8%A5%BF%E5%88%A9%E4%BA%9A%E4%B8%89%E6%9D%83%E5%B9%BF%E5%9C%BA%EF%BC%89%E3%80%81%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
          <outline text="商业中心（瑞典魏林比商业中心、英国伦敦哈罗城市中心）、" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%95%86%E4%B8%9A%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%EF%BC%88%E7%91%9E%E5%85%B8%E9%AD%8F%E6%9E%97%E6%AF%94%E5%95%86%E4%B8%9A%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%E3%80%81%E8%8B%B1%E5%9B%BD%E4%BC%A6%E6%95%A6%E5%93%88%E7%BD%97%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%EF%BC%89%E3%80%81%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
          <outline text="展览中心（美国西雅图世界博览会）及娱乐中心等。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%B1%95%E8%A7%88%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%EF%BC%88%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E8%A5%BF%E9%9B%85%E5%9B%BE%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E5%8D%9A%E8%A7%88%E4%BC%9A%EF%BC%89%E5%8F%8A%E5%A8%B1%E4%B9%90%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%E7%AD%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        </outline>
      </outline>
    </outline>
    <outline text="二、公共建筑的功能关系与空间组合" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BA%8C%E3%80%81%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%9A%84%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%E4%B8%8E%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E7%BB%84%E5%90%88%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="公共建筑是人们进行社会活动的场所，在公共建筑的功能问题中，功能分区、人流疏散、空间组成以及建筑与室外环境的联系等，是核心问题。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E6%98%AF%E4%BA%BA%E4%BB%AC%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E6%B4%BB%E5%8A%A8%E7%9A%84%E5%9C%BA%E6%89%80%EF%BC%8C%E5%9C%A8%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%9A%84%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E4%B8%AD%EF%BC%8C%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E5%88%86%E5%8C%BA%E3%80%81%E4%BA%BA%E6%B5%81%E7%96%8F%E6%95%A3%E3%80%81%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E7%BB%84%E6%88%90%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%8A%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E4%B8%8E%E5%AE%A4%E5%A4%96%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E7%9A%84%E8%81%94%E7%B3%BB%E7%AD%89%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%AF%E6%A0%B8%E5%BF%83%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="其中最突出的则是建筑空间的使用性质和人流活动的问题。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%85%B6%E4%B8%AD%E6%9C%80%E7%AA%81%E5%87%BA%E7%9A%84%E5%88%99%E6%98%AF%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E6%80%A7%E8%B4%A8%E5%92%8C%E4%BA%BA%E6%B5%81%E6%B4%BB%E5%8A%A8%E7%9A%84%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（一）公共建筑的空间构成" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%80%EF%BC%89%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%9A%84%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E6%9E%84%E6%88%90%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="各种公共建筑的使用性质和类型尽管不同，但都可以分成主要使用部分、次要使用部分（或称辅助部分）和交通联系部分。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%90%84%E7%A7%8D%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E6%80%A7%E8%B4%A8%E5%92%8C%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B%E5%B0%BD%E7%AE%A1%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%86%E9%83%BD%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E5%88%86%E6%88%90%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E3%80%81%E6%AC%A1%E8%A6%81%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%EF%BC%88%E6%88%96%E7%A7%B0%E8%BE%85%E5%8A%A9%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%EF%BC%89%E5%92%8C%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E8%81%94%E7%B3%BB%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="设计中应首先抓住这三大部分的关系进行排列组合，逐一解决各种矛盾问题，以求得功能关系的合理与完善。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E4%B8%AD%E5%BA%94%E9%A6%96%E5%85%88%E6%8A%93%E4%BD%8F%E8%BF%99%E4%B8%89%E5%A4%A7%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E7%9A%84%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E6%8E%92%E5%88%97%E7%BB%84%E5%90%88%EF%BC%8C%E9%80%90%E4%B8%80%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E5%90%84%E7%A7%8D%E7%9F%9B%E7%9B%BE%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A5%E6%B1%82%E5%BE%97%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%E7%9A%84%E5%90%88%E7%90%86%E4%B8%8E%E5%AE%8C%E5%96%84%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="在这三部分的构成关系中，交通联系空间的配置往往起到关键作用。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9C%A8%E8%BF%99%E4%B8%89%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E7%9A%84%E6%9E%84%E6%88%90%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%E4%B8%AD%EF%BC%8C%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E8%81%94%E7%B3%BB%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E7%9A%84%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E5%BE%80%E5%BE%80%E8%B5%B7%E5%88%B0%E5%85%B3%E9%94%AE%E4%BD%9C%E7%94%A8%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="交通联系部分一般可分为：水平交通、垂直交通和枢纽交通三种基本空间形式。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E8%81%94%E7%B3%BB%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E4%B8%80%E8%88%AC%E5%8F%AF%E5%88%86%E4%B8%BA%EF%BC%9A%E6%B0%B4%E5%B9%B3%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E3%80%81%E5%9E%82%E7%9B%B4%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E5%92%8C%E6%9E%A2%E7%BA%BD%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E4%B8%89%E7%A7%8D%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="1.水平交通" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1.%E6%B0%B4%E5%B9%B3%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="常采用过道、过厅、通廊等空间形式。设计时应直截了当，忌曲折多变。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%B8%B8%E9%87%87%E7%94%A8%E8%BF%87%E9%81%93%E3%80%81%E8%BF%87%E5%8E%85%E3%80%81%E9%80%9A%E5%BB%8A%E7%AD%89%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E3%80%82%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E6%97%B6%E5%BA%94%E7%9B%B4%E6%88%AA%E4%BA%86%E5%BD%93%EF%BC%8C%E5%BF%8C%E6%9B%B2%E6%8A%98%E5%A4%9A%E5%8F%98%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="与各部分空间均应有密切联系，具备良好的采光与通风。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%8E%E5%90%84%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E5%9D%87%E5%BA%94%E6%9C%89%E5%AF%86%E5%88%87%E8%81%94%E7%B3%BB%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%B7%E5%A4%87%E8%89%AF%E5%A5%BD%E7%9A%84%E9%87%87%E5%85%89%E4%B8%8E%E9%80%9A%E9%A3%8E%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="2.垂直交通" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2.%E5%9E%82%E7%9B%B4%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="常采用楼梯（直跑、双跑或三跑楼梯）、电梯、自动扶梯，以及坡道等形式。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%B8%B8%E9%87%87%E7%94%A8%E6%A5%BC%E6%A2%AF%EF%BC%88%E7%9B%B4%E8%B7%91%E3%80%81%E5%8F%8C%E8%B7%91%E6%88%96%E4%B8%89%E8%B7%91%E6%A5%BC%E6%A2%AF%EF%BC%89%E3%80%81%E7%94%B5%E6%A2%AF%E3%80%81%E8%87%AA%E5%8A%A8%E6%89%B6%E6%A2%AF%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%8A%E5%9D%A1%E9%81%93%E7%AD%89%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="公共建筑中楼梯的位置与数量应依据功能需要和消防要求而定。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E4%B8%AD%E6%A5%BC%E6%A2%AF%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%8D%E7%BD%AE%E4%B8%8E%E6%95%B0%E9%87%8F%E5%BA%94%E4%BE%9D%E6%8D%AE%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E5%92%8C%E6%B6%88%E9%98%B2%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E8%80%8C%E5%AE%9A%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="应靠近交通枢纽，布置均匀、有主次且应与使用者的人流量相适应。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%BA%94%E9%9D%A0%E8%BF%91%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E6%9E%A2%E7%BA%BD%EF%BC%8C%E5%B8%83%E7%BD%AE%E5%9D%87%E5%8C%80%E3%80%81%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%BB%E6%AC%A1%E4%B8%94%E5%BA%94%E4%B8%8E%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E8%80%85%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%BA%E6%B5%81%E9%87%8F%E7%9B%B8%E9%80%82%E5%BA%94%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="3.枢纽交通" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E3.%E6%9E%A2%E7%BA%BD%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="考虑到人流的集散、方向的转换、空间的过渡，以及与通道、楼梯等空间的衔接等，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%80%83%E8%99%91%E5%88%B0%E4%BA%BA%E6%B5%81%E7%9A%84%E9%9B%86%E6%95%A3%E3%80%81%E6%96%B9%E5%90%91%E7%9A%84%E8%BD%AC%E6%8D%A2%E3%80%81%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E7%9A%84%E8%BF%87%E6%B8%A1%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%8A%E4%B8%8E%E9%80%9A%E9%81%93%E3%80%81%E6%A5%BC%E6%A2%AF%E7%AD%89%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E7%9A%84%E8%A1%94%E6%8E%A5%E7%AD%89%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="需要设置门厅、过厅等空间形式，起到交通枢纽与空间过渡的作用。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE%E9%97%A8%E5%8E%85%E3%80%81%E8%BF%87%E5%8E%85%E7%AD%89%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%EF%BC%8C%E8%B5%B7%E5%88%B0%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E6%9E%A2%E7%BA%BD%E4%B8%8E%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E8%BF%87%E6%B8%A1%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%9C%E7%94%A8%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="使用方便、空间得体、结构合理、装修适当、经济有效。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E6%96%B9%E4%BE%BF%E3%80%81%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E5%BE%97%E4%BD%93%E3%80%81%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E5%90%88%E7%90%86%E3%80%81%E8%A3%85%E4%BF%AE%E9%80%82%E5%BD%93%E3%80%81%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E6%9C%89%E6%95%88%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="应兼顾使用功能和空间意境的创造。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%BA%94%E5%85%BC%E9%A1%BE%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E5%92%8C%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E6%84%8F%E5%A2%83%E7%9A%84%E5%88%9B%E9%80%A0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="4.空间组合" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E4.%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E7%BB%84%E5%90%88%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（1）分隔性空间组合" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E5%88%86%E9%9A%94%E6%80%A7%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E7%BB%84%E5%90%88%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="分隔性空间组合的特点是以交通空间为联系手段，组合各类房间。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%88%86%E9%9A%94%E6%80%A7%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E7%BB%84%E5%90%88%E7%9A%84%E7%89%B9%E7%82%B9%E6%98%AF%E4%BB%A5%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E4%B8%BA%E8%81%94%E7%B3%BB%E6%89%8B%E6%AE%B5%EF%BC%8C%E7%BB%84%E5%90%88%E5%90%84%E7%B1%BB%E6%88%BF%E9%97%B4%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="常称之为“走道式”建筑布局，广泛运用于办公、学校、医院、宿舍等建筑。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%B8%B8%E7%A7%B0%E4%B9%8B%E4%B8%BA%E2%80%9C%E8%B5%B0%E9%81%93%E5%BC%8F%E2%80%9D%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%EF%BC%8C%E5%B9%BF%E6%B3%9B%E8%BF%90%E7%94%A8%E4%BA%8E%E5%8A%9E%E5%85%AC%E3%80%81%E5%AD%A6%E6%A0%A1%E3%80%81%E5%8C%BB%E9%99%A2%E3%80%81%E5%AE%BF%E8%88%8D%E7%AD%89%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="有内廊式（走道在中间，联系两侧房间）和外廊式（走道位于一侧，联系单面房间）两种布置方式。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%9C%89%E5%86%85%E5%BB%8A%E5%BC%8F%EF%BC%88%E8%B5%B0%E9%81%93%E5%9C%A8%E4%B8%AD%E9%97%B4%EF%BC%8C%E8%81%94%E7%B3%BB%E4%B8%A4%E4%BE%A7%E6%88%BF%E9%97%B4%EF%BC%89%E5%92%8C%E5%A4%96%E5%BB%8A%E5%BC%8F%EF%BC%88%E8%B5%B0%E9%81%93%E4%BD%8D%E4%BA%8E%E4%B8%80%E4%BE%A7%EF%BC%8C%E8%81%94%E7%B3%BB%E5%8D%95%E9%9D%A2%E6%88%BF%E9%97%B4%EF%BC%89%E4%B8%A4%E7%A7%8D%E5%B8%83%E7%BD%AE%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（2）连续性空间组合" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E8%BF%9E%E7%BB%AD%E6%80%A7%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E7%BB%84%E5%90%88%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="展览类型的公共建筑，为满足参观路线的要求，在空间组合上要求有一定的连续性。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%B1%95%E8%A7%88%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B%E7%9A%84%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%BA%E6%BB%A1%E8%B6%B3%E5%8F%82%E8%A7%82%E8%B7%AF%E7%BA%BF%E7%9A%84%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%EF%BC%8C%E5%9C%A8%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E7%BB%84%E5%90%88%E4%B8%8A%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%9A%E7%9A%84%E8%BF%9E%E7%BB%AD%E6%80%A7%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="基本上可分为5种形式：串联式、放射式、串联兼通道式、串联兼放射式、综合性大厅式。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E4%B8%8A%E5%8F%AF%E5%88%86%E4%B8%BA5%E7%A7%8D%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%B2%E8%81%94%E5%BC%8F%E3%80%81%E6%94%BE%E5%B0%84%E5%BC%8F%E3%80%81%E4%B8%B2%E8%81%94%E5%85%BC%E9%80%9A%E9%81%93%E5%BC%8F%E3%80%81%E4%B8%B2%E8%81%94%E5%85%BC%E6%94%BE%E5%B0%84%E5%BC%8F%E3%80%81%E7%BB%BC%E5%90%88%E6%80%A7%E5%A4%A7%E5%8E%85%E5%BC%8F%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（3）观演性空间组合" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E8%A7%82%E6%BC%94%E6%80%A7%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E7%BB%84%E5%90%88%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="观演类型的公共建筑（体育馆、影剧院、音乐厅、歌舞厅、娱乐城），一般有大型的空间作为组合的中心，围绕大型空间布置服务性空间。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%A7%82%E6%BC%94%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B%E7%9A%84%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%EF%BC%88%E4%BD%93%E8%82%B2%E9%A6%86%E3%80%81%E5%BD%B1%E5%89%A7%E9%99%A2%E3%80%81%E9%9F%B3%E4%B9%90%E5%8E%85%E3%80%81%E6%AD%8C%E8%88%9E%E5%8E%85%E3%80%81%E5%A8%B1%E4%B9%90%E5%9F%8E%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%80%E8%88%AC%E6%9C%89%E5%A4%A7%E5%9E%8B%E7%9A%84%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%BA%E7%BB%84%E5%90%88%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%EF%BC%8C%E5%9B%B4%E7%BB%95%E5%A4%A7%E5%9E%8B%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E5%B8%83%E7%BD%AE%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E6%80%A7%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="服务性空间与大型空间应联系密切，并构成空间整体。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E6%80%A7%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E4%B8%8E%E5%A4%A7%E5%9E%8B%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E5%BA%94%E8%81%94%E7%B3%BB%E5%AF%86%E5%88%87%EF%BC%8C%E5%B9%B6%E6%9E%84%E6%88%90%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E6%95%B4%E4%BD%93%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（4）高层性空间组合" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%884%EF%BC%89%E9%AB%98%E5%B1%82%E6%80%A7%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E7%BB%84%E5%90%88%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="高层公共建筑（酒店、办公楼、多功能大厦）的空间组合反映在交通组织上，是以垂直交通系统为主，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%AB%98%E5%B1%82%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%EF%BC%88%E9%85%92%E5%BA%97%E3%80%81%E5%8A%9E%E5%85%AC%E6%A5%BC%E3%80%81%E5%A4%9A%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E5%A4%A7%E5%8E%A6%EF%BC%89%E7%9A%84%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E7%BB%84%E5%90%88%E5%8F%8D%E6%98%A0%E5%9C%A8%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E7%BB%84%E7%BB%87%E4%B8%8A%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%AF%E4%BB%A5%E5%9E%82%E7%9B%B4%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%BB%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="有板式和塔式两种（而低层公共建筑的空间组合，常以水平交通为主）。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%9C%89%E6%9D%BF%E5%BC%8F%E5%92%8C%E5%A1%94%E5%BC%8F%E4%B8%A4%E7%A7%8D%EF%BC%88%E8%80%8C%E4%BD%8E%E5%B1%82%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%9A%84%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E7%BB%84%E5%90%88%EF%BC%8C%E5%B8%B8%E4%BB%A5%E6%B0%B4%E5%B9%B3%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%BB%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（5）综合性空间组合" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%885%EF%BC%89%E7%BB%BC%E5%90%88%E6%80%A7%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E7%BB%84%E5%90%88%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="一些功能要求复杂的公共建筑，常采用综合形式的空间组合，如文化宫、俱乐部、大型会议和办公场所；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%80%E4%BA%9B%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E5%A4%8D%E6%9D%82%E7%9A%84%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%EF%BC%8C%E5%B8%B8%E9%87%87%E7%94%A8%E7%BB%BC%E5%90%88%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E7%9A%84%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E7%BB%84%E5%90%88%EF%BC%8C%E5%A6%82%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96%E5%AE%AB%E3%80%81%E4%BF%B1%E4%B9%90%E9%83%A8%E3%80%81%E5%A4%A7%E5%9E%8B%E4%BC%9A%E8%AE%AE%E5%92%8C%E5%8A%9E%E5%85%AC%E5%9C%BA%E6%89%80%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="这类公共建筑的空间与体形是相辅相成的，应灵活运用各种空间组合手段。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%BF%99%E7%B1%BB%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%9A%84%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E4%B8%8E%E4%BD%93%E5%BD%A2%E6%98%AF%E7%9B%B8%E8%BE%85%E7%9B%B8%E6%88%90%E7%9A%84%EF%BC%8C%E5%BA%94%E7%81%B5%E6%B4%BB%E8%BF%90%E7%94%A8%E5%90%84%E7%A7%8D%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E7%BB%84%E5%90%88%E6%89%8B%E6%AE%B5%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（二）公共建筑的功能分区" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%BA%8C%EF%BC%89%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%9A%84%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E5%88%86%E5%8C%BA%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="功能分区的概念是，将空间按不同功能要求进行分类，并根据它们之间联系的密切程度加以组合、划分。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E5%88%86%E5%8C%BA%E7%9A%84%E6%A6%82%E5%BF%B5%E6%98%AF%EF%BC%8C%E5%B0%86%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E6%8C%89%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB%EF%BC%8C%E5%B9%B6%E6%A0%B9%E6%8D%AE%E5%AE%83%E4%BB%AC%E4%B9%8B%E9%97%B4%E8%81%94%E7%B3%BB%E7%9A%84%E5%AF%86%E5%88%87%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%A6%E5%8A%A0%E4%BB%A5%E7%BB%84%E5%90%88%E3%80%81%E5%88%92%E5%88%86%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="功能分区的原则是：分区明确、联系方便，并按主、次，内、外，闹、静关系合理安排，使其各得其所；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E5%88%86%E5%8C%BA%E7%9A%84%E5%8E%9F%E5%88%99%E6%98%AF%EF%BC%9A%E5%88%86%E5%8C%BA%E6%98%8E%E7%A1%AE%E3%80%81%E8%81%94%E7%B3%BB%E6%96%B9%E4%BE%BF%EF%BC%8C%E5%B9%B6%E6%8C%89%E4%B8%BB%E3%80%81%E6%AC%A1%EF%BC%8C%E5%86%85%E3%80%81%E5%A4%96%EF%BC%8C%E9%97%B9%E3%80%81%E9%9D%99%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%E5%90%88%E7%90%86%E5%AE%89%E6%8E%92%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%BF%E5%85%B6%E5%90%84%E5%BE%97%E5%85%B6%E6%89%80%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="同时还要根据实际使用要求，按人流活动的顺序关系安排位置。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%90%8C%E6%97%B6%E8%BF%98%E8%A6%81%E6%A0%B9%E6%8D%AE%E5%AE%9E%E9%99%85%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%EF%BC%8C%E6%8C%89%E4%BA%BA%E6%B5%81%E6%B4%BB%E5%8A%A8%E7%9A%84%E9%A1%BA%E5%BA%8F%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%E5%AE%89%E6%8E%92%E4%BD%8D%E7%BD%AE%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="空间组合、划分时要以主要空间为核心，次要空间的安排要有利于主要空间功能的发挥；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E7%BB%84%E5%90%88%E3%80%81%E5%88%92%E5%88%86%E6%97%B6%E8%A6%81%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E4%B8%BA%E6%A0%B8%E5%BF%83%EF%BC%8C%E6%AC%A1%E8%A6%81%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%89%E6%8E%92%E8%A6%81%E6%9C%89%E5%88%A9%E4%BA%8E%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%91%E6%8C%A5%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="对外联系的空间要靠近交通枢纽，内部使用的空间要相对隐蔽；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%AF%B9%E5%A4%96%E8%81%94%E7%B3%BB%E7%9A%84%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E8%A6%81%E9%9D%A0%E8%BF%91%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E6%9E%A2%E7%BA%BD%EF%BC%8C%E5%86%85%E9%83%A8%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E7%9A%84%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E8%A6%81%E7%9B%B8%E5%AF%B9%E9%9A%90%E8%94%BD%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="空间的联系与隔离要在深入分析的基础上恰当处理。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E7%9A%84%E8%81%94%E7%B3%BB%E4%B8%8E%E9%9A%94%E7%A6%BB%E8%A6%81%E5%9C%A8%E6%B7%B1%E5%85%A5%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E4%B8%8A%E6%81%B0%E5%BD%93%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（三）公共建筑的人流聚集与疏散" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%89%EF%BC%89%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%BA%E6%B5%81%E8%81%9A%E9%9B%86%E4%B8%8E%E7%96%8F%E6%95%A3%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="公共建筑在人流组织上，可以归纳为平面和立体两种方式。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%9C%A8%E4%BA%BA%E6%B5%81%E7%BB%84%E7%BB%87%E4%B8%8A%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E5%BD%92%E7%BA%B3%E4%B8%BA%E5%B9%B3%E9%9D%A2%E5%92%8C%E7%AB%8B%E4%BD%93%E4%B8%A4%E7%A7%8D%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="中小型公共建筑的人流活动比较简单，多采用平面组织方式。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%AD%E5%B0%8F%E5%9E%8B%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%BA%E6%B5%81%E6%B4%BB%E5%8A%A8%E6%AF%94%E8%BE%83%E7%AE%80%E5%8D%95%EF%BC%8C%E5%A4%9A%E9%87%87%E7%94%A8%E5%B9%B3%E9%9D%A2%E7%BB%84%E7%BB%87%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="规模较大的公共建筑，由于功能要求比较复杂，需要采用立体方式组织人流活动，如大型交通建筑。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%E8%BE%83%E5%A4%A7%E7%9A%84%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%EF%BC%8C%E7%94%B1%E4%BA%8E%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E6%AF%94%E8%BE%83%E5%A4%8D%E6%9D%82%EF%BC%8C%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E9%87%87%E7%94%A8%E7%AB%8B%E4%BD%93%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%E7%BB%84%E7%BB%87%E4%BA%BA%E6%B5%81%E6%B4%BB%E5%8A%A8%EF%BC%8C%E5%A6%82%E5%A4%A7%E5%9E%8B%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="公共建筑的人流疏散，有：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%BA%E6%B5%81%E7%96%8F%E6%95%A3%EF%BC%8C%E6%9C%89%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="连续性的（医院、商店、旅馆）、" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%BF%9E%E7%BB%AD%E6%80%A7%E7%9A%84%EF%BC%88%E5%8C%BB%E9%99%A2%E3%80%81%E5%95%86%E5%BA%97%E3%80%81%E6%97%85%E9%A6%86%EF%BC%89%E3%80%81%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="集中性的（影剧院、会堂、体育馆）、" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%9B%86%E4%B8%AD%E6%80%A7%E7%9A%84%EF%BC%88%E5%BD%B1%E5%89%A7%E9%99%A2%E3%80%81%E4%BC%9A%E5%A0%82%E3%80%81%E4%BD%93%E8%82%B2%E9%A6%86%EF%BC%89%E3%80%81%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="兼有连续和集中性的（展览馆、学校、铁路客运站）。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%85%BC%E6%9C%89%E8%BF%9E%E7%BB%AD%E5%92%8C%E9%9B%86%E4%B8%AD%E6%80%A7%E7%9A%84%EF%BC%88%E5%B1%95%E8%A7%88%E9%A6%86%E3%80%81%E5%AD%A6%E6%A0%A1%E3%80%81%E9%93%81%E8%B7%AF%E5%AE%A2%E8%BF%90%E7%AB%99%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      </outline>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（四）功能对于单一空间量、形、质的规定性单一建筑空间的大小、容量、形状以及采光、通风、日照条件是适用性的基本因素，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E5%9B%9B%EF%BC%89%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E5%AF%B9%E4%BA%8E%E5%8D%95%E4%B8%80%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E9%87%8F%E3%80%81%E5%BD%A2%E3%80%81%E8%B4%A8%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%84%E5%AE%9A%E6%80%A7%E5%8D%95%E4%B8%80%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%A7%E5%B0%8F%E3%80%81%E5%AE%B9%E9%87%8F%E3%80%81%E5%BD%A2%E7%8A%B6%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%8A%E9%87%87%E5%85%89%E3%80%81%E9%80%9A%E9%A3%8E%E3%80%81%E6%97%A5%E7%85%A7%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%E6%98%AF%E9%80%82%E7%94%A8%E6%80%A7%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E5%9B%A0%E7%B4%A0%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="同样是建筑功能问题的重要方面，应在设计中综合考虑，统筹解决。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%90%8C%E6%A0%B7%E6%98%AF%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E7%9A%84%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81%E6%96%B9%E9%9D%A2%EF%BC%8C%E5%BA%94%E5%9C%A8%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E4%B8%AD%E7%BB%BC%E5%90%88%E8%80%83%E8%99%91%EF%BC%8C%E7%BB%9F%E7%AD%B9%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="三、公共建筑的造型艺术" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%89%E3%80%81%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%9A%84%E9%80%A0%E5%9E%8B%E8%89%BA%E6%9C%AF%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="公共建筑的造型不仅有下面所列三个方面的内容，还包括民族形式、地域文化、构图技巧以及形式美的规律等。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%9A%84%E9%80%A0%E5%9E%8B%E4%B8%8D%E4%BB%85%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%8B%E9%9D%A2%E6%89%80%E5%88%97%E4%B8%89%E4%B8%AA%E6%96%B9%E9%9D%A2%E7%9A%84%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%98%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E6%B0%91%E6%97%8F%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E3%80%81%E5%9C%B0%E5%9F%9F%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96%E3%80%81%E6%9E%84%E5%9B%BE%E6%8A%80%E5%B7%A7%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%8A%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E7%BE%8E%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%84%E5%BE%8B%E7%AD%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（一）公共建筑造型艺术的基本特点" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%80%EF%BC%89%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E9%80%A0%E5%9E%8B%E8%89%BA%E6%9C%AF%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E7%89%B9%E7%82%B9%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="多样统一既是建筑艺术形式普遍认同的法则，自然也是公共建筑造型创作的重要依据。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%A4%9A%E6%A0%B7%E7%BB%9F%E4%B8%80%E6%97%A2%E6%98%AF%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%89%BA%E6%9C%AF%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E6%99%AE%E9%81%8D%E8%AE%A4%E5%90%8C%E7%9A%84%E6%B3%95%E5%88%99%EF%BC%8C%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6%E4%B9%9F%E6%98%AF%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E9%80%A0%E5%9E%8B%E5%88%9B%E4%BD%9C%E7%9A%84%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81%E4%BE%9D%E6%8D%AE%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="形式美的法则用于建筑艺术形式的创作时，常被称为“建筑构图原理”。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E7%BE%8E%E7%9A%84%E6%B3%95%E5%88%99%E7%94%A8%E4%BA%8E%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%89%BA%E6%9C%AF%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E7%9A%84%E5%88%9B%E4%BD%9C%E6%97%B6%EF%BC%8C%E5%B8%B8%E8%A2%AB%E7%A7%B0%E4%B8%BA%E2%80%9C%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E6%9E%84%E5%9B%BE%E5%8E%9F%E7%90%86%E2%80%9D%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="建筑的空间与实体是对立统一的两个方面，运用一定的构图技巧把它解决好，是建筑艺术创作中的核心问题。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%9A%84%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E4%B8%8E%E5%AE%9E%E4%BD%93%E6%98%AF%E5%AF%B9%E7%AB%8B%E7%BB%9F%E4%B8%80%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%A4%E4%B8%AA%E6%96%B9%E9%9D%A2%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%90%E7%94%A8%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%9A%E7%9A%84%E6%9E%84%E5%9B%BE%E6%8A%80%E5%B7%A7%E6%8A%8A%E5%AE%83%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E5%A5%BD%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%AF%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%89%BA%E6%9C%AF%E5%88%9B%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E6%A0%B8%E5%BF%83%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="只有处理好“多样统一”“形式与内容的统一”“正确对待传统与革新”等问题，才能创作出好的建筑作品。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%8F%AA%E6%9C%89%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86%E5%A5%BD%E2%80%9C%E5%A4%9A%E6%A0%B7%E7%BB%9F%E4%B8%80%E2%80%9D%E2%80%9C%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E4%B8%8E%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%9F%E4%B8%80%E2%80%9D%E2%80%9C%E6%AD%A3%E7%A1%AE%E5%AF%B9%E5%BE%85%E4%BC%A0%E7%BB%9F%E4%B8%8E%E9%9D%A9%E6%96%B0%E2%80%9D%E7%AD%89%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%EF%BC%8C%E6%89%8D%E8%83%BD%E5%88%9B%E4%BD%9C%E5%87%BA%E5%A5%BD%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E4%BD%9C%E5%93%81%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（二）室内空间环境艺术" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%BA%8C%EF%BC%89%E5%AE%A4%E5%86%85%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E8%89%BA%E6%9C%AF%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="《公共建筑设计原理》（第四版）着重分析了室内空间与比例尺度的关系、围透划分与序列导向的关系这两方面问题。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E3%80%8A%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%8E%9F%E7%90%86%E3%80%8B%EF%BC%88%E7%AC%AC%E5%9B%9B%E7%89%88%EF%BC%89%E7%9D%80%E9%87%8D%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E4%BA%86%E5%AE%A4%E5%86%85%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E4%B8%8E%E6%AF%94%E4%BE%8B%E5%B0%BA%E5%BA%A6%E7%9A%84%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%E3%80%81%E5%9B%B4%E9%80%8F%E5%88%92%E5%88%86%E4%B8%8E%E5%BA%8F%E5%88%97%E5%AF%BC%E5%90%91%E7%9A%84%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%E8%BF%99%E4%B8%A4%E6%96%B9%E9%9D%A2%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="其中西班牙巴塞罗那博览会德国馆，采用了围中有透、透中有围、围透结合的方法，从而创造出流动性的空间。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%85%B6%E4%B8%AD%E8%A5%BF%E7%8F%AD%E7%89%99%E5%B7%B4%E5%A1%9E%E7%BD%97%E9%82%A3%E5%8D%9A%E8%A7%88%E4%BC%9A%E5%BE%B7%E5%9B%BD%E9%A6%86%EF%BC%8C%E9%87%87%E7%94%A8%E4%BA%86%E5%9B%B4%E4%B8%AD%E6%9C%89%E9%80%8F%E3%80%81%E9%80%8F%E4%B8%AD%E6%9C%89%E5%9B%B4%E3%80%81%E5%9B%B4%E9%80%8F%E7%BB%93%E5%90%88%E7%9A%84%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%8E%E8%80%8C%E5%88%9B%E9%80%A0%E5%87%BA%E6%B5%81%E5%8A%A8%E6%80%A7%E7%9A%84%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（三）室外空间环境艺术" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%89%EF%BC%89%E5%AE%A4%E5%A4%96%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E8%89%BA%E6%9C%AF%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="公共建筑的形体与空间是建筑造型艺术中矛盾的两个方面，它们之间互为依存，不可分割。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%A2%E4%BD%93%E4%B8%8E%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E6%98%AF%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E9%80%A0%E5%9E%8B%E8%89%BA%E6%9C%AF%E4%B8%AD%E7%9F%9B%E7%9B%BE%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%A4%E4%B8%AA%E6%96%B9%E9%9D%A2%EF%BC%8C%E5%AE%83%E4%BB%AC%E4%B9%8B%E9%97%B4%E4%BA%92%E4%B8%BA%E4%BE%9D%E5%AD%98%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%AF%E5%88%86%E5%89%B2%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="公共建筑外部形体的艺术形式离不开统一与变化的构图原则。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%A4%96%E9%83%A8%E5%BD%A2%E4%BD%93%E7%9A%84%E8%89%BA%E6%9C%AF%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E7%A6%BB%E4%B8%8D%E5%BC%80%E7%BB%9F%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%8E%E5%8F%98%E5%8C%96%E7%9A%84%E6%9E%84%E5%9B%BE%E5%8E%9F%E5%88%99%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="构图中应注意“主从关系、对比与协调、均衡与稳定、节奏与韵律”等方面的关系。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%9E%84%E5%9B%BE%E4%B8%AD%E5%BA%94%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F%E2%80%9C%E4%B8%BB%E4%BB%8E%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%E3%80%81%E5%AF%B9%E6%AF%94%E4%B8%8E%E5%8D%8F%E8%B0%83%E3%80%81%E5%9D%87%E8%A1%A1%E4%B8%8E%E7%A8%B3%E5%AE%9A%E3%80%81%E8%8A%82%E5%A5%8F%E4%B8%8E%E9%9F%B5%E5%BE%8B%E2%80%9D%E7%AD%89%E6%96%B9%E9%9D%A2%E7%9A%84%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="常用的韵律手法有连续的韵律、渐变的韵律、起伏的韵律、交错的韵律（巴塞罗那博览会德国馆）等。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E7%9A%84%E9%9F%B5%E5%BE%8B%E6%89%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%89%E8%BF%9E%E7%BB%AD%E7%9A%84%E9%9F%B5%E5%BE%8B%E3%80%81%E6%B8%90%E5%8F%98%E7%9A%84%E9%9F%B5%E5%BE%8B%E3%80%81%E8%B5%B7%E4%BC%8F%E7%9A%84%E9%9F%B5%E5%BE%8B%E3%80%81%E4%BA%A4%E9%94%99%E7%9A%84%E9%9F%B5%E5%BE%8B%EF%BC%88%E5%B7%B4%E5%A1%9E%E7%BD%97%E9%82%A3%E5%8D%9A%E8%A7%88%E4%BC%9A%E5%BE%B7%E5%9B%BD%E9%A6%86%EF%BC%89%E7%AD%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="四、公共建筑的技术与经济问题" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9B%9B%E3%80%81%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%9A%84%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E4%B8%8E%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="建筑空间和体形的构成要以一定的工程技术条件作为手段。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E5%92%8C%E4%BD%93%E5%BD%A2%E7%9A%84%E6%9E%84%E6%88%90%E8%A6%81%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%9A%E7%9A%84%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%BA%E6%89%8B%E6%AE%B5%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="建筑的空间要求和建筑技术的发展是相互促进的。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%9A%84%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E5%92%8C%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E6%98%AF%E7%9B%B8%E4%BA%92%E4%BF%83%E8%BF%9B%E7%9A%84%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="选择技术形式时要满足功能要求，符合经济原则。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%80%89%E6%8B%A9%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E6%97%B6%E8%A6%81%E6%BB%A1%E8%B6%B3%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%EF%BC%8C%E7%AC%A6%E5%90%88%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E5%8E%9F%E5%88%99%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（一）公共建筑与结构技术" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%80%EF%BC%89%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E4%B8%8E%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="公共建筑常用的三种结构形式：混合结构、框架结构、空间结构。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%89%E7%A7%8D%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%EF%BC%9A%E6%B7%B7%E5%90%88%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E3%80%81%E6%A1%86%E6%9E%B6%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E3%80%81%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="1.混合结构" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1.%E6%B7%B7%E5%90%88%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="常为砖砌墙体、钢筋混凝土梁板体系，梁板跨度不大，承重墙平面呈矩形网格布置，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%B8%B8%E4%B8%BA%E7%A0%96%E7%A0%8C%E5%A2%99%E4%BD%93%E3%80%81%E9%92%A2%E7%AD%8B%E6%B7%B7%E5%87%9D%E5%9C%9F%E6%A2%81%E6%9D%BF%E4%BD%93%E7%B3%BB%EF%BC%8C%E6%A2%81%E6%9D%BF%E8%B7%A8%E5%BA%A6%E4%B8%8D%E5%A4%A7%EF%BC%8C%E6%89%BF%E9%87%8D%E5%A2%99%E5%B9%B3%E9%9D%A2%E5%91%88%E7%9F%A9%E5%BD%A2%E7%BD%91%E6%A0%BC%E5%B8%83%E7%BD%AE%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="适用于房间不大、层数不多的建筑（如学校、办公楼、医院）。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%80%82%E7%94%A8%E4%BA%8E%E6%88%BF%E9%97%B4%E4%B8%8D%E5%A4%A7%E3%80%81%E5%B1%82%E6%95%B0%E4%B8%8D%E5%A4%9A%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%EF%BC%88%E5%A6%82%E5%AD%A6%E6%A0%A1%E3%80%81%E5%8A%9E%E5%85%AC%E6%A5%BC%E3%80%81%E5%8C%BB%E9%99%A2%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="其承重墙要尽量均匀、交圈，上下层对齐，洞口大小有限，墙体高厚比要合理，大房间在上，小房间在下。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%85%B6%E6%89%BF%E9%87%8D%E5%A2%99%E8%A6%81%E5%B0%BD%E9%87%8F%E5%9D%87%E5%8C%80%E3%80%81%E4%BA%A4%E5%9C%88%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8A%E4%B8%8B%E5%B1%82%E5%AF%B9%E9%BD%90%EF%BC%8C%E6%B4%9E%E5%8F%A3%E5%A4%A7%E5%B0%8F%E6%9C%89%E9%99%90%EF%BC%8C%E5%A2%99%E4%BD%93%E9%AB%98%E5%8E%9A%E6%AF%94%E8%A6%81%E5%90%88%E7%90%86%EF%BC%8C%E5%A4%A7%E6%88%BF%E9%97%B4%E5%9C%A8%E4%B8%8A%EF%BC%8C%E5%B0%8F%E6%88%BF%E9%97%B4%E5%9C%A8%E4%B8%8B%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="2.框架结构" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2.%E6%A1%86%E6%9E%B6%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="承重与非承重构件分工明确，空间处理灵活，适用于高层或空间组合复杂的建筑。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%89%BF%E9%87%8D%E4%B8%8E%E9%9D%9E%E6%89%BF%E9%87%8D%E6%9E%84%E4%BB%B6%E5%88%86%E5%B7%A5%E6%98%8E%E7%A1%AE%EF%BC%8C%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86%E7%81%B5%E6%B4%BB%EF%BC%8C%E9%80%82%E7%94%A8%E4%BA%8E%E9%AB%98%E5%B1%82%E6%88%96%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E7%BB%84%E5%90%88%E5%A4%8D%E6%9D%82%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="3.空间结构（大跨度结构）" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E3.%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%EF%BC%88%E5%A4%A7%E8%B7%A8%E5%BA%A6%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%EF%BC%89%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="充分发挥材料性能，提供中间无柱的巨大空间，满足特殊的使用要求。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%85%85%E5%88%86%E5%8F%91%E6%8C%A5%E6%9D%90%E6%96%99%E6%80%A7%E8%83%BD%EF%BC%8C%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E4%B8%AD%E9%97%B4%E6%97%A0%E6%9F%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%B7%A8%E5%A4%A7%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%EF%BC%8C%E6%BB%A1%E8%B6%B3%E7%89%B9%E6%AE%8A%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="悬索、空间薄壁、充气薄膜、空间网架等，结合结构、构造课程，了解受力特点和造型的关系，记住国内外著名实例。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%82%AC%E7%B4%A2%E3%80%81%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E8%96%84%E5%A3%81%E3%80%81%E5%85%85%E6%B0%94%E8%96%84%E8%86%9C%E3%80%81%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E7%BD%91%E6%9E%B6%E7%AD%89%EF%BC%8C%E7%BB%93%E5%90%88%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E3%80%81%E6%9E%84%E9%80%A0%E8%AF%BE%E7%A8%8B%EF%BC%8C%E4%BA%86%E8%A7%A3%E5%8F%97%E5%8A%9B%E7%89%B9%E7%82%B9%E5%92%8C%E9%80%A0%E5%9E%8B%E7%9A%84%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%EF%BC%8C%E8%AE%B0%E4%BD%8F%E5%9B%BD%E5%86%85%E5%A4%96%E8%91%97%E5%90%8D%E5%AE%9E%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（二）公共建筑与设备" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%BA%8C%EF%BC%89%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E4%B8%8E%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="公共建筑的设备布置包含恰当安排设备用房，解决好建筑、结构与设备上的各种矛盾，注意减噪、防火、隔热。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%E5%B8%83%E7%BD%AE%E5%8C%85%E5%90%AB%E6%81%B0%E5%BD%93%E5%AE%89%E6%8E%92%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%E7%94%A8%E6%88%BF%EF%BC%8C%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E5%A5%BD%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E3%80%81%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E4%B8%8E%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%90%84%E7%A7%8D%E7%9F%9B%E7%9B%BE%EF%BC%8C%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F%E5%87%8F%E5%99%AA%E3%80%81%E9%98%B2%E7%81%AB%E3%80%81%E9%9A%94%E7%83%AD%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="结合设备课程，了解采暖、空调、照明各种系统的选型原则和适用范围。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%BB%93%E5%90%88%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%E8%AF%BE%E7%A8%8B%EF%BC%8C%E4%BA%86%E8%A7%A3%E9%87%87%E6%9A%96%E3%80%81%E7%A9%BA%E8%B0%83%E3%80%81%E7%85%A7%E6%98%8E%E5%90%84%E7%A7%8D%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%9A%84%E9%80%89%E5%9E%8B%E5%8E%9F%E5%88%99%E5%92%8C%E9%80%82%E7%94%A8%E8%8C%83%E5%9B%B4%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="1.采暖系统" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1.%E9%87%87%E6%9A%96%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="热水系统舒适、稳定，适用于居住建筑和托幼。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%83%AD%E6%B0%B4%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E8%88%92%E9%80%82%E3%80%81%E7%A8%B3%E5%AE%9A%EF%BC%8C%E9%80%82%E7%94%A8%E4%BA%8E%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%92%8C%E6%89%98%E5%B9%BC%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="蒸汽系统加热快，适用于间歇采暖建筑如会堂、剧场。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%92%B8%E6%B1%BD%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E5%8A%A0%E7%83%AD%E5%BF%AB%EF%BC%8C%E9%80%82%E7%94%A8%E4%BA%8E%E9%97%B4%E6%AD%87%E9%87%87%E6%9A%96%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%A6%82%E4%BC%9A%E5%A0%82%E3%80%81%E5%89%A7%E5%9C%BA%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="2.空调系统" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2.%E7%A9%BA%E8%B0%83%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="集中空调服务面大，机房集中，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%9B%86%E4%B8%AD%E7%A9%BA%E8%B0%83%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E9%9D%A2%E5%A4%A7%EF%BC%8C%E6%9C%BA%E6%88%BF%E9%9B%86%E4%B8%AD%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="管理方便，风速及噪声低，但机房大，风道粗，层高要求大，风量不易调节，运行费角大，不适用于小风量的复杂空间。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E6%96%B9%E4%BE%BF%EF%BC%8C%E9%A3%8E%E9%80%9F%E5%8F%8A%E5%99%AA%E5%A3%B0%E4%BD%8E%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%86%E6%9C%BA%E6%88%BF%E5%A4%A7%EF%BC%8C%E9%A3%8E%E9%81%93%E7%B2%97%EF%BC%8C%E5%B1%82%E9%AB%98%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E5%A4%A7%EF%BC%8C%E9%A3%8E%E9%87%8F%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%93%E8%B0%83%E8%8A%82%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E8%B4%B9%E8%A7%92%E5%A4%A7%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8D%E9%80%82%E7%94%A8%E4%BA%8E%E5%B0%8F%E9%A3%8E%E9%87%8F%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%8D%E6%9D%82%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="风机盘管系统，室温可调，适用于空间复杂、灵清潍需调温的建筑（如宾馆、实验室）。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%A3%8E%E6%9C%BA%E7%9B%98%E7%AE%A1%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%EF%BC%8C%E5%AE%A4%E6%B8%A9%E5%8F%AF%E8%B0%83%EF%BC%8C%E9%80%82%E7%94%A8%E4%BA%8E%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E5%A4%8D%E6%9D%82%E3%80%81%E7%81%B5%E6%B8%85%E6%BD%8D%E9%9C%80%E8%B0%83%E6%B8%A9%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%EF%BC%88%E5%A6%82%E5%AE%BE%E9%A6%86%E3%80%81%E5%AE%9E%E9%AA%8C%E5%AE%A4%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（三）公共建筑与经济" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%89%EF%BC%89%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E4%B8%8E%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="应当把一定的建筑标准作为考虑建筑经济问题的基础，设计要符合国家规定的建筑标准，防止铺张浪费，也不可片面追求低标准而降低建筑质量。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%BA%94%E5%BD%93%E6%8A%8A%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%9A%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E6%A0%87%E5%87%86%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%BA%E8%80%83%E8%99%91%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%EF%BC%8C%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E8%A6%81%E7%AC%A6%E5%90%88%E5%9B%BD%E5%AE%B6%E8%A7%84%E5%AE%9A%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E6%A0%87%E5%87%86%EF%BC%8C%E9%98%B2%E6%AD%A2%E9%93%BA%E5%BC%A0%E6%B5%AA%E8%B4%B9%EF%BC%8C%E4%B9%9F%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%AF%E7%89%87%E9%9D%A2%E8%BF%BD%E6%B1%82%E4%BD%8E%E6%A0%87%E5%87%86%E8%80%8C%E9%99%8D%E4%BD%8E%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%B4%A8%E9%87%8F%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="要注意节约建筑面积和体积，计算和控制建筑的有效面积系数、使用面积系数、结构面积系数和体积系数等指标，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%A6%81%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F%E8%8A%82%E7%BA%A6%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E9%9D%A2%E7%A7%AF%E5%92%8C%E4%BD%93%E7%A7%AF%EF%BC%8C%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E5%92%8C%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%89%E6%95%88%E9%9D%A2%E7%A7%AF%E7%B3%BB%E6%95%B0%E3%80%81%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E9%9D%A2%E7%A7%AF%E7%B3%BB%E6%95%B0%E3%80%81%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E9%9D%A2%E7%A7%AF%E7%B3%BB%E6%95%B0%E5%92%8C%E4%BD%93%E7%A7%AF%E7%B3%BB%E6%95%B0%E7%AD%89%E6%8C%87%E6%A0%87%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="节约用地，降低造价，以期获得较好的经济效益。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%8A%82%E7%BA%A6%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%8C%E9%99%8D%E4%BD%8E%E9%80%A0%E4%BB%B7%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A5%E6%9C%9F%E8%8E%B7%E5%BE%97%E8%BE%83%E5%A5%BD%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E6%95%88%E7%9B%8A%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="" _mubu_text="" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="第二节    住宅设计原理" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E8%8A%82%20%20%20%20%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%85%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%8E%9F%E7%90%86%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="一、住宅套型与家庭人口构成" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%80%E3%80%81%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%85%E5%A5%97%E5%9E%8B%E4%B8%8E%E5%AE%B6%E5%BA%AD%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E6%9E%84%E6%88%90%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="住宅建筑应能提供不同的套型居住空间供各种不同户型的住户使用。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%85%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%BA%94%E8%83%BD%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E7%9A%84%E5%A5%97%E5%9E%8B%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E4%BE%9B%E5%90%84%E7%A7%8D%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E6%88%B7%E5%9E%8B%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%8F%E6%88%B7%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="户型：是根据住户家庭人口构成（如人口规模、代际数和家庭结构）的不同而划分的住户类型。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%88%B7%E5%9E%8B%EF%BC%9A%E6%98%AF%E6%A0%B9%E6%8D%AE%E4%BD%8F%E6%88%B7%E5%AE%B6%E5%BA%AD%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E6%9E%84%E6%88%90%EF%BC%88%E5%A6%82%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%E3%80%81%E4%BB%A3%E9%99%85%E6%95%B0%E5%92%8C%E5%AE%B6%E5%BA%AD%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%EF%BC%89%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E8%80%8C%E5%88%92%E5%88%86%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%8F%E6%88%B7%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="套型：则是指为满足不同户型住户的生活居住需要而设计的不同类型的居住空间。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%A5%97%E5%9E%8B%EF%BC%9A%E5%88%99%E6%98%AF%E6%8C%87%E4%B8%BA%E6%BB%A1%E8%B6%B3%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E6%88%B7%E5%9E%8B%E4%BD%8F%E6%88%B7%E7%9A%84%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E8%80%8C%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B%E7%9A%84%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（一）家庭人口构成" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%80%EF%BC%89%E5%AE%B6%E5%BA%AD%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E6%9E%84%E6%88%90%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="不同的家庭人口构成形成不同的住户户型，而不同的住户户型则需要不同的住宅套型设计。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%B6%E5%BA%AD%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E6%9E%84%E6%88%90%E5%BD%A2%E6%88%90%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%8F%E6%88%B7%E6%88%B7%E5%9E%8B%EF%BC%8C%E8%80%8C%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%8F%E6%88%B7%E6%88%B7%E5%9E%8B%E5%88%99%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%85%E5%A5%97%E5%9E%8B%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="进行住宅套型设计时，首先必须了解住户的家庭人口构成情况。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%85%E5%A5%97%E5%9E%8B%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E6%97%B6%EF%BC%8C%E9%A6%96%E5%85%88%E5%BF%85%E9%A1%BB%E4%BA%86%E8%A7%A3%E4%BD%8F%E6%88%B7%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%B6%E5%BA%AD%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E6%9E%84%E6%88%90%E6%83%85%E5%86%B5%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="家庭人口构成可从户人口规模、户代际数和家庭人口结构等三方面考量。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%AE%B6%E5%BA%AD%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E6%9E%84%E6%88%90%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%8E%E6%88%B7%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%E3%80%81%E6%88%B7%E4%BB%A3%E9%99%85%E6%95%B0%E5%92%8C%E5%AE%B6%E5%BA%AD%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E7%AD%89%E4%B8%89%E6%96%B9%E9%9D%A2%E8%80%83%E9%87%8F%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="1.户人口规模" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1.%E6%88%B7%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="户人口规模指住户家庭人口的数量，对住宅套型的建筑面积指标和需布置的床位数具有决定意义。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%88%B7%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%E6%8C%87%E4%BD%8F%E6%88%B7%E5%AE%B6%E5%BA%AD%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E7%9A%84%E6%95%B0%E9%87%8F%EF%BC%8C%E5%AF%B9%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%85%E5%A5%97%E5%9E%8B%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E9%9D%A2%E7%A7%AF%E6%8C%87%E6%A0%87%E5%92%8C%E9%9C%80%E5%B8%83%E7%BD%AE%E7%9A%84%E5%BA%8A%E4%BD%8D%E6%95%B0%E5%85%B7%E6%9C%89%E5%86%B3%E5%AE%9A%E6%84%8F%E4%B9%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="在具体时期和地区的住宅建设中，不同户人口规模在总户数中所占比例将影响不同住宅套型的修建比例。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9C%A8%E5%85%B7%E4%BD%93%E6%97%B6%E6%9C%9F%E5%92%8C%E5%9C%B0%E5%8C%BA%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%85%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E4%B8%AD%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E6%88%B7%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%E5%9C%A8%E6%80%BB%E6%88%B7%E6%95%B0%E4%B8%AD%E6%89%80%E5%8D%A0%E6%AF%94%E4%BE%8B%E5%B0%86%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%85%E5%A5%97%E5%9E%8B%E7%9A%84%E4%BF%AE%E5%BB%BA%E6%AF%94%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="2.户代际数" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2.%E6%88%B7%E4%BB%A3%E9%99%85%E6%95%B0%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="户代际数指住户家庭常住人口的代际数。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%88%B7%E4%BB%A3%E9%99%85%E6%95%B0%E6%8C%87%E4%BD%8F%E6%88%B7%E5%AE%B6%E5%BA%AD%E5%B8%B8%E4%BD%8F%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E7%9A%84%E4%BB%A3%E9%99%85%E6%95%B0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="随着社会发展，多代户家庭趋于分解。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%9A%8F%E7%9D%80%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%EF%BC%8C%E5%A4%9A%E4%BB%A3%E6%88%B7%E5%AE%B6%E5%BA%AD%E8%B6%8B%E4%BA%8E%E5%88%86%E8%A7%A3%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="在住宅套型设计中，要使几代人能够各得其所、相对独立，又要使其相互联系、相互关照。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9C%A8%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%85%E5%A5%97%E5%9E%8B%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E4%B8%AD%EF%BC%8C%E8%A6%81%E4%BD%BF%E5%87%A0%E4%BB%A3%E4%BA%BA%E8%83%BD%E5%A4%9F%E5%90%84%E5%BE%97%E5%85%B6%E6%89%80%E3%80%81%E7%9B%B8%E5%AF%B9%E7%8B%AC%E7%AB%8B%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%88%E8%A6%81%E4%BD%BF%E5%85%B6%E7%9B%B8%E4%BA%92%E8%81%94%E7%B3%BB%E3%80%81%E7%9B%B8%E4%BA%92%E5%85%B3%E7%85%A7%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="3.家庭人口结构" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E3.%E5%AE%B6%E5%BA%AD%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="家庭人口结构指住户家庭成员的关系网络。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%AE%B6%E5%BA%AD%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E6%8C%87%E4%BD%8F%E6%88%B7%E5%AE%B6%E5%BA%AD%E6%88%90%E5%91%98%E7%9A%84%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="由于性别、辈分、姻亲关系等不同，可分为单身户、夫妻户、核心户、主干户、联合户及其他户。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%94%B1%E4%BA%8E%E6%80%A7%E5%88%AB%E3%80%81%E8%BE%88%E5%88%86%E3%80%81%E5%A7%BB%E4%BA%B2%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%E7%AD%89%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%AF%E5%88%86%E4%B8%BA%E5%8D%95%E8%BA%AB%E6%88%B7%E3%80%81%E5%A4%AB%E5%A6%BB%E6%88%B7%E3%80%81%E6%A0%B8%E5%BF%83%E6%88%B7%E3%80%81%E4%B8%BB%E5%B9%B2%E6%88%B7%E3%80%81%E8%81%94%E5%90%88%E6%88%B7%E5%8F%8A%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E6%88%B7%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="核心户：是指一对夫妻和其未婚子女所组成的家庭；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%A0%B8%E5%BF%83%E6%88%B7%EF%BC%9A%E6%98%AF%E6%8C%87%E4%B8%80%E5%AF%B9%E5%A4%AB%E5%A6%BB%E5%92%8C%E5%85%B6%E6%9C%AA%E5%A9%9A%E5%AD%90%E5%A5%B3%E6%89%80%E7%BB%84%E6%88%90%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%B6%E5%BA%AD%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="主干户：是指一对夫妻和其一对已婚子女所组成的家庭；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%BB%E5%B9%B2%E6%88%B7%EF%BC%9A%E6%98%AF%E6%8C%87%E4%B8%80%E5%AF%B9%E5%A4%AB%E5%A6%BB%E5%92%8C%E5%85%B6%E4%B8%80%E5%AF%B9%E5%B7%B2%E5%A9%9A%E5%AD%90%E5%A5%B3%E6%89%80%E7%BB%84%E6%88%90%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%B6%E5%BA%AD%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="联合户：是指一对夫妻和其多对已婚子女所组成的家庭。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%81%94%E5%90%88%E6%88%B7%EF%BC%9A%E6%98%AF%E6%8C%87%E4%B8%80%E5%AF%B9%E5%A4%AB%E5%A6%BB%E5%92%8C%E5%85%B6%E5%A4%9A%E5%AF%B9%E5%B7%B2%E5%A9%9A%E5%AD%90%E5%A5%B3%E6%89%80%E7%BB%84%E6%88%90%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%B6%E5%BA%AD%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（二）套型与家庭生活模式" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%BA%8C%EF%BC%89%E5%A5%97%E5%9E%8B%E4%B8%8E%E5%AE%B6%E5%BA%AD%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="住户的家庭生活行为模式是影响住宅套型空间组合的主要因素。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BD%8F%E6%88%B7%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%B6%E5%BA%AD%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%BA%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F%E6%98%AF%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%85%E5%A5%97%E5%9E%8B%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E7%BB%84%E5%90%88%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E5%9B%A0%E7%B4%A0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="家庭生活行为模式可分为家务型、休养型、交际型、家庭职业型、文化型等" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%AE%B6%E5%BA%AD%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%BA%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F%E5%8F%AF%E5%88%86%E4%B8%BA%E5%AE%B6%E5%8A%A1%E5%9E%8B%E3%80%81%E4%BC%91%E5%85%BB%E5%9E%8B%E3%80%81%E4%BA%A4%E9%99%85%E5%9E%8B%E3%80%81%E5%AE%B6%E5%BA%AD%E8%81%8C%E4%B8%9A%E5%9E%8B%E3%80%81%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96%E5%9E%8B%E7%AD%89%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（三）套型居住环境与生理" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%89%EF%BC%89%E5%A5%97%E5%9E%8B%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E4%B8%8E%E7%94%9F%E7%90%86%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="住宅套型作为一户居民家庭的居住空间环境，其空间形式必须满足人的生理活动需求，其空间的环境质量也必须符合人体生理上的需要。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%85%E5%A5%97%E5%9E%8B%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%80%E6%88%B7%E5%B1%85%E6%B0%91%E5%AE%B6%E5%BA%AD%E7%9A%84%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%B6%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E5%BF%85%E9%A1%BB%E6%BB%A1%E8%B6%B3%E4%BA%BA%E7%9A%84%E7%94%9F%E7%90%86%E6%B4%BB%E5%8A%A8%E9%9C%80%E6%B1%82%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%B6%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E7%9A%84%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E8%B4%A8%E9%87%8F%E4%B9%9F%E5%BF%85%E9%A1%BB%E7%AC%A6%E5%90%88%E4%BA%BA%E4%BD%93%E7%94%9F%E7%90%86%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="应当按照人的生理需要划分空间，同时保证良好的套型空间环境质量。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%BA%94%E5%BD%93%E6%8C%89%E7%85%A7%E4%BA%BA%E7%9A%84%E7%94%9F%E7%90%86%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E5%88%92%E5%88%86%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%EF%BC%8C%E5%90%8C%E6%97%B6%E4%BF%9D%E8%AF%81%E8%89%AF%E5%A5%BD%E7%9A%84%E5%A5%97%E5%9E%8B%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E8%B4%A8%E9%87%8F%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（四）套型居住环境与心理" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E5%9B%9B%EF%BC%89%E5%A5%97%E5%9E%8B%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E4%B8%8E%E5%BF%83%E7%90%86%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="人对居住空间环境的共同心理需求可归纳为：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BA%BA%E5%AF%B9%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E7%9A%84%E5%85%B1%E5%90%8C%E5%BF%83%E7%90%86%E9%9C%80%E6%B1%82%E5%8F%AF%E5%BD%92%E7%BA%B3%E4%B8%BA%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="安全感与心理健康、" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E6%84%9F%E4%B8%8E%E5%BF%83%E7%90%86%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%E3%80%81%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="私密性与开放性、" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%A7%81%E5%AF%86%E6%80%A7%E4%B8%8E%E5%BC%80%E6%94%BE%E6%80%A7%E3%80%81%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="自主性与灵活性、" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%87%AA%E4%B8%BB%E6%80%A7%E4%B8%8E%E7%81%B5%E6%B4%BB%E6%80%A7%E3%80%81%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="意境与趣味、" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%84%8F%E5%A2%83%E4%B8%8E%E8%B6%A3%E5%91%B3%E3%80%81%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="自然回归性等。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6%E5%9B%9E%E5%BD%92%E6%80%A7%E7%AD%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      </outline>
    </outline>
    <outline text="二、住宅套型设计" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BA%8C%E3%80%81%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%85%E5%A5%97%E5%9E%8B%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（一）住宅各功能空间" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%80%EF%BC%89%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%85%E5%90%84%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="1.居住空间" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1.%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="一套住宅根据不同的套型标准和居住对象，可以划分为卧室、起居室、工作学习室、餐室等。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%80%E5%A5%97%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%85%E6%A0%B9%E6%8D%AE%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E7%9A%84%E5%A5%97%E5%9E%8B%E6%A0%87%E5%87%86%E5%92%8C%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E5%AF%B9%E8%B1%A1%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E5%88%92%E5%88%86%E4%B8%BA%E5%8D%A7%E5%AE%A4%E3%80%81%E8%B5%B7%E5%B1%85%E5%AE%A4%E3%80%81%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E5%AE%A4%E3%80%81%E9%A4%90%E5%AE%A4%E7%AD%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="2.厨卫空间" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2.%E5%8E%A8%E5%8D%AB%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="厨卫空间是住宅设计的核心部分，它对住宅的功能与质量起着关键作用。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%8E%A8%E5%8D%AB%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E6%98%AF%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%85%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E7%9A%84%E6%A0%B8%E5%BF%83%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%EF%BC%8C%E5%AE%83%E5%AF%B9%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%85%E7%9A%84%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E4%B8%8E%E8%B4%A8%E9%87%8F%E8%B5%B7%E7%9D%80%E5%85%B3%E9%94%AE%E4%BD%9C%E7%94%A8%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="3.交通及其他辅助空间" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E3.%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E5%8F%8A%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E8%BE%85%E5%8A%A9%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（1）交通联系空间" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E8%81%94%E7%B3%BB%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="包括门斗或前室、过道、过厅及户内楼梯等。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E9%97%A8%E6%96%97%E6%88%96%E5%89%8D%E5%AE%A4%E3%80%81%E8%BF%87%E9%81%93%E3%80%81%E8%BF%87%E5%8E%85%E5%8F%8A%E6%88%B7%E5%86%85%E6%A5%BC%E6%A2%AF%E7%AD%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（2）贮藏空间" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E8%B4%AE%E8%97%8F%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="一套住宅中可以合理利用空间布置贮藏设施。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%80%E5%A5%97%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%85%E4%B8%AD%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E5%90%88%E7%90%86%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E5%B8%83%E7%BD%AE%E8%B4%AE%E8%97%8F%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（3）室外空间" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E5%AE%A4%E5%A4%96%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="住宅的室外活动空间，包括阳台、露台以及低层住宅的户内庭院。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%85%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%A4%E5%A4%96%E6%B4%BB%E5%8A%A8%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%EF%BC%8C%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E9%98%B3%E5%8F%B0%E3%80%81%E9%9C%B2%E5%8F%B0%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%8A%E4%BD%8E%E5%B1%82%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%85%E7%9A%84%E6%88%B7%E5%86%85%E5%BA%AD%E9%99%A2%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（4）其他设施" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%884%EF%BC%89%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="包括晾晒设施、垃圾处理等。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E6%99%BE%E6%99%92%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E3%80%81%E5%9E%83%E5%9C%BE%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86%E7%AD%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（二）住宅套型空间组合设计" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%BA%8C%EF%BC%89%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%85%E5%A5%97%E5%9E%8B%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E7%BB%84%E5%90%88%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="1.户内功能分区" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1.%E6%88%B7%E5%86%85%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E5%88%86%E5%8C%BA%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（1）内外分区。按空间使用功能的私密程度的层次划分，卧室、书房、主人卫生间等为私密区，应安排在最内部。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E5%86%85%E5%A4%96%E5%88%86%E5%8C%BA%E3%80%82%E6%8C%89%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E7%9A%84%E7%A7%81%E5%AF%86%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%A6%E7%9A%84%E5%B1%82%E6%AC%A1%E5%88%92%E5%88%86%EF%BC%8C%E5%8D%A7%E5%AE%A4%E3%80%81%E4%B9%A6%E6%88%BF%E3%80%81%E4%B8%BB%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%AB%E7%94%9F%E9%97%B4%E7%AD%89%E4%B8%BA%E7%A7%81%E5%AF%86%E5%8C%BA%EF%BC%8C%E5%BA%94%E5%AE%89%E6%8E%92%E5%9C%A8%E6%9C%80%E5%86%85%E9%83%A8%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（2）动静分区。会客厅、起居室、餐厅、厨房和家务室是住宅中的动区；卧室、书房是静区。有时也可将父母与孩子的活动按动静分区来考虑。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E5%8A%A8%E9%9D%99%E5%88%86%E5%8C%BA%E3%80%82%E4%BC%9A%E5%AE%A2%E5%8E%85%E3%80%81%E8%B5%B7%E5%B1%85%E5%AE%A4%E3%80%81%E9%A4%90%E5%8E%85%E3%80%81%E5%8E%A8%E6%88%BF%E5%92%8C%E5%AE%B6%E5%8A%A1%E5%AE%A4%E6%98%AF%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%85%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E5%8A%A8%E5%8C%BA%EF%BC%9B%E5%8D%A7%E5%AE%A4%E3%80%81%E4%B9%A6%E6%88%BF%E6%98%AF%E9%9D%99%E5%8C%BA%E3%80%82%E6%9C%89%E6%97%B6%E4%B9%9F%E5%8F%AF%E5%B0%86%E7%88%B6%E6%AF%8D%E4%B8%8E%E5%AD%A9%E5%AD%90%E7%9A%84%E6%B4%BB%E5%8A%A8%E6%8C%89%E5%8A%A8%E9%9D%99%E5%88%86%E5%8C%BA%E6%9D%A5%E8%80%83%E8%99%91%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（3）洁污分区。主要体现为有烟气、污水及垃圾污染的区域和清洁卫生区域的区分。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E6%B4%81%E6%B1%A1%E5%88%86%E5%8C%BA%E3%80%82%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E4%BD%93%E7%8E%B0%E4%B8%BA%E6%9C%89%E7%83%9F%E6%B0%94%E3%80%81%E6%B1%A1%E6%B0%B4%E5%8F%8A%E5%9E%83%E5%9C%BE%E6%B1%A1%E6%9F%93%E7%9A%84%E5%8C%BA%E5%9F%9F%E5%92%8C%E6%B8%85%E6%B4%81%E5%8D%AB%E7%94%9F%E5%8C%BA%E5%9F%9F%E7%9A%84%E5%8C%BA%E5%88%86%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（4）合理分室" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%884%EF%BC%89%E5%90%88%E7%90%86%E5%88%86%E5%AE%A4%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="住宅的合理分室是把不同的功能空间分别独立出来，避免空间功能的合用与重叠。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%85%E7%9A%84%E5%90%88%E7%90%86%E5%88%86%E5%AE%A4%E6%98%AF%E6%8A%8A%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E7%9A%84%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E5%88%86%E5%88%AB%E7%8B%AC%E7%AB%8B%E5%87%BA%E6%9D%A5%EF%BC%8C%E9%81%BF%E5%85%8D%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E7%9A%84%E5%90%88%E7%94%A8%E4%B8%8E%E9%87%8D%E5%8F%A0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="合理分室包括生理分室和功能分室两方面。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%90%88%E7%90%86%E5%88%86%E5%AE%A4%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E7%94%9F%E7%90%86%E5%88%86%E5%AE%A4%E5%92%8C%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E5%88%86%E5%AE%A4%E4%B8%A4%E6%96%B9%E9%9D%A2%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="生理分室与家庭成员的性别、年龄、人数、辈分、婚姻关系等因素有关。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%94%9F%E7%90%86%E5%88%86%E5%AE%A4%E4%B8%8E%E5%AE%B6%E5%BA%AD%E6%88%90%E5%91%98%E7%9A%84%E6%80%A7%E5%88%AB%E3%80%81%E5%B9%B4%E9%BE%84%E3%80%81%E4%BA%BA%E6%95%B0%E3%80%81%E8%BE%88%E5%88%86%E3%80%81%E5%A9%9A%E5%A7%BB%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%E7%AD%89%E5%9B%A0%E7%B4%A0%E6%9C%89%E5%85%B3%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="功能分室是把不同的功能空间分离，避免互相干扰，提高使用质量。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E5%88%86%E5%AE%A4%E6%98%AF%E6%8A%8A%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E7%9A%84%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E5%88%86%E7%A6%BB%EF%BC%8C%E9%81%BF%E5%85%8D%E4%BA%92%E7%9B%B8%E5%B9%B2%E6%89%B0%EF%BC%8C%E6%8F%90%E9%AB%98%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E8%B4%A8%E9%87%8F%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="2.套型朝向及通风组织" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2.%E5%A5%97%E5%9E%8B%E6%9C%9D%E5%90%91%E5%8F%8A%E9%80%9A%E9%A3%8E%E7%BB%84%E7%BB%87%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（1）单朝向套型" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E5%8D%95%E6%9C%9D%E5%90%91%E5%A5%97%E5%9E%8B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="一套住宅只有一个朝向时，应避免最不利朝向，如北方地区应避免北向，南方地区应避免西向。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%80%E5%A5%97%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%85%E5%8F%AA%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E6%9C%9D%E5%90%91%E6%97%B6%EF%BC%8C%E5%BA%94%E9%81%BF%E5%85%8D%E6%9C%80%E4%B8%8D%E5%88%A9%E6%9C%9D%E5%90%91%EF%BC%8C%E5%A6%82%E5%8C%97%E6%96%B9%E5%9C%B0%E5%8C%BA%E5%BA%94%E9%81%BF%E5%85%8D%E5%8C%97%E5%90%91%EF%BC%8C%E5%8D%97%E6%96%B9%E5%9C%B0%E5%8C%BA%E5%BA%94%E9%81%BF%E5%85%8D%E8%A5%BF%E5%90%91%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="单朝向时，套内通风较难解决，可用对通风要求不高的北方地区；在严寒地区还有利于防寒。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%8D%95%E6%9C%9D%E5%90%91%E6%97%B6%EF%BC%8C%E5%A5%97%E5%86%85%E9%80%9A%E9%A3%8E%E8%BE%83%E9%9A%BE%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%AF%E7%94%A8%E5%AF%B9%E9%80%9A%E9%A3%8E%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E4%B8%8D%E9%AB%98%E7%9A%84%E5%8C%97%E6%96%B9%E5%9C%B0%E5%8C%BA%EF%BC%9B%E5%9C%A8%E4%B8%A5%E5%AF%92%E5%9C%B0%E5%8C%BA%E8%BF%98%E6%9C%89%E5%88%A9%E4%BA%8E%E9%98%B2%E5%AF%92%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（2）每套有相对或相邻两个朝向" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E6%AF%8F%E5%A5%97%E6%9C%89%E7%9B%B8%E5%AF%B9%E6%88%96%E7%9B%B8%E9%82%BB%E4%B8%A4%E4%B8%AA%E6%9C%9D%E5%90%91%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="此类套型有利于组织套内通风，但应注意厨房、卫生间与居室间的气流组织，避免油烟等有害气体对居住环境的污染。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%AD%A4%E7%B1%BB%E5%A5%97%E5%9E%8B%E6%9C%89%E5%88%A9%E4%BA%8E%E7%BB%84%E7%BB%87%E5%A5%97%E5%86%85%E9%80%9A%E9%A3%8E%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%86%E5%BA%94%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F%E5%8E%A8%E6%88%BF%E3%80%81%E5%8D%AB%E7%94%9F%E9%97%B4%E4%B8%8E%E5%B1%85%E5%AE%A4%E9%97%B4%E7%9A%84%E6%B0%94%E6%B5%81%E7%BB%84%E7%BB%87%EF%BC%8C%E9%81%BF%E5%85%8D%E6%B2%B9%E7%83%9F%E7%AD%89%E6%9C%89%E5%AE%B3%E6%B0%94%E4%BD%93%E5%AF%B9%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E7%9A%84%E6%B1%A1%E6%9F%93%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（3）利用平面凹凸及设置内矢井来组织朝向及通风这种处理方式常可起到增加房屋进深的作用，有利于节约用地。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8%E5%B9%B3%E9%9D%A2%E5%87%B9%E5%87%B8%E5%8F%8A%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE%E5%86%85%E7%9F%A2%E4%BA%95%E6%9D%A5%E7%BB%84%E7%BB%87%E6%9C%9D%E5%90%91%E5%8F%8A%E9%80%9A%E9%A3%8E%E8%BF%99%E7%A7%8D%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%E5%B8%B8%E5%8F%AF%E8%B5%B7%E5%88%B0%E5%A2%9E%E5%8A%A0%E6%88%BF%E5%B1%8B%E8%BF%9B%E6%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%9C%E7%94%A8%EF%BC%8C%E6%9C%89%E5%88%A9%E4%BA%8E%E8%8A%82%E7%BA%A6%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="3.套型的空间组织" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E3.%E5%A5%97%E5%9E%8B%E7%9A%84%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E7%BB%84%E7%BB%87%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="套型的空间组织千变万化。目前常见的大致有：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%A5%97%E5%9E%8B%E7%9A%84%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E7%BB%84%E7%BB%87%E5%8D%83%E5%8F%98%E4%B8%87%E5%8C%96%E3%80%82%E7%9B%AE%E5%89%8D%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%81%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%A7%E8%87%B4%E6%9C%89%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（1）餐室厨房型（DK型）是指炊事与就餐合用同一空间的形式，适用于小面积、人口少的住户。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E9%A4%90%E5%AE%A4%E5%8E%A8%E6%88%BF%E5%9E%8B%EF%BC%88DK%E5%9E%8B%EF%BC%89%E6%98%AF%E6%8C%87%E7%82%8A%E4%BA%8B%E4%B8%8E%E5%B0%B1%E9%A4%90%E5%90%88%E7%94%A8%E5%90%8C%E4%B8%80%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%EF%BC%8C%E9%80%82%E7%94%A8%E4%BA%8E%E5%B0%8F%E9%9D%A2%E7%A7%AF%E3%80%81%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E5%B0%91%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%8F%E6%88%B7%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="采用DK式空间，必须注意油烟的排除及采光通风问题的解决。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%87%87%E7%94%A8DK%E5%BC%8F%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%EF%BC%8C%E5%BF%85%E9%A1%BB%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F%E6%B2%B9%E7%83%9F%E7%9A%84%E6%8E%92%E9%99%A4%E5%8F%8A%E9%87%87%E5%85%89%E9%80%9A%E9%A3%8E%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="另有一种D·K型，将就餐空间与厨房紧邻并适当隔离，使就餐与炉灶分开，避免油烟污染。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%8F%A6%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%80%E7%A7%8DD%C2%B7K%E5%9E%8B%EF%BC%8C%E5%B0%86%E5%B0%B1%E9%A4%90%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E4%B8%8E%E5%8E%A8%E6%88%BF%E7%B4%A7%E9%82%BB%E5%B9%B6%E9%80%82%E5%BD%93%E9%9A%94%E7%A6%BB%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%BF%E5%B0%B1%E9%A4%90%E4%B8%8E%E7%82%89%E7%81%B6%E5%88%86%E5%BC%80%EF%BC%8C%E9%81%BF%E5%85%8D%E6%B2%B9%E7%83%9F%E6%B1%A1%E6%9F%93%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（2）小方厅型（B·D型）用兼作就餐和家务的小方厅组织套内空间。家庭人口多、卧室不足、生活标准较低时采用。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E5%B0%8F%E6%96%B9%E5%8E%85%E5%9E%8B%EF%BC%88B%C2%B7D%E5%9E%8B%EF%BC%89%E7%94%A8%E5%85%BC%E4%BD%9C%E5%B0%B1%E9%A4%90%E5%92%8C%E5%AE%B6%E5%8A%A1%E7%9A%84%E5%B0%8F%E6%96%B9%E5%8E%85%E7%BB%84%E7%BB%87%E5%A5%97%E5%86%85%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E3%80%82%E5%AE%B6%E5%BA%AD%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E5%A4%9A%E3%80%81%E5%8D%A7%E5%AE%A4%E4%B8%8D%E8%B6%B3%E3%80%81%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E6%A0%87%E5%87%86%E8%BE%83%E4%BD%8E%E6%97%B6%E9%87%87%E7%94%A8%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（3）起居型（LBD型）将起居空间独立出来，并以其为中心组织套内空间，有利于动静分区。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E8%B5%B7%E5%B1%85%E5%9E%8B%EF%BC%88LBD%E5%9E%8B%EF%BC%89%E5%B0%86%E8%B5%B7%E5%B1%85%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E7%8B%AC%E7%AB%8B%E5%87%BA%E6%9D%A5%EF%BC%8C%E5%B9%B6%E4%BB%A5%E5%85%B6%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%E7%BB%84%E7%BB%87%E5%A5%97%E5%86%85%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%EF%BC%8C%E6%9C%89%E5%88%A9%E4%BA%8E%E5%8A%A8%E9%9D%99%E5%88%86%E5%8C%BA%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="这种形式又可分为以下几种：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%BF%99%E7%A7%8D%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E5%8F%88%E5%8F%AF%E5%88%86%E4%B8%BA%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8B%E5%87%A0%E7%A7%8D%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="1）L·BD型：仅将起居独立，睡眠与用餐合一；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1%EF%BC%89L%C2%B7BD%E5%9E%8B%EF%BC%9A%E4%BB%85%E5%B0%86%E8%B5%B7%E5%B1%85%E7%8B%AC%E7%AB%8B%EF%BC%8C%E7%9D%A1%E7%9C%A0%E4%B8%8E%E7%94%A8%E9%A4%90%E5%90%88%E4%B8%80%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="2）L·B·D型：将起居、用餐、睡眠均分离开来；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2%EF%BC%89L%C2%B7B%C2%B7D%E5%9E%8B%EF%BC%9A%E5%B0%86%E8%B5%B7%E5%B1%85%E3%80%81%E7%94%A8%E9%A4%90%E3%80%81%E7%9D%A1%E7%9C%A0%E5%9D%87%E5%88%86%E7%A6%BB%E5%BC%80%E6%9D%A5%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="3）B·LD型：将睡眠独立，起居、用餐合一。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E3%EF%BC%89B%C2%B7LD%E5%9E%8B%EF%BC%9A%E5%B0%86%E7%9D%A1%E7%9C%A0%E7%8B%AC%E7%AB%8B%EF%BC%8C%E8%B5%B7%E5%B1%85%E3%80%81%E7%94%A8%E9%A4%90%E5%90%88%E4%B8%80%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      </outline>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（4）起居、餐厨合一型（LDK型）将起居、用餐、炊事等活动设于同一空间中，国外较多见，但不大符合我国生活习惯。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%884%EF%BC%89%E8%B5%B7%E5%B1%85%E3%80%81%E9%A4%90%E5%8E%A8%E5%90%88%E4%B8%80%E5%9E%8B%EF%BC%88LDK%E5%9E%8B%EF%BC%89%E5%B0%86%E8%B5%B7%E5%B1%85%E3%80%81%E7%94%A8%E9%A4%90%E3%80%81%E7%82%8A%E4%BA%8B%E7%AD%89%E6%B4%BB%E5%8A%A8%E8%AE%BE%E4%BA%8E%E5%90%8C%E4%B8%80%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E4%B8%AD%EF%BC%8C%E5%9B%BD%E5%A4%96%E8%BE%83%E5%A4%9A%E8%A7%81%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%86%E4%B8%8D%E5%A4%A7%E7%AC%A6%E5%90%88%E6%88%91%E5%9B%BD%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E4%B9%A0%E6%83%AF%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="主要是我国烹饪时油烟较大，易对起居产生污染。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E6%98%AF%E6%88%91%E5%9B%BD%E7%83%B9%E9%A5%AA%E6%97%B6%E6%B2%B9%E7%83%9F%E8%BE%83%E5%A4%A7%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%93%E5%AF%B9%E8%B5%B7%E5%B1%85%E4%BA%A7%E7%94%9F%E6%B1%A1%E6%9F%93%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（5）三维空间组合型" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%885%EF%BC%89%E4%B8%89%E7%BB%B4%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E7%BB%84%E5%90%88%E5%9E%8B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="包括变层高住宅、复式住宅和跃层住宅等形式。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E5%8F%98%E5%B1%82%E9%AB%98%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%85%E3%80%81%E5%A4%8D%E5%BC%8F%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%85%E5%92%8C%E8%B7%83%E5%B1%82%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%85%E7%AD%89%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="4.空间可灵活分隔的住宅体系" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E4.%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E5%8F%AF%E7%81%B5%E6%B4%BB%E5%88%86%E9%9A%94%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%85%E4%BD%93%E7%B3%BB%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（1）SAR体系住宅" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89SAR%E4%BD%93%E7%B3%BB%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%85%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="由荷兰建筑师提出的一套住宅设计理论和方法，也叫支撑体住宅体系。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%94%B1%E8%8D%B7%E5%85%B0%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%88%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%80%E5%A5%97%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%85%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA%E5%92%8C%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%EF%BC%8C%E4%B9%9F%E5%8F%AB%E6%94%AF%E6%92%91%E4%BD%93%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%85%E4%BD%93%E7%B3%BB%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="它将住宅的设计和建造分为两部分；支撑体和填充体。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%AE%83%E5%B0%86%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%85%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%92%8C%E5%BB%BA%E9%80%A0%E5%88%86%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%A4%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%EF%BC%9B%E6%94%AF%E6%92%91%E4%BD%93%E5%92%8C%E5%A1%AB%E5%85%85%E4%BD%93%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="SAR体系住宅具有很大的灵活性和可变性。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3ESAR%E4%BD%93%E7%B3%BB%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%85%E5%85%B7%E6%9C%89%E5%BE%88%E5%A4%A7%E7%9A%84%E7%81%B5%E6%B4%BB%E6%80%A7%E5%92%8C%E5%8F%AF%E5%8F%98%E6%80%A7%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="套型面积可大可小，套型单元可分可合，并为居住者参与设计提供了可能。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%A5%97%E5%9E%8B%E9%9D%A2%E7%A7%AF%E5%8F%AF%E5%A4%A7%E5%8F%AF%E5%B0%8F%EF%BC%8C%E5%A5%97%E5%9E%8B%E5%8D%95%E5%85%83%E5%8F%AF%E5%88%86%E5%8F%AF%E5%90%88%EF%BC%8C%E5%B9%B6%E4%B8%BA%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E8%80%85%E5%8F%82%E4%B8%8E%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E4%BA%86%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（2）大开间住宅" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E5%A4%A7%E5%BC%80%E9%97%B4%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%85%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="这种住宅使用大开间结构，一般将楼梯间、厨房、卫生间相对固定，其余空间不作分隔，而由住户自行选择空间划分形式。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%BF%99%E7%A7%8D%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%85%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E5%A4%A7%E5%BC%80%E9%97%B4%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%80%E8%88%AC%E5%B0%86%E6%A5%BC%E6%A2%AF%E9%97%B4%E3%80%81%E5%8E%A8%E6%88%BF%E3%80%81%E5%8D%AB%E7%94%9F%E9%97%B4%E7%9B%B8%E5%AF%B9%E5%9B%BA%E5%AE%9A%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%B6%E4%BD%99%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E4%B8%8D%E4%BD%9C%E5%88%86%E9%9A%94%EF%BC%8C%E8%80%8C%E7%94%B1%E4%BD%8F%E6%88%B7%E8%87%AA%E8%A1%8C%E9%80%89%E6%8B%A9%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E5%88%92%E5%88%86%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="三、住宅建筑的质量与经济问题" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%89%E3%80%81%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%85%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%9A%84%E8%B4%A8%E9%87%8F%E4%B8%8E%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="住宅质量标准主要有三项内容，即功能与室内环境标准、设备与设施标准和建筑结构与安全防卫标准" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%85%E8%B4%A8%E9%87%8F%E6%A0%87%E5%87%86%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%89%E9%A1%B9%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%EF%BC%8C%E5%8D%B3%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E4%B8%8E%E5%AE%A4%E5%86%85%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E6%A0%87%E5%87%86%E3%80%81%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%E4%B8%8E%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E6%A0%87%E5%87%86%E5%92%8C%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E4%B8%8E%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E9%98%B2%E5%8D%AB%E6%A0%87%E5%87%86%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="住宅的质量和经济问题是一个综合性课题，从规划、设计、施工，一直到维修、管理等一系列建设活动过程中，都包含有经济因素。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%85%E7%9A%84%E8%B4%A8%E9%87%8F%E5%92%8C%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E7%BB%BC%E5%90%88%E6%80%A7%E8%AF%BE%E9%A2%98%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%8E%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E3%80%81%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E3%80%81%E6%96%BD%E5%B7%A5%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E5%88%B0%E7%BB%B4%E4%BF%AE%E3%80%81%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E7%AD%89%E4%B8%80%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E6%B4%BB%E5%8A%A8%E8%BF%87%E7%A8%8B%E4%B8%AD%EF%BC%8C%E9%83%BD%E5%8C%85%E5%90%AB%E6%9C%89%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E5%9B%A0%E7%B4%A0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="经济的概念是投入与产出的矛盾统一体，涉及节约与效益两个方面。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E7%9A%84%E6%A6%82%E5%BF%B5%E6%98%AF%E6%8A%95%E5%85%A5%E4%B8%8E%E4%BA%A7%E5%87%BA%E7%9A%84%E7%9F%9B%E7%9B%BE%E7%BB%9F%E4%B8%80%E4%BD%93%EF%BC%8C%E6%B6%89%E5%8F%8A%E8%8A%82%E7%BA%A6%E4%B8%8E%E6%95%88%E7%9B%8A%E4%B8%A4%E4%B8%AA%E6%96%B9%E9%9D%A2%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="为使不同的设计具有可比性，通常采用平均每平方米建筑面积的资金投入作为一项经济指标，也就是造价。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%BA%E4%BD%BF%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%85%B7%E6%9C%89%E5%8F%AF%E6%AF%94%E6%80%A7%EF%BC%8C%E9%80%9A%E5%B8%B8%E9%87%87%E7%94%A8%E5%B9%B3%E5%9D%87%E6%AF%8F%E5%B9%B3%E6%96%B9%E7%B1%B3%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E9%9D%A2%E7%A7%AF%E7%9A%84%E8%B5%84%E9%87%91%E6%8A%95%E5%85%A5%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%80%E9%A1%B9%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E6%8C%87%E6%A0%87%EF%BC%8C%E4%B9%9F%E5%B0%B1%E6%98%AF%E9%80%A0%E4%BB%B7%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（一）节约材料" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%80%EF%BC%89%E8%8A%82%E7%BA%A6%E6%9D%90%E6%96%99%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="在设计中应尽量节约钢材、永泥、木材三大主材的消耗。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9C%A8%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E4%B8%AD%E5%BA%94%E5%B0%BD%E9%87%8F%E8%8A%82%E7%BA%A6%E9%92%A2%E6%9D%90%E3%80%81%E6%B0%B8%E6%B3%A5%E3%80%81%E6%9C%A8%E6%9D%90%E4%B8%89%E5%A4%A7%E4%B8%BB%E6%9D%90%E7%9A%84%E6%B6%88%E8%80%97%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="在基地许可时，尽量采用多单元拼接，一般以3~4个单元或房屋的长度在60m左右较为合适。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9C%A8%E5%9F%BA%E5%9C%B0%E8%AE%B8%E5%8F%AF%E6%97%B6%EF%BC%8C%E5%B0%BD%E9%87%8F%E9%87%87%E7%94%A8%E5%A4%9A%E5%8D%95%E5%85%83%E6%8B%BC%E6%8E%A5%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%80%E8%88%AC%E4%BB%A53~4%E4%B8%AA%E5%8D%95%E5%85%83%E6%88%96%E6%88%BF%E5%B1%8B%E7%9A%84%E9%95%BF%E5%BA%A6%E5%9C%A860m%E5%B7%A6%E5%8F%B3%E8%BE%83%E4%B8%BA%E5%90%88%E9%80%82%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="充分利用材料的强度，推广新结构、新技术、新材料；因地制宜、就地取材。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%85%85%E5%88%86%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8%E6%9D%90%E6%96%99%E7%9A%84%E5%BC%BA%E5%BA%A6%EF%BC%8C%E6%8E%A8%E5%B9%BF%E6%96%B0%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E3%80%81%E6%96%B0%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E3%80%81%E6%96%B0%E6%9D%90%E6%96%99%EF%BC%9B%E5%9B%A0%E5%9C%B0%E5%88%B6%E5%AE%9C%E3%80%81%E5%B0%B1%E5%9C%B0%E5%8F%96%E6%9D%90%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="选择适当的建筑材料和构造方案，同时注意管线设备的集中布置。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%80%89%E6%8B%A9%E9%80%82%E5%BD%93%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E6%9D%90%E6%96%99%E5%92%8C%E6%9E%84%E9%80%A0%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%EF%BC%8C%E5%90%8C%E6%97%B6%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F%E7%AE%A1%E7%BA%BF%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%E7%9A%84%E9%9B%86%E4%B8%AD%E5%B8%83%E7%BD%AE%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（二）节约能源" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%BA%8C%EF%BC%89%E8%8A%82%E7%BA%A6%E8%83%BD%E6%BA%90%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="就住宅建筑设计而言，节能包括降低建设及使用期间的能耗与提高能源使用效率两方面内容。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%B0%B1%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%85%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E8%80%8C%E8%A8%80%EF%BC%8C%E8%8A%82%E8%83%BD%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E9%99%8D%E4%BD%8E%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E5%8F%8A%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E6%9C%9F%E9%97%B4%E7%9A%84%E8%83%BD%E8%80%97%E4%B8%8E%E6%8F%90%E9%AB%98%E8%83%BD%E6%BA%90%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E6%95%88%E7%8E%87%E4%B8%A4%E6%96%B9%E9%9D%A2%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="节约能源的措施主要有：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%8A%82%E7%BA%A6%E8%83%BD%E6%BA%90%E7%9A%84%E6%8E%AA%E6%96%BD%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E6%9C%89%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="合理的规划布局（朝向、通风），" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%90%88%E7%90%86%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%EF%BC%88%E6%9C%9D%E5%90%91%E3%80%81%E9%80%9A%E9%A3%8E%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="合理的体形系数，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%90%88%E7%90%86%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%93%E5%BD%A2%E7%B3%BB%E6%95%B0%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="合理的建筑外围护结构的热工性能，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%90%88%E7%90%86%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%A4%96%E5%9B%B4%E6%8A%A4%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E7%9A%84%E7%83%AD%E5%B7%A5%E6%80%A7%E8%83%BD%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="有效合理的设备设施，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%9C%89%E6%95%88%E5%90%88%E7%90%86%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="以及尽量采用可再生能源。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%8A%E5%B0%BD%E9%87%8F%E9%87%87%E7%94%A8%E5%8F%AF%E5%86%8D%E7%94%9F%E8%83%BD%E6%BA%90%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      </outline>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（三）节约用地" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%89%EF%BC%89%E8%8A%82%E7%BA%A6%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="1.住宅单体设计中的节地措施：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1.%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%85%E5%8D%95%E4%BD%93%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E8%8A%82%E5%9C%B0%E6%8E%AA%E6%96%BD%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（1）8层以下住宅增加层数可节约较多用地，超过8层后再增加层数，则节地效果不大。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%898%E5%B1%82%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8B%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%85%E5%A2%9E%E5%8A%A0%E5%B1%82%E6%95%B0%E5%8F%AF%E8%8A%82%E7%BA%A6%E8%BE%83%E5%A4%9A%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%8C%E8%B6%85%E8%BF%878%E5%B1%82%E5%90%8E%E5%86%8D%E5%A2%9E%E5%8A%A0%E5%B1%82%E6%95%B0%EF%BC%8C%E5%88%99%E8%8A%82%E5%9C%B0%E6%95%88%E6%9E%9C%E4%B8%8D%E5%A4%A7%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（2）降低层高可降低住宅总高度，住宅的日照间距用地也相应减少。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E9%99%8D%E4%BD%8E%E5%B1%82%E9%AB%98%E5%8F%AF%E9%99%8D%E4%BD%8E%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%85%E6%80%BB%E9%AB%98%E5%BA%A6%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%85%E7%9A%84%E6%97%A5%E7%85%A7%E9%97%B4%E8%B7%9D%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E4%B9%9F%E7%9B%B8%E5%BA%94%E5%87%8F%E5%B0%91%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（3）北退台或斜屋面也可获得减少日照间距用地的效果。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E5%8C%97%E9%80%80%E5%8F%B0%E6%88%96%E6%96%9C%E5%B1%8B%E9%9D%A2%E4%B9%9F%E5%8F%AF%E8%8E%B7%E5%BE%97%E5%87%8F%E5%B0%91%E6%97%A5%E7%85%A7%E9%97%B4%E8%B7%9D%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E7%9A%84%E6%95%88%E6%9E%9C%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（4）加大进深、缩小面宽对节约用地有相当显著的作用。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%884%EF%BC%89%E5%8A%A0%E5%A4%A7%E8%BF%9B%E6%B7%B1%E3%80%81%E7%BC%A9%E5%B0%8F%E9%9D%A2%E5%AE%BD%E5%AF%B9%E8%8A%82%E7%BA%A6%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E6%9C%89%E7%9B%B8%E5%BD%93%E6%98%BE%E8%91%97%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%9C%E7%94%A8%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="2.住宅群体布置中的节地措施：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2.%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%85%E7%BE%A4%E4%BD%93%E5%B8%83%E7%BD%AE%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E8%8A%82%E5%9C%B0%E6%8E%AA%E6%96%BD%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（1）合理确定日照间距系数，在满足卫生条件的前提下，尽量采用较小的间距系数，对于节地是很有意义的。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E5%90%88%E7%90%86%E7%A1%AE%E5%AE%9A%E6%97%A5%E7%85%A7%E9%97%B4%E8%B7%9D%E7%B3%BB%E6%95%B0%EF%BC%8C%E5%9C%A8%E6%BB%A1%E8%B6%B3%E5%8D%AB%E7%94%9F%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%E7%9A%84%E5%89%8D%E6%8F%90%E4%B8%8B%EF%BC%8C%E5%B0%BD%E9%87%8F%E9%87%87%E7%94%A8%E8%BE%83%E5%B0%8F%E7%9A%84%E9%97%B4%E8%B7%9D%E7%B3%BB%E6%95%B0%EF%BC%8C%E5%AF%B9%E4%BA%8E%E8%8A%82%E5%9C%B0%E6%98%AF%E5%BE%88%E6%9C%89%E6%84%8F%E4%B9%89%E7%9A%84%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（2）适当布置东西向住宅，让房屋日照间距用地有一部分重叠，可进一步节约用地。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E9%80%82%E5%BD%93%E5%B8%83%E7%BD%AE%E4%B8%9C%E8%A5%BF%E5%90%91%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%85%EF%BC%8C%E8%AE%A9%E6%88%BF%E5%B1%8B%E6%97%A5%E7%85%A7%E9%97%B4%E8%B7%9D%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%80%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E9%87%8D%E5%8F%A0%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%AF%E8%BF%9B%E4%B8%80%E6%AD%A5%E8%8A%82%E7%BA%A6%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（3）适当布置高层塔式住宅，可显著提高土地利用率。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E9%80%82%E5%BD%93%E5%B8%83%E7%BD%AE%E9%AB%98%E5%B1%82%E5%A1%94%E5%BC%8F%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%85%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%AF%E6%98%BE%E8%91%97%E6%8F%90%E9%AB%98%E5%9C%9F%E5%9C%B0%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8%E7%8E%87%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（4）总图布置适当偏角，日照间距系数可以折减，可以节约用地。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%884%EF%BC%89%E6%80%BB%E5%9B%BE%E5%B8%83%E7%BD%AE%E9%80%82%E5%BD%93%E5%81%8F%E8%A7%92%EF%BC%8C%E6%97%A5%E7%85%A7%E9%97%B4%E8%B7%9D%E7%B3%BB%E6%95%B0%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E6%8A%98%E5%87%8F%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E8%8A%82%E7%BA%A6%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（5）在城市干道南侧布置高层，把日照间距用地纳入道路用地。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%885%EF%BC%89%E5%9C%A8%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%B9%B2%E9%81%93%E5%8D%97%E4%BE%A7%E5%B8%83%E7%BD%AE%E9%AB%98%E5%B1%82%EF%BC%8C%E6%8A%8A%E6%97%A5%E7%85%A7%E9%97%B4%E8%B7%9D%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E7%BA%B3%E5%85%A5%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（四）节约用水" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E5%9B%9B%EF%BC%89%E8%8A%82%E7%BA%A6%E7%94%A8%E6%B0%B4%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="淡水资源的匮乏已成为世界性问题，我国人均水资源的拥有量仅为世界平均水平的1/4，这是一个不容忽视的问题。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%B7%A1%E6%B0%B4%E8%B5%84%E6%BA%90%E7%9A%84%E5%8C%AE%E4%B9%8F%E5%B7%B2%E6%88%90%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E6%80%A7%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%EF%BC%8C%E6%88%91%E5%9B%BD%E4%BA%BA%E5%9D%87%E6%B0%B4%E8%B5%84%E6%BA%90%E7%9A%84%E6%8B%A5%E6%9C%89%E9%87%8F%E4%BB%85%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E5%B9%B3%E5%9D%87%E6%B0%B4%E5%B9%B3%E7%9A%841/4%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%99%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E4%B8%8D%E5%AE%B9%E5%BF%BD%E8%A7%86%E7%9A%84%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="住宅建筑中可采用如下节水措施：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%85%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E4%B8%AD%E5%8F%AF%E9%87%87%E7%94%A8%E5%A6%82%E4%B8%8B%E8%8A%82%E6%B0%B4%E6%8E%AA%E6%96%BD%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="中水利用、" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%AD%E6%B0%B4%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8%E3%80%81%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="雨水收集与利用、" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%9B%A8%E6%B0%B4%E6%94%B6%E9%9B%86%E4%B8%8E%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8%E3%80%81%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="采用节水设备（器具）、" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%87%87%E7%94%A8%E8%8A%82%E6%B0%B4%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%EF%BC%88%E5%99%A8%E5%85%B7%EF%BC%89%E3%80%81%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="节约景观用水、" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%8A%82%E7%BA%A6%E6%99%AF%E8%A7%82%E7%94%A8%E6%B0%B4%E3%80%81%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="采用循环用水等。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%87%87%E7%94%A8%E5%BE%AA%E7%8E%AF%E7%94%A8%E6%B0%B4%E7%AD%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      </outline>
    </outline>
    <outline text="" _mubu_text="" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="第三节    建筑构图原原理" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%89%E8%8A%82%20%20%20%20%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E6%9E%84%E5%9B%BE%E5%8E%9F%E5%8E%9F%E7%90%86%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="建筑的发展表现为复杂的矛盾运动形式，建筑的形式与内容是对立统一的辩证关系。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E8%A1%A8%E7%8E%B0%E4%B8%BA%E5%A4%8D%E6%9D%82%E7%9A%84%E7%9F%9B%E7%9B%BE%E8%BF%90%E5%8A%A8%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%EF%BC%8C%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E4%B8%8E%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%E6%98%AF%E5%AF%B9%E7%AB%8B%E7%BB%9F%E4%B8%80%E7%9A%84%E8%BE%A9%E8%AF%81%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="建筑发展演进的三个主导因素是：功能和使用要求、精神和审美要求，以及以必要的物质技术手段来达到前面的两个要求。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E6%BC%94%E8%BF%9B%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%89%E4%B8%AA%E4%B8%BB%E5%AF%BC%E5%9B%A0%E7%B4%A0%E6%98%AF%EF%BC%9A%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E5%92%8C%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E3%80%81%E7%B2%BE%E7%A5%9E%E5%92%8C%E5%AE%A1%E7%BE%8E%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%8A%E4%BB%A5%E5%BF%85%E8%A6%81%E7%9A%84%E7%89%A9%E8%B4%A8%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E6%89%8B%E6%AE%B5%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%BE%E5%88%B0%E5%89%8D%E9%9D%A2%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%A4%E4%B8%AA%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（一）功能与空间" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%80%EF%BC%89%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E4%B8%8E%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="建筑总是有它具体的目的和使用要求的，这在建筑中被称为“功能”，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E6%80%BB%E6%98%AF%E6%9C%89%E5%AE%83%E5%85%B7%E4%BD%93%E7%9A%84%E7%9B%AE%E7%9A%84%E5%92%8C%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E7%9A%84%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%99%E5%9C%A8%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E4%B8%AD%E8%A2%AB%E7%A7%B0%E4%B8%BA%E2%80%9C%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E2%80%9D%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="所以美国芝加哥学派的现代主义建筑大师路易斯·沙利文提出了“形式追随功能”的理念。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%89%80%E4%BB%A5%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E8%8A%9D%E5%8A%A0%E5%93%A5%E5%AD%A6%E6%B4%BE%E7%9A%84%E7%8E%B0%E4%BB%A3%E4%B8%BB%E4%B9%89%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%A4%A7%E5%B8%88%E8%B7%AF%E6%98%93%E6%96%AF%C2%B7%E6%B2%99%E5%88%A9%E6%96%87%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E4%BA%86%E2%80%9C%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E8%BF%BD%E9%9A%8F%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E2%80%9D%E7%9A%84%E7%90%86%E5%BF%B5%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="人们经常提及的“建筑形式”，是由空间、体形、轮廓、虚实、凹凸、色彩、质地、装饰等要素集合而形成的复杂的概念。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BA%BA%E4%BB%AC%E7%BB%8F%E5%B8%B8%E6%8F%90%E5%8F%8A%E7%9A%84%E2%80%9C%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E2%80%9D%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%AF%E7%94%B1%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E3%80%81%E4%BD%93%E5%BD%A2%E3%80%81%E8%BD%AE%E5%BB%93%E3%80%81%E8%99%9A%E5%AE%9E%E3%80%81%E5%87%B9%E5%87%B8%E3%80%81%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E3%80%81%E8%B4%A8%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%81%E8%A3%85%E9%A5%B0%E7%AD%89%E8%A6%81%E7%B4%A0%E9%9B%86%E5%90%88%E8%80%8C%E5%BD%A2%E6%88%90%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%8D%E6%9D%82%E7%9A%84%E6%A6%82%E5%BF%B5%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="这些要素有的和功能保持着紧密而直接的联系；有的和功能的联系并不直接、紧密；有的则几乎和功能没有联系。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%BF%99%E4%BA%9B%E8%A6%81%E7%B4%A0%E6%9C%89%E7%9A%84%E5%92%8C%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E4%BF%9D%E6%8C%81%E7%9D%80%E7%B4%A7%E5%AF%86%E8%80%8C%E7%9B%B4%E6%8E%A5%E7%9A%84%E8%81%94%E7%B3%BB%EF%BC%9B%E6%9C%89%E7%9A%84%E5%92%8C%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E7%9A%84%E8%81%94%E7%B3%BB%E5%B9%B6%E4%B8%8D%E7%9B%B4%E6%8E%A5%E3%80%81%E7%B4%A7%E5%AF%86%EF%BC%9B%E6%9C%89%E7%9A%84%E5%88%99%E5%87%A0%E4%B9%8E%E5%92%8C%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E6%B2%A1%E6%9C%89%E8%81%94%E7%B3%BB%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="基于这一事实，我们不能笼统地认为一切形式均来自功能。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%BA%E4%BA%8E%E8%BF%99%E4%B8%80%E4%BA%8B%E5%AE%9E%EF%BC%8C%E6%88%91%E4%BB%AC%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E7%AC%BC%E7%BB%9F%E5%9C%B0%E8%AE%A4%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%80%E5%88%87%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E5%9D%87%E6%9D%A5%E8%87%AA%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="1.功能对空间形式的规定性" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1.%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E5%AF%B9%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%84%E5%AE%9A%E6%80%A7%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="容器有盛放物品的功能；反过来，这一功能对容器的空间形式也具有以下三个方面的规定性：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%AE%B9%E5%99%A8%E6%9C%89%E7%9B%9B%E6%94%BE%E7%89%A9%E5%93%81%E7%9A%84%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%EF%BC%9B%E5%8F%8D%E8%BF%87%E6%9D%A5%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%99%E4%B8%80%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E5%AF%B9%E5%AE%B9%E5%99%A8%E7%9A%84%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E4%B9%9F%E5%85%B7%E6%9C%89%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8B%E4%B8%89%E4%B8%AA%E6%96%B9%E9%9D%A2%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%84%E5%AE%9A%E6%80%A7%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（1）量的规定性：具有合适的大小和容量，足以容纳物品。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E9%87%8F%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%84%E5%AE%9A%E6%80%A7%EF%BC%9A%E5%85%B7%E6%9C%89%E5%90%88%E9%80%82%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%A7%E5%B0%8F%E5%92%8C%E5%AE%B9%E9%87%8F%EF%BC%8C%E8%B6%B3%E4%BB%A5%E5%AE%B9%E7%BA%B3%E7%89%A9%E5%93%81%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（2）形的规定性：具有合适的形状以适应所盛放的特定物品。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E5%BD%A2%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%84%E5%AE%9A%E6%80%A7%EF%BC%9A%E5%85%B7%E6%9C%89%E5%90%88%E9%80%82%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%A2%E7%8A%B6%E4%BB%A5%E9%80%82%E5%BA%94%E6%89%80%E7%9B%9B%E6%94%BE%E7%9A%84%E7%89%B9%E5%AE%9A%E7%89%A9%E5%93%81%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（3）质的规定性：所围合的空间具有适当的物理条件，如温、湿度等，以防止物品受到损害或变质。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E8%B4%A8%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%84%E5%AE%9A%E6%80%A7%EF%BC%9A%E6%89%80%E5%9B%B4%E5%90%88%E7%9A%84%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E5%85%B7%E6%9C%89%E9%80%82%E5%BD%93%E7%9A%84%E7%89%A9%E7%90%86%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%EF%BC%8C%E5%A6%82%E6%B8%A9%E3%80%81%E6%B9%BF%E5%BA%A6%E7%AD%89%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A5%E9%98%B2%E6%AD%A2%E7%89%A9%E5%93%81%E5%8F%97%E5%88%B0%E6%8D%9F%E5%AE%B3%E6%88%96%E5%8F%98%E8%B4%A8%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="2.功能对于单一空间形式的规定性" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2.%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E5%AF%B9%E4%BA%8E%E5%8D%95%E4%B8%80%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%84%E5%AE%9A%E6%80%A7%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="房间是组成建筑最基本的单位，它通常是以单一空间的形式存在的。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%88%BF%E9%97%B4%E6%98%AF%E7%BB%84%E6%88%90%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E6%9C%80%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%95%E4%BD%8D%EF%BC%8C%E5%AE%83%E9%80%9A%E5%B8%B8%E6%98%AF%E4%BB%A5%E5%8D%95%E4%B8%80%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E5%AD%98%E5%9C%A8%E7%9A%84%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="不同性质的房间，具有不同的空间形式。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E6%80%A7%E8%B4%A8%E7%9A%84%E6%88%BF%E9%97%B4%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%B7%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E7%9A%84%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="如果把“房间或厅堂”看成是容器，它盛放的是人或人们的活动，那么它也必须具有上述三个方面的规定性。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%A6%82%E6%9E%9C%E6%8A%8A%E2%80%9C%E6%88%BF%E9%97%B4%E6%88%96%E5%8E%85%E5%A0%82%E2%80%9D%E7%9C%8B%E6%88%90%E6%98%AF%E5%AE%B9%E5%99%A8%EF%BC%8C%E5%AE%83%E7%9B%9B%E6%94%BE%E7%9A%84%E6%98%AF%E4%BA%BA%E6%88%96%E4%BA%BA%E4%BB%AC%E7%9A%84%E6%B4%BB%E5%8A%A8%EF%BC%8C%E9%82%A3%E4%B9%88%E5%AE%83%E4%B9%9F%E5%BF%85%E9%A1%BB%E5%85%B7%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%8A%E8%BF%B0%E4%B8%89%E4%B8%AA%E6%96%B9%E9%9D%A2%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%84%E5%AE%9A%E6%80%A7%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="3.功能对于多空间组合形式的规定性" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E3.%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E5%AF%B9%E4%BA%8E%E5%A4%9A%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E7%BB%84%E5%90%88%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%84%E5%AE%9A%E6%80%A7%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="空间组合形式是千变万化的，但是不论这种变化是何等复杂，它终究要反映不同功能联系的特点。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E7%BB%84%E5%90%88%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E6%98%AF%E5%8D%83%E5%8F%98%E4%B8%87%E5%8C%96%E7%9A%84%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%86%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%8D%E8%AE%BA%E8%BF%99%E7%A7%8D%E5%8F%98%E5%8C%96%E6%98%AF%E4%BD%95%E7%AD%89%E5%A4%8D%E6%9D%82%EF%BC%8C%E5%AE%83%E7%BB%88%E7%A9%B6%E8%A6%81%E5%8F%8D%E6%98%A0%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E8%81%94%E7%B3%BB%E7%9A%84%E7%89%B9%E7%82%B9%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="基于此，可以概括出下列5种具有典型意义的空间组合形式：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%BA%E4%BA%8E%E6%AD%A4%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E6%A6%82%E6%8B%AC%E5%87%BA%E4%B8%8B%E5%88%975%E7%A7%8D%E5%85%B7%E6%9C%89%E5%85%B8%E5%9E%8B%E6%84%8F%E4%B9%89%E7%9A%84%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E7%BB%84%E5%90%88%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（1）用“走道”来连接各使用空间。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E7%94%A8%E2%80%9C%E8%B5%B0%E9%81%93%E2%80%9D%E6%9D%A5%E8%BF%9E%E6%8E%A5%E5%90%84%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（2）各使用空间围绕着“楼梯”来布置。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E5%90%84%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E5%9B%B4%E7%BB%95%E7%9D%80%E2%80%9C%E6%A5%BC%E6%A2%AF%E2%80%9D%E6%9D%A5%E5%B8%83%E7%BD%AE%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（3）以“广厅”直接连接各使用空间。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E4%BB%A5%E2%80%9C%E5%B9%BF%E5%8E%85%E2%80%9D%E7%9B%B4%E6%8E%A5%E8%BF%9E%E6%8E%A5%E5%90%84%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（4）各使用空间互相串联套，直接连通。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%884%EF%BC%89%E5%90%84%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E4%BA%92%E7%9B%B8%E4%B8%B2%E8%81%94%E5%A5%97%EF%BC%8C%E7%9B%B4%E6%8E%A5%E8%BF%9E%E9%80%9A%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（5）以大空间为中心，周围环绕小空间。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%885%EF%BC%89%E4%BB%A5%E5%A4%A7%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%EF%BC%8C%E5%91%A8%E5%9B%B4%E7%8E%AF%E7%BB%95%E5%B0%8F%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（二）空间与结构" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%BA%8C%EF%BC%89%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E4%B8%8E%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="建筑空间，是人们凭借着一定的物质材料，从自然空间中围隔出来的一—由原来的自然空间变为人造空间。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%AF%E4%BA%BA%E4%BB%AC%E5%87%AD%E5%80%9F%E7%9D%80%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%9A%E7%9A%84%E7%89%A9%E8%B4%A8%E6%9D%90%E6%96%99%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%8E%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%B4%E9%9A%94%E5%87%BA%E6%9D%A5%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%80%E2%80%94%E7%94%B1%E5%8E%9F%E6%9D%A5%E7%9A%84%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E5%8F%98%E4%B8%BA%E4%BA%BA%E9%80%A0%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="所围隔的空间必须具有确定的量（大小、容积）、确定的形（形状）、确定的质（能避风雨、御寒暑、可通风采光等）。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%89%80%E5%9B%B4%E9%9A%94%E7%9A%84%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E5%BF%85%E9%A1%BB%E5%85%B7%E6%9C%89%E7%A1%AE%E5%AE%9A%E7%9A%84%E9%87%8F%EF%BC%88%E5%A4%A7%E5%B0%8F%E3%80%81%E5%AE%B9%E7%A7%AF%EF%BC%89%E3%80%81%E7%A1%AE%E5%AE%9A%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%A2%EF%BC%88%E5%BD%A2%E7%8A%B6%EF%BC%89%E3%80%81%E7%A1%AE%E5%AE%9A%E7%9A%84%E8%B4%A8%EF%BC%88%E8%83%BD%E9%81%BF%E9%A3%8E%E9%9B%A8%E3%80%81%E5%BE%A1%E5%AF%92%E6%9A%91%E3%80%81%E5%8F%AF%E9%80%9A%E9%A3%8E%E9%87%87%E5%85%89%E7%AD%89%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="空间可分为：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E5%8F%AF%E5%88%86%E4%B8%BA%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="符合使用功能的适用空间、" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%AC%A6%E5%90%88%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E7%9A%84%E9%80%82%E7%94%A8%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E3%80%81%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="符合审美要求的视觉空间、" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%AC%A6%E5%90%88%E5%AE%A1%E7%BE%8E%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%86%E8%A7%89%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E3%80%81%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="符合材料性能和力学规律的结构空间。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%AC%A6%E5%90%88%E6%9D%90%E6%96%99%E6%80%A7%E8%83%BD%E5%92%8C%E5%8A%9B%E5%AD%A6%E8%A7%84%E5%BE%8B%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      </outline>
    </outline>
    <outline text="不同的结构形式不仅能适应不同的功能要求，而且也各具独特的表现力。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E4%B8%8D%E4%BB%85%E8%83%BD%E9%80%82%E5%BA%94%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E7%9A%84%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%EF%BC%8C%E8%80%8C%E4%B8%94%E4%B9%9F%E5%90%84%E5%85%B7%E7%8B%AC%E7%89%B9%E7%9A%84%E8%A1%A8%E7%8E%B0%E5%8A%9B%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="美籍芬兰裔建筑师埃罗·沙里宁认为“每一个时代都是用它当代的技术来创造自己的建筑。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%BE%8E%E7%B1%8D%E8%8A%AC%E5%85%B0%E8%A3%94%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%88%E5%9F%83%E7%BD%97%C2%B7%E6%B2%99%E9%87%8C%E5%AE%81%E8%AE%A4%E4%B8%BA%E2%80%9C%E6%AF%8F%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E6%97%B6%E4%BB%A3%E9%83%BD%E6%98%AF%E7%94%A8%E5%AE%83%E5%BD%93%E4%BB%A3%E7%9A%84%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E6%9D%A5%E5%88%9B%E9%80%A0%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="但是没有任何一个时代拥有过像我们现在处理建筑上所拥有的这样神奇的技术”。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BD%86%E6%98%AF%E6%B2%A1%E6%9C%89%E4%BB%BB%E4%BD%95%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E6%97%B6%E4%BB%A3%E6%8B%A5%E6%9C%89%E8%BF%87%E5%83%8F%E6%88%91%E4%BB%AC%E7%8E%B0%E5%9C%A8%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E4%B8%8A%E6%89%80%E6%8B%A5%E6%9C%89%E7%9A%84%E8%BF%99%E6%A0%B7%E7%A5%9E%E5%A5%87%E7%9A%84%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E2%80%9D%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（1）以墙和柱承重的梁板结构体系。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E4%BB%A5%E5%A2%99%E5%92%8C%E6%9F%B1%E6%89%BF%E9%87%8D%E7%9A%84%E6%A2%81%E6%9D%BF%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E4%BD%93%E7%B3%BB%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（2）框架结构体系。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E6%A1%86%E6%9E%B6%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E4%BD%93%E7%B3%BB%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（3）大跨度结构体系。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E5%A4%A7%E8%B7%A8%E5%BA%A6%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E4%BD%93%E7%B3%BB%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（4）悬挑结构体系。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%884%EF%BC%89%E6%82%AC%E6%8C%91%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E4%BD%93%E7%B3%BB%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（5）其他结构体系（剪力墙、井筒、充气结构等）。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%885%EF%BC%89%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E4%BD%93%E7%B3%BB%EF%BC%88%E5%89%AA%E5%8A%9B%E5%A2%99%E3%80%81%E4%BA%95%E7%AD%92%E3%80%81%E5%85%85%E6%B0%94%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E7%AD%89%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（三）形式美的原则" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%89%EF%BC%89%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E7%BE%8E%E7%9A%84%E5%8E%9F%E5%88%99%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="1.形式美的原则——多样统一" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1.%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E7%BE%8E%E7%9A%84%E5%8E%9F%E5%88%99%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E5%A4%9A%E6%A0%B7%E7%BB%9F%E4%B8%80%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="古今中外的建筑，尽管在形式处理方面有极大差别，但凡属优秀作品，必然遵循一个共同的准则——多样统一。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%8F%A4%E4%BB%8A%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%96%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%EF%BC%8C%E5%B0%BD%E7%AE%A1%E5%9C%A8%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86%E6%96%B9%E9%9D%A2%E6%9C%89%E6%9E%81%E5%A4%A7%E5%B7%AE%E5%88%AB%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%86%E5%87%A1%E5%B1%9E%E4%BC%98%E7%A7%80%E4%BD%9C%E5%93%81%EF%BC%8C%E5%BF%85%E7%84%B6%E9%81%B5%E5%BE%AA%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E5%85%B1%E5%90%8C%E7%9A%84%E5%87%86%E5%88%99%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E5%A4%9A%E6%A0%B7%E7%BB%9F%E4%B8%80%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="多样统一，也称有机统一，也就是在统一中求变化，在变化中求统一。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%A4%9A%E6%A0%B7%E7%BB%9F%E4%B8%80%EF%BC%8C%E4%B9%9F%E7%A7%B0%E6%9C%89%E6%9C%BA%E7%BB%9F%E4%B8%80%EF%BC%8C%E4%B9%9F%E5%B0%B1%E6%98%AF%E5%9C%A8%E7%BB%9F%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AD%E6%B1%82%E5%8F%98%E5%8C%96%EF%BC%8C%E5%9C%A8%E5%8F%98%E5%8C%96%E4%B8%AD%E6%B1%82%E7%BB%9F%E4%B8%80%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="强调有秩序的变化。应当指出“形式美的原则”与“审美观念”是两种不同范畴；前者是绝对的，后者是相对的。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%BC%BA%E8%B0%83%E6%9C%89%E7%A7%A9%E5%BA%8F%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%98%E5%8C%96%E3%80%82%E5%BA%94%E5%BD%93%E6%8C%87%E5%87%BA%E2%80%9C%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E7%BE%8E%E7%9A%84%E5%8E%9F%E5%88%99%E2%80%9D%E4%B8%8E%E2%80%9C%E5%AE%A1%E7%BE%8E%E8%A7%82%E5%BF%B5%E2%80%9D%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%A4%E7%A7%8D%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E8%8C%83%E7%95%B4%EF%BC%9B%E5%89%8D%E8%80%85%E6%98%AF%E7%BB%9D%E5%AF%B9%E7%9A%84%EF%BC%8C%E5%90%8E%E8%80%85%E6%98%AF%E7%9B%B8%E5%AF%B9%E7%9A%84%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="2.形式美的若干基本范畴" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2.%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E7%BE%8E%E7%9A%84%E8%8B%A5%E5%B9%B2%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E8%8C%83%E7%95%B4%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（1）以简单的几何形状求统一" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E4%BB%A5%E7%AE%80%E5%8D%95%E7%9A%84%E5%87%A0%E4%BD%95%E5%BD%A2%E7%8A%B6%E6%B1%82%E7%BB%9F%E4%B8%80%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="古代美学家认为，简单、肯定的几何形状可以引起人的美感。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%8F%A4%E4%BB%A3%E7%BE%8E%E5%AD%A6%E5%AE%B6%E8%AE%A4%E4%B8%BA%EF%BC%8C%E7%AE%80%E5%8D%95%E3%80%81%E8%82%AF%E5%AE%9A%E7%9A%84%E5%87%A0%E4%BD%95%E5%BD%A2%E7%8A%B6%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E5%BC%95%E8%B5%B7%E4%BA%BA%E7%9A%84%E7%BE%8E%E6%84%9F%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="现代建筑大师勒·柯布西耶也强调：“原始的体形是美的体形，因为它能使我们清晰地辨认。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%8E%B0%E4%BB%A3%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%A4%A7%E5%B8%88%E5%8B%92%C2%B7%E6%9F%AF%E5%B8%83%E8%A5%BF%E8%80%B6%E4%B9%9F%E5%BC%BA%E8%B0%83%EF%BC%9A%E2%80%9C%E5%8E%9F%E5%A7%8B%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%93%E5%BD%A2%E6%98%AF%E7%BE%8E%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%93%E5%BD%A2%EF%BC%8C%E5%9B%A0%E4%B8%BA%E5%AE%83%E8%83%BD%E4%BD%BF%E6%88%91%E4%BB%AC%E6%B8%85%E6%99%B0%E5%9C%B0%E8%BE%A8%E8%AE%A4%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="”这些观点可以从古今中外的许多建筑实例中得到证实。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D%E8%BF%99%E4%BA%9B%E8%A7%82%E7%82%B9%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E4%BB%8E%E5%8F%A4%E4%BB%8A%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%96%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%B8%E5%A4%9A%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%AE%9E%E4%BE%8B%E4%B8%AD%E5%BE%97%E5%88%B0%E8%AF%81%E5%AE%9E%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（2）主从与重点" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E4%B8%BB%E4%BB%8E%E4%B8%8E%E9%87%8D%E7%82%B9%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="在由若干要素组成的整体中，每一要素在整体中所占的比重和所处的地位，将会影响到整体的统一性。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9C%A8%E7%94%B1%E8%8B%A5%E5%B9%B2%E8%A6%81%E7%B4%A0%E7%BB%84%E6%88%90%E7%9A%84%E6%95%B4%E4%BD%93%E4%B8%AD%EF%BC%8C%E6%AF%8F%E4%B8%80%E8%A6%81%E7%B4%A0%E5%9C%A8%E6%95%B4%E4%BD%93%E4%B8%AD%E6%89%80%E5%8D%A0%E7%9A%84%E6%AF%94%E9%87%8D%E5%92%8C%E6%89%80%E5%A4%84%E7%9A%84%E5%9C%B0%E4%BD%8D%EF%BC%8C%E5%B0%86%E4%BC%9A%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%E5%88%B0%E6%95%B4%E4%BD%93%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%9F%E4%B8%80%E6%80%A7%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="倘使所有要素都竞相突出自己，或者都处于同等重要地位，不分主次，就会削弱整体的完整统一性。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%80%98%E4%BD%BF%E6%89%80%E6%9C%89%E8%A6%81%E7%B4%A0%E9%83%BD%E7%AB%9E%E7%9B%B8%E7%AA%81%E5%87%BA%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%EF%BC%8C%E6%88%96%E8%80%85%E9%83%BD%E5%A4%84%E4%BA%8E%E5%90%8C%E7%AD%89%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81%E5%9C%B0%E4%BD%8D%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8D%E5%88%86%E4%B8%BB%E6%AC%A1%EF%BC%8C%E5%B0%B1%E4%BC%9A%E5%89%8A%E5%BC%B1%E6%95%B4%E4%BD%93%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%8C%E6%95%B4%E7%BB%9F%E4%B8%80%E6%80%A7%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="在一个有机统一体中，各组成部分应当有主与从的差别；有重点与一般的差别；有核心与外围组织的差别。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9C%A8%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E6%9C%89%E6%9C%BA%E7%BB%9F%E4%B8%80%E4%BD%93%E4%B8%AD%EF%BC%8C%E5%90%84%E7%BB%84%E6%88%90%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E5%BA%94%E5%BD%93%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%BB%E4%B8%8E%E4%BB%8E%E7%9A%84%E5%B7%AE%E5%88%AB%EF%BC%9B%E6%9C%89%E9%87%8D%E7%82%B9%E4%B8%8E%E4%B8%80%E8%88%AC%E7%9A%84%E5%B7%AE%E5%88%AB%EF%BC%9B%E6%9C%89%E6%A0%B8%E5%BF%83%E4%B8%8E%E5%A4%96%E5%9B%B4%E7%BB%84%E7%BB%87%E7%9A%84%E5%B7%AE%E5%88%AB%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="否则难免流于松散、单调而失去统一。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%90%A6%E5%88%99%E9%9A%BE%E5%85%8D%E6%B5%81%E4%BA%8E%E6%9D%BE%E6%95%A3%E3%80%81%E5%8D%95%E8%B0%83%E8%80%8C%E5%A4%B1%E5%8E%BB%E7%BB%9F%E4%B8%80%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（3）均衡与稳定" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E5%9D%87%E8%A1%A1%E4%B8%8E%E7%A8%B3%E5%AE%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="人类从与重力做斗争的实践中逐渐形成一整套与重力有联系的审美观念，这就是均衡与稳定。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BA%BA%E7%B1%BB%E4%BB%8E%E4%B8%8E%E9%87%8D%E5%8A%9B%E5%81%9A%E6%96%97%E4%BA%89%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%9E%E8%B7%B5%E4%B8%AD%E9%80%90%E6%B8%90%E5%BD%A2%E6%88%90%E4%B8%80%E6%95%B4%E5%A5%97%E4%B8%8E%E9%87%8D%E5%8A%9B%E6%9C%89%E8%81%94%E7%B3%BB%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%A1%E7%BE%8E%E8%A7%82%E5%BF%B5%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%99%E5%B0%B1%E6%98%AF%E5%9D%87%E8%A1%A1%E4%B8%8E%E7%A8%B3%E5%AE%9A%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="对称的形式天然就是均衡的，但也可以用不对称的形式来保持均衡。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%AF%B9%E7%A7%B0%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E5%A4%A9%E7%84%B6%E5%B0%B1%E6%98%AF%E5%9D%87%E8%A1%A1%E7%9A%84%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%86%E4%B9%9F%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E7%94%A8%E4%B8%8D%E5%AF%B9%E7%A7%B0%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E6%9D%A5%E4%BF%9D%E6%8C%81%E5%9D%87%E8%A1%A1%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="除了静态的均衡外，也可依靠运动来求得平衡，这种形式的均衡称为动态均衡。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%99%A4%E4%BA%86%E9%9D%99%E6%80%81%E7%9A%84%E5%9D%87%E8%A1%A1%E5%A4%96%EF%BC%8C%E4%B9%9F%E5%8F%AF%E4%BE%9D%E9%9D%A0%E8%BF%90%E5%8A%A8%E6%9D%A5%E6%B1%82%E5%BE%97%E5%B9%B3%E8%A1%A1%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%99%E7%A7%8D%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E7%9A%84%E5%9D%87%E8%A1%A1%E7%A7%B0%E4%B8%BA%E5%8A%A8%E6%80%81%E5%9D%87%E8%A1%A1%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="古典建筑的设计思想更多的是从静态均衡的角度来考虑问题，近现代建筑师还往往用动态均衡的观点来考虑问题。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%8F%A4%E5%85%B8%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E6%80%9D%E6%83%B3%E6%9B%B4%E5%A4%9A%E7%9A%84%E6%98%AF%E4%BB%8E%E9%9D%99%E6%80%81%E5%9D%87%E8%A1%A1%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%92%E5%BA%A6%E6%9D%A5%E8%80%83%E8%99%91%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%91%E7%8E%B0%E4%BB%A3%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%88%E8%BF%98%E5%BE%80%E5%BE%80%E7%94%A8%E5%8A%A8%E6%80%81%E5%9D%87%E8%A1%A1%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%82%E7%82%B9%E6%9D%A5%E8%80%83%E8%99%91%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="和均衡相关联的是稳定。均衡所涉及的主要是建筑构图中各要素左与右、前与后之间相对轻重关系的处理，稳定所涉及的则是建筑整体上下轻重关系的处理。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%92%8C%E5%9D%87%E8%A1%A1%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3%E8%81%94%E7%9A%84%E6%98%AF%E7%A8%B3%E5%AE%9A%E3%80%82%E5%9D%87%E8%A1%A1%E6%89%80%E6%B6%89%E5%8F%8A%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E6%98%AF%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E6%9E%84%E5%9B%BE%E4%B8%AD%E5%90%84%E8%A6%81%E7%B4%A0%E5%B7%A6%E4%B8%8E%E5%8F%B3%E3%80%81%E5%89%8D%E4%B8%8E%E5%90%8E%E4%B9%8B%E9%97%B4%E7%9B%B8%E5%AF%B9%E8%BD%BB%E9%87%8D%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86%EF%BC%8C%E7%A8%B3%E5%AE%9A%E6%89%80%E6%B6%89%E5%8F%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%88%99%E6%98%AF%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E6%95%B4%E4%BD%93%E4%B8%8A%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BB%E9%87%8D%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（4）对比与微差" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%884%EF%BC%89%E5%AF%B9%E6%AF%94%E4%B8%8E%E5%BE%AE%E5%B7%AE%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="建筑功能和技术赋予建筑以各种形式上的差异性。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E5%92%8C%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E8%B5%8B%E4%BA%88%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E4%BB%A5%E5%90%84%E7%A7%8D%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%B7%AE%E5%BC%82%E6%80%A7%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="对比与微差研究的是如何利用这些差异性来求得建筑形式上的完美统一。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%AF%B9%E6%AF%94%E4%B8%8E%E5%BE%AE%E5%B7%AE%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E7%9A%84%E6%98%AF%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8%E8%BF%99%E4%BA%9B%E5%B7%AE%E5%BC%82%E6%80%A7%E6%9D%A5%E6%B1%82%E5%BE%97%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%8C%E7%BE%8E%E7%BB%9F%E4%B8%80%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="对比指的是要素之间显著的差异，微差指的是不显著的差异。就形式美而言，两者都是不可缺少的。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%AF%B9%E6%AF%94%E6%8C%87%E7%9A%84%E6%98%AF%E8%A6%81%E7%B4%A0%E4%B9%8B%E9%97%B4%E6%98%BE%E8%91%97%E7%9A%84%E5%B7%AE%E5%BC%82%EF%BC%8C%E5%BE%AE%E5%B7%AE%E6%8C%87%E7%9A%84%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%BE%E8%91%97%E7%9A%84%E5%B7%AE%E5%BC%82%E3%80%82%E5%B0%B1%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E7%BE%8E%E8%80%8C%E8%A8%80%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%A4%E8%80%85%E9%83%BD%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%AF%E7%BC%BA%E5%B0%91%E7%9A%84%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="对比可以借彼此之间的烘托陪衬来突出各自的特点以求得变化，微差则可以借助相互之间的共同性以求得和谐。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%AF%B9%E6%AF%94%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E5%80%9F%E5%BD%BC%E6%AD%A4%E4%B9%8B%E9%97%B4%E7%9A%84%E7%83%98%E6%89%98%E9%99%AA%E8%A1%AC%E6%9D%A5%E7%AA%81%E5%87%BA%E5%90%84%E8%87%AA%E7%9A%84%E7%89%B9%E7%82%B9%E4%BB%A5%E6%B1%82%E5%BE%97%E5%8F%98%E5%8C%96%EF%BC%8C%E5%BE%AE%E5%B7%AE%E5%88%99%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E5%80%9F%E5%8A%A9%E7%9B%B8%E4%BA%92%E4%B9%8B%E9%97%B4%E7%9A%84%E5%85%B1%E5%90%8C%E6%80%A7%E4%BB%A5%E6%B1%82%E5%BE%97%E5%92%8C%E8%B0%90%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="对比和微差只限于同一性质的差异之间。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%AF%B9%E6%AF%94%E5%92%8C%E5%BE%AE%E5%B7%AE%E5%8F%AA%E9%99%90%E4%BA%8E%E5%90%8C%E4%B8%80%E6%80%A7%E8%B4%A8%E7%9A%84%E5%B7%AE%E5%BC%82%E4%B9%8B%E9%97%B4%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（5）韵律与节奏" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%885%EF%BC%89%E9%9F%B5%E5%BE%8B%E4%B8%8E%E8%8A%82%E5%A5%8F%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="爱好节奏和谐之类的美的形式是人类生来就有的自然倾向。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%88%B1%E5%A5%BD%E8%8A%82%E5%A5%8F%E5%92%8C%E8%B0%90%E4%B9%8B%E7%B1%BB%E7%9A%84%E7%BE%8E%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E6%98%AF%E4%BA%BA%E7%B1%BB%E7%94%9F%E6%9D%A5%E5%B0%B1%E6%9C%89%E7%9A%84%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6%E5%80%BE%E5%90%91%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="韵律美是一种以具有条理性、重复性和连续性为特征的美的形式。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%9F%B5%E5%BE%8B%E7%BE%8E%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%80%E7%A7%8D%E4%BB%A5%E5%85%B7%E6%9C%89%E6%9D%A1%E7%90%86%E6%80%A7%E3%80%81%E9%87%8D%E5%A4%8D%E6%80%A7%E5%92%8C%E8%BF%9E%E7%BB%AD%E6%80%A7%E4%B8%BA%E7%89%B9%E5%BE%81%E7%9A%84%E7%BE%8E%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="韵律美有几种不同的类型：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%9F%B5%E5%BE%8B%E7%BE%8E%E6%9C%89%E5%87%A0%E7%A7%8D%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E7%9A%84%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="①连续的韵律；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E2%91%A0%E8%BF%9E%E7%BB%AD%E7%9A%84%E9%9F%B5%E5%BE%8B%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="②渐变韵律；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E2%91%A1%E6%B8%90%E5%8F%98%E9%9F%B5%E5%BE%8B%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="③起伏韵律；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E2%91%A2%E8%B5%B7%E4%BC%8F%E9%9F%B5%E5%BE%8B%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="④交错韵律。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E2%91%A3%E4%BA%A4%E9%94%99%E9%9F%B5%E5%BE%8B%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      </outline>
      <outline text="借助韵律，既可加强整体的统一性，又可以求得丰富多彩的变化。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%80%9F%E5%8A%A9%E9%9F%B5%E5%BE%8B%EF%BC%8C%E6%97%A2%E5%8F%AF%E5%8A%A0%E5%BC%BA%E6%95%B4%E4%BD%93%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%9F%E4%B8%80%E6%80%A7%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%88%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E6%B1%82%E5%BE%97%E4%B8%B0%E5%AF%8C%E5%A4%9A%E5%BD%A9%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%98%E5%8C%96%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（6）比例与尺度" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%886%EF%BC%89%E6%AF%94%E4%BE%8B%E4%B8%8E%E5%B0%BA%E5%BA%A6%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="比例研究的是物体长、宽、高三个方向量度之间关系的问题。和谐的比例可以产生美感。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%AF%94%E4%BE%8B%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E7%9A%84%E6%98%AF%E7%89%A9%E4%BD%93%E9%95%BF%E3%80%81%E5%AE%BD%E3%80%81%E9%AB%98%E4%B8%89%E4%B8%AA%E6%96%B9%E5%90%91%E9%87%8F%E5%BA%A6%E4%B9%8B%E9%97%B4%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%E7%9A%84%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E3%80%82%E5%92%8C%E8%B0%90%E7%9A%84%E6%AF%94%E4%BE%8B%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E4%BA%A7%E7%94%9F%E7%BE%8E%E6%84%9F%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="怎样才能获得和谐的比例，人类至今并无统一的看法。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%80%8E%E6%A0%B7%E6%89%8D%E8%83%BD%E8%8E%B7%E5%BE%97%E5%92%8C%E8%B0%90%E7%9A%84%E6%AF%94%E4%BE%8B%EF%BC%8C%E4%BA%BA%E7%B1%BB%E8%87%B3%E4%BB%8A%E5%B9%B6%E6%97%A0%E7%BB%9F%E4%B8%80%E7%9A%84%E7%9C%8B%E6%B3%95%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="有人用圆、正方形、正三角形等具有定量制约关系的几何图形作为判别比例关系的标准；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%86%E3%80%81%E6%AD%A3%E6%96%B9%E5%BD%A2%E3%80%81%E6%AD%A3%E4%B8%89%E8%A7%92%E5%BD%A2%E7%AD%89%E5%85%B7%E6%9C%89%E5%AE%9A%E9%87%8F%E5%88%B6%E7%BA%A6%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%E7%9A%84%E5%87%A0%E4%BD%95%E5%9B%BE%E5%BD%A2%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%BA%E5%88%A4%E5%88%AB%E6%AF%94%E4%BE%8B%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%E7%9A%84%E6%A0%87%E5%87%86%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="至于长方形的比例，有人提出1：1.618的“黄金分割”或称“黄金比”；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%87%B3%E4%BA%8E%E9%95%BF%E6%96%B9%E5%BD%A2%E7%9A%84%E6%AF%94%E4%BE%8B%EF%BC%8C%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%BA%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA1%EF%BC%9A1.618%E7%9A%84%E2%80%9C%E9%BB%84%E9%87%91%E5%88%86%E5%89%B2%E2%80%9D%E6%88%96%E7%A7%B0%E2%80%9C%E9%BB%84%E9%87%91%E6%AF%94%E2%80%9D%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="现代建筑师勒·柯布西耶把比例和人体尺度结合起来，提出一种独特的“模度”体系。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%8E%B0%E4%BB%A3%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%88%E5%8B%92%C2%B7%E6%9F%AF%E5%B8%83%E8%A5%BF%E8%80%B6%E6%8A%8A%E6%AF%94%E4%BE%8B%E5%92%8C%E4%BA%BA%E4%BD%93%E5%B0%BA%E5%BA%A6%E7%BB%93%E5%90%88%E8%B5%B7%E6%9D%A5%EF%BC%8C%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E4%B8%80%E7%A7%8D%E7%8B%AC%E7%89%B9%E7%9A%84%E2%80%9C%E6%A8%A1%E5%BA%A6%E2%80%9D%E4%BD%93%E7%B3%BB%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="毕达哥拉斯学派（亦称南意大利学派）最早发现了“黄金分割”规律。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%AF%95%E8%BE%BE%E5%93%A5%E6%8B%89%E6%96%AF%E5%AD%A6%E6%B4%BE%EF%BC%88%E4%BA%A6%E7%A7%B0%E5%8D%97%E6%84%8F%E5%A4%A7%E5%88%A9%E5%AD%A6%E6%B4%BE%EF%BC%89%E6%9C%80%E6%97%A9%E5%8F%91%E7%8E%B0%E4%BA%86%E2%80%9C%E9%BB%84%E9%87%91%E5%88%86%E5%89%B2%E2%80%9D%E8%A7%84%E5%BE%8B%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="然而，还不能仅从形式本身来判别怎样的比例才能产生美的效果。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%84%B6%E8%80%8C%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%98%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E4%BB%85%E4%BB%8E%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E6%9C%AC%E8%BA%AB%E6%9D%A5%E5%88%A4%E5%88%AB%E6%80%8E%E6%A0%B7%E7%9A%84%E6%AF%94%E4%BE%8B%E6%89%8D%E8%83%BD%E4%BA%A7%E7%94%9F%E7%BE%8E%E7%9A%84%E6%95%88%E6%9E%9C%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="脱离材料的力学性能而追求一种绝对的、抽象的比例是荒唐的。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%84%B1%E7%A6%BB%E6%9D%90%E6%96%99%E7%9A%84%E5%8A%9B%E5%AD%A6%E6%80%A7%E8%83%BD%E8%80%8C%E8%BF%BD%E6%B1%82%E4%B8%80%E7%A7%8D%E7%BB%9D%E5%AF%B9%E7%9A%84%E3%80%81%E6%8A%BD%E8%B1%A1%E7%9A%84%E6%AF%94%E4%BE%8B%E6%98%AF%E8%8D%92%E5%94%90%E7%9A%84%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="良好的比例一定要正确反映事物内在的逻辑性。功能对于比例的影响也不容忽视。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%89%AF%E5%A5%BD%E7%9A%84%E6%AF%94%E4%BE%8B%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%9A%E8%A6%81%E6%AD%A3%E7%A1%AE%E5%8F%8D%E6%98%A0%E4%BA%8B%E7%89%A9%E5%86%85%E5%9C%A8%E7%9A%84%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91%E6%80%A7%E3%80%82%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E5%AF%B9%E4%BA%8E%E6%AF%94%E4%BE%8B%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%E4%B9%9F%E4%B8%8D%E5%AE%B9%E5%BF%BD%E8%A7%86%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="美不能离开目的性，“美”和“善”是不可分割的。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%BE%8E%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E7%A6%BB%E5%BC%80%E7%9B%AE%E7%9A%84%E6%80%A7%EF%BC%8C%E2%80%9C%E7%BE%8E%E2%80%9D%E5%92%8C%E2%80%9C%E5%96%84%E2%80%9D%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%AF%E5%88%86%E5%89%B2%E7%9A%84%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="不同的民族由于文化传统的不同，往往也会创造出独特的比例形式。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E7%9A%84%E6%B0%91%E6%97%8F%E7%94%B1%E4%BA%8E%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96%E4%BC%A0%E7%BB%9F%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%EF%BC%8C%E5%BE%80%E5%BE%80%E4%B9%9F%E4%BC%9A%E5%88%9B%E9%80%A0%E5%87%BA%E7%8B%AC%E7%89%B9%E7%9A%84%E6%AF%94%E4%BE%8B%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="构成良好比例的因素是极其复杂的，既有绝对的一面，又有相对的一面，企图找到一个放在任何地方都适合的，绝对美的比例，事实上是办不到的。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%9E%84%E6%88%90%E8%89%AF%E5%A5%BD%E6%AF%94%E4%BE%8B%E7%9A%84%E5%9B%A0%E7%B4%A0%E6%98%AF%E6%9E%81%E5%85%B6%E5%A4%8D%E6%9D%82%E7%9A%84%EF%BC%8C%E6%97%A2%E6%9C%89%E7%BB%9D%E5%AF%B9%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%80%E9%9D%A2%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%88%E6%9C%89%E7%9B%B8%E5%AF%B9%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%80%E9%9D%A2%EF%BC%8C%E4%BC%81%E5%9B%BE%E6%89%BE%E5%88%B0%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E6%94%BE%E5%9C%A8%E4%BB%BB%E4%BD%95%E5%9C%B0%E6%96%B9%E9%83%BD%E9%80%82%E5%90%88%E7%9A%84%EF%BC%8C%E7%BB%9D%E5%AF%B9%E7%BE%8E%E7%9A%84%E6%AF%94%E4%BE%8B%EF%BC%8C%E4%BA%8B%E5%AE%9E%E4%B8%8A%E6%98%AF%E5%8A%9E%E4%B8%8D%E5%88%B0%E7%9A%84%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="和比例相联系的另一个范畴是尺度。尺度所研究的是建筑物的整体或局部给人感觉上的大小印象和其真实大小之间的关系问题。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%92%8C%E6%AF%94%E4%BE%8B%E7%9B%B8%E8%81%94%E7%B3%BB%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%A6%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E8%8C%83%E7%95%B4%E6%98%AF%E5%B0%BA%E5%BA%A6%E3%80%82%E5%B0%BA%E5%BA%A6%E6%89%80%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E7%9A%84%E6%98%AF%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%89%A9%E7%9A%84%E6%95%B4%E4%BD%93%E6%88%96%E5%B1%80%E9%83%A8%E7%BB%99%E4%BA%BA%E6%84%9F%E8%A7%89%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%A7%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%B0%E8%B1%A1%E5%92%8C%E5%85%B6%E7%9C%9F%E5%AE%9E%E5%A4%A7%E5%B0%8F%E4%B9%8B%E9%97%B4%E7%9A%84%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="尺度涉及真实大小和尺寸，但不能把尺寸的大小和尺度的概念混为一谈。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%B0%BA%E5%BA%A6%E6%B6%89%E5%8F%8A%E7%9C%9F%E5%AE%9E%E5%A4%A7%E5%B0%8F%E5%92%8C%E5%B0%BA%E5%AF%B8%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%86%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E6%8A%8A%E5%B0%BA%E5%AF%B8%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%A7%E5%B0%8F%E5%92%8C%E5%B0%BA%E5%BA%A6%E7%9A%84%E6%A6%82%E5%BF%B5%E6%B7%B7%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%80%E8%B0%88%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="尺度一般不是指要素真实尺寸的大小，而是指要素给人感觉上的大小印象和其真实大小之间的关系。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%B0%BA%E5%BA%A6%E4%B8%80%E8%88%AC%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AF%E6%8C%87%E8%A6%81%E7%B4%A0%E7%9C%9F%E5%AE%9E%E5%B0%BA%E5%AF%B8%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%A7%E5%B0%8F%EF%BC%8C%E8%80%8C%E6%98%AF%E6%8C%87%E8%A6%81%E7%B4%A0%E7%BB%99%E4%BA%BA%E6%84%9F%E8%A7%89%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%A7%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%B0%E8%B1%A1%E5%92%8C%E5%85%B6%E7%9C%9F%E5%AE%9E%E5%A4%A7%E5%B0%8F%E4%B9%8B%E9%97%B4%E7%9A%84%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（四）内部空间处理" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E5%9B%9B%EF%BC%89%E5%86%85%E9%83%A8%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="单一空间的体量与尺度、形状与比例、围与透、分隔与界面处理、色彩与质感。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%8D%95%E4%B8%80%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%93%E9%87%8F%E4%B8%8E%E5%B0%BA%E5%BA%A6%E3%80%81%E5%BD%A2%E7%8A%B6%E4%B8%8E%E6%AF%94%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%81%E5%9B%B4%E4%B8%8E%E9%80%8F%E3%80%81%E5%88%86%E9%9A%94%E4%B8%8E%E7%95%8C%E9%9D%A2%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86%E3%80%81%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E4%B8%8E%E8%B4%A8%E6%84%9F%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="多空间组合中的对比与变化、重复与再现、衔接与过渡、渗透与层次、引导与暗示、节奏与序列。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%A4%9A%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E7%BB%84%E5%90%88%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E5%AF%B9%E6%AF%94%E4%B8%8E%E5%8F%98%E5%8C%96%E3%80%81%E9%87%8D%E5%A4%8D%E4%B8%8E%E5%86%8D%E7%8E%B0%E3%80%81%E8%A1%94%E6%8E%A5%E4%B8%8E%E8%BF%87%E6%B8%A1%E3%80%81%E6%B8%97%E9%80%8F%E4%B8%8E%E5%B1%82%E6%AC%A1%E3%80%81%E5%BC%95%E5%AF%BC%E4%B8%8E%E6%9A%97%E7%A4%BA%E3%80%81%E8%8A%82%E5%A5%8F%E4%B8%8E%E5%BA%8F%E5%88%97%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="建筑空间有内、外之分，在一般情况下，人们常常用有无屋顶当作区分内、外部空间的标志。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E6%9C%89%E5%86%85%E3%80%81%E5%A4%96%E4%B9%8B%E5%88%86%EF%BC%8C%E5%9C%A8%E4%B8%80%E8%88%AC%E6%83%85%E5%86%B5%E4%B8%8B%EF%BC%8C%E4%BA%BA%E4%BB%AC%E5%B8%B8%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E6%9C%89%E6%97%A0%E5%B1%8B%E9%A1%B6%E5%BD%93%E4%BD%9C%E5%8C%BA%E5%88%86%E5%86%85%E3%80%81%E5%A4%96%E9%83%A8%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E7%9A%84%E6%A0%87%E5%BF%97%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="日本建筑师芦原义信在《外部空间设计》一书中也是用这种方法来区分的。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%88%E8%8A%A6%E5%8E%9F%E4%B9%89%E4%BF%A1%E5%9C%A8%E3%80%8A%E5%A4%96%E9%83%A8%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E3%80%8B%E4%B8%80%E4%B9%A6%E4%B8%AD%E4%B9%9F%E6%98%AF%E7%94%A8%E8%BF%99%E7%A7%8D%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%E6%9D%A5%E5%8C%BA%E5%88%86%E7%9A%84%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（五）外部体形处理" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%BA%94%EF%BC%89%E5%A4%96%E9%83%A8%E4%BD%93%E5%BD%A2%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="外部体形是内部空间的反映，要考虑建筑个性与性格特征的表现，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%A4%96%E9%83%A8%E4%BD%93%E5%BD%A2%E6%98%AF%E5%86%85%E9%83%A8%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%8D%E6%98%A0%EF%BC%8C%E8%A6%81%E8%80%83%E8%99%91%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E4%B8%AA%E6%80%A7%E4%B8%8E%E6%80%A7%E6%A0%BC%E7%89%B9%E5%BE%81%E7%9A%84%E8%A1%A8%E7%8E%B0%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="体量组合与立面处理（主从分明，有机结合、对比与变化、稳定与均衡、比例与尺度、虚实凹凸、色彩与质感、装饰与细部）。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BD%93%E9%87%8F%E7%BB%84%E5%90%88%E4%B8%8E%E7%AB%8B%E9%9D%A2%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%BB%E4%BB%8E%E5%88%86%E6%98%8E%EF%BC%8C%E6%9C%89%E6%9C%BA%E7%BB%93%E5%90%88%E3%80%81%E5%AF%B9%E6%AF%94%E4%B8%8E%E5%8F%98%E5%8C%96%E3%80%81%E7%A8%B3%E5%AE%9A%E4%B8%8E%E5%9D%87%E8%A1%A1%E3%80%81%E6%AF%94%E4%BE%8B%E4%B8%8E%E5%B0%BA%E5%BA%A6%E3%80%81%E8%99%9A%E5%AE%9E%E5%87%B9%E5%87%B8%E3%80%81%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E4%B8%8E%E8%B4%A8%E6%84%9F%E3%80%81%E8%A3%85%E9%A5%B0%E4%B8%8E%E7%BB%86%E9%83%A8%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（六）群体组合" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E5%85%AD%EF%BC%89%E7%BE%A4%E4%BD%93%E7%BB%84%E5%90%88%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="建筑与环境关系要有机联系、统一和谐。建筑要结合地形设计。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E4%B8%8E%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%E8%A6%81%E6%9C%89%E6%9C%BA%E8%81%94%E7%B3%BB%E3%80%81%E7%BB%9F%E4%B8%80%E5%92%8C%E8%B0%90%E3%80%82%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%A6%81%E7%BB%93%E5%90%88%E5%9C%B0%E5%BD%A2%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="运用对称、轴线引导与转折、向心等手法，可通过结合地形、体形重复、形式与风格一致等手段获得统一与和谐。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%BF%90%E7%94%A8%E5%AF%B9%E7%A7%B0%E3%80%81%E8%BD%B4%E7%BA%BF%E5%BC%95%E5%AF%BC%E4%B8%8E%E8%BD%AC%E6%8A%98%E3%80%81%E5%90%91%E5%BF%83%E7%AD%89%E6%89%8B%E6%B3%95%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%AF%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87%E7%BB%93%E5%90%88%E5%9C%B0%E5%BD%A2%E3%80%81%E4%BD%93%E5%BD%A2%E9%87%8D%E5%A4%8D%E3%80%81%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E4%B8%8E%E9%A3%8E%E6%A0%BC%E4%B8%80%E8%87%B4%E7%AD%89%E6%89%8B%E6%AE%B5%E8%8E%B7%E5%BE%97%E7%BB%9F%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%8E%E5%92%8C%E8%B0%90%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="" _mubu_text="" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（七）当代西方建筑的审美特点" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%83%EF%BC%89%E5%BD%93%E4%BB%A3%E8%A5%BF%E6%96%B9%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%A1%E7%BE%8E%E7%89%B9%E7%82%B9%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="" _mubu_text="" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="从近代到20世纪末的近二百年历史中，建筑的审美观念发生了两次重大转折：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BB%8E%E8%BF%91%E4%BB%A3%E5%88%B020%E4%B8%96%E7%BA%AA%E6%9C%AB%E7%9A%84%E8%BF%91%E4%BA%8C%E7%99%BE%E5%B9%B4%E5%8E%86%E5%8F%B2%E4%B8%AD%EF%BC%8C%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%A1%E7%BE%8E%E8%A7%82%E5%BF%B5%E5%8F%91%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%86%E4%B8%A4%E6%AC%A1%E9%87%8D%E5%A4%A7%E8%BD%AC%E6%8A%98%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="1.从古典建筑的构图原理到现代建筑的技术美学古典建筑的美学思想历史悠久，古希腊的亚里士多德系统论述了形式美的原则，即" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1.%E4%BB%8E%E5%8F%A4%E5%85%B8%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%9A%84%E6%9E%84%E5%9B%BE%E5%8E%9F%E7%90%86%E5%88%B0%E7%8E%B0%E4%BB%A3%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%9A%84%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E7%BE%8E%E5%AD%A6%E5%8F%A4%E5%85%B8%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%9A%84%E7%BE%8E%E5%AD%A6%E6%80%9D%E6%83%B3%E5%8E%86%E5%8F%B2%E6%82%A0%E4%B9%85%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%A4%E5%B8%8C%E8%85%8A%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%9A%E9%87%8C%E5%A3%AB%E5%A4%9A%E5%BE%B7%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E8%AE%BA%E8%BF%B0%E4%BA%86%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E7%BE%8E%E7%9A%84%E5%8E%9F%E5%88%99%EF%BC%8C%E5%8D%B3%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="“多样统一”，毕达哥拉斯学派提出了“黄金分割”规律。1924年，拉普森所著《建筑构图原理》在英国出版。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%E5%A4%9A%E6%A0%B7%E7%BB%9F%E4%B8%80%E2%80%9D%EF%BC%8C%E6%AF%95%E8%BE%BE%E5%93%A5%E6%8B%89%E6%96%AF%E5%AD%A6%E6%B4%BE%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E4%BA%86%E2%80%9C%E9%BB%84%E9%87%91%E5%88%86%E5%89%B2%E2%80%9D%E8%A7%84%E5%BE%8B%E3%80%821924%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%8C%E6%8B%89%E6%99%AE%E6%A3%AE%E6%89%80%E8%91%97%E3%80%8A%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E6%9E%84%E5%9B%BE%E5%8E%9F%E7%90%86%E3%80%8B%E5%9C%A8%E8%8B%B1%E5%9B%BD%E5%87%BA%E7%89%88%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="工业革命后，建筑功能日趋复杂，新的建筑类型日益增多；再也不能把它容纳到古典建筑简单的空间形式之中，于是便引发了新建筑运动。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%9A%E9%9D%A9%E5%91%BD%E5%90%8E%EF%BC%8C%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E6%97%A5%E8%B6%8B%E5%A4%8D%E6%9D%82%EF%BC%8C%E6%96%B0%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B%E6%97%A5%E7%9B%8A%E5%A2%9E%E5%A4%9A%EF%BC%9B%E5%86%8D%E4%B9%9F%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E6%8A%8A%E5%AE%83%E5%AE%B9%E7%BA%B3%E5%88%B0%E5%8F%A4%E5%85%B8%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%AE%80%E5%8D%95%E7%9A%84%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E4%B9%8B%E4%B8%AD%EF%BC%8C%E4%BA%8E%E6%98%AF%E4%BE%BF%E5%BC%95%E5%8F%91%E4%BA%86%E6%96%B0%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%BF%90%E5%8A%A8%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="古典建筑形式虽然遭到了否定，但是它所依据的美学思想却依然存在。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%8F%A4%E5%85%B8%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E8%99%BD%E7%84%B6%E9%81%AD%E5%88%B0%E4%BA%86%E5%90%A6%E5%AE%9A%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%86%E6%98%AF%E5%AE%83%E6%89%80%E4%BE%9D%E6%8D%AE%E7%9A%84%E7%BE%8E%E5%AD%A6%E6%80%9D%E6%83%B3%E5%8D%B4%E4%BE%9D%E7%84%B6%E5%AD%98%E5%9C%A8%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="2.从现代建筑的技术美学到当代建筑的审美特点" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2.%E4%BB%8E%E7%8E%B0%E4%BB%A3%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%9A%84%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E7%BE%8E%E5%AD%A6%E5%88%B0%E5%BD%93%E4%BB%A3%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%A1%E7%BE%8E%E7%89%B9%E7%82%B9%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="（1）变异的美学特征" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E5%8F%98%E5%BC%82%E7%9A%84%E7%BE%8E%E5%AD%A6%E7%89%B9%E5%BE%81%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="1）追求多义与含混。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1%EF%BC%89%E8%BF%BD%E6%B1%82%E5%A4%9A%E4%B9%89%E4%B8%8E%E5%90%AB%E6%B7%B7%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="例如日本建筑师黑川纪章设计的名古屋市现代美术馆，在建筑形式上运用各种要素相互冲突又相互包容，创造出包含模糊信息的建筑区域；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BE%8B%E5%A6%82%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%88%E9%BB%91%E5%B7%9D%E7%BA%AA%E7%AB%A0%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E7%9A%84%E5%90%8D%E5%8F%A4%E5%B1%8B%E5%B8%82%E7%8E%B0%E4%BB%A3%E7%BE%8E%E6%9C%AF%E9%A6%86%EF%BC%8C%E5%9C%A8%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E4%B8%8A%E8%BF%90%E7%94%A8%E5%90%84%E7%A7%8D%E8%A6%81%E7%B4%A0%E7%9B%B8%E4%BA%92%E5%86%B2%E7%AA%81%E5%8F%88%E7%9B%B8%E4%BA%92%E5%8C%85%E5%AE%B9%EF%BC%8C%E5%88%9B%E9%80%A0%E5%87%BA%E5%8C%85%E5%90%AB%E6%A8%A1%E7%B3%8A%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%8C%BA%E5%9F%9F%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      </outline>
      <outline text="2）追求个性表现。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2%EF%BC%89%E8%BF%BD%E6%B1%82%E4%B8%AA%E6%80%A7%E8%A1%A8%E7%8E%B0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="例如美国建筑师盖里设计的加利福尼亚航天博物馆，用各种几何形体塑造出奇特怪异的形象，使建筑像一个无法复制的雕塑品，充分表现了作者独特的个性：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BE%8B%E5%A6%82%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%88%E7%9B%96%E9%87%8C%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E7%9A%84%E5%8A%A0%E5%88%A9%E7%A6%8F%E5%B0%BC%E4%BA%9A%E8%88%AA%E5%A4%A9%E5%8D%9A%E7%89%A9%E9%A6%86%EF%BC%8C%E7%94%A8%E5%90%84%E7%A7%8D%E5%87%A0%E4%BD%95%E5%BD%A2%E4%BD%93%E5%A1%91%E9%80%A0%E5%87%BA%E5%A5%87%E7%89%B9%E6%80%AA%E5%BC%82%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%A2%E8%B1%A1%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%BF%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%83%8F%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E6%97%A0%E6%B3%95%E5%A4%8D%E5%88%B6%E7%9A%84%E9%9B%95%E5%A1%91%E5%93%81%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%85%E5%88%86%E8%A1%A8%E7%8E%B0%E4%BA%86%E4%BD%9C%E8%80%85%E7%8B%AC%E7%89%B9%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%AA%E6%80%A7%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      </outline>
      <outline text="3）怪诞与滑稽。如高松伸设计的“织阵”像一个怪异的“仿生机器”，功能失去了对形式的制约，表现出极大的随意性；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E3%EF%BC%89%E6%80%AA%E8%AF%9E%E4%B8%8E%E6%BB%91%E7%A8%BD%E3%80%82%E5%A6%82%E9%AB%98%E6%9D%BE%E4%BC%B8%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E7%9A%84%E2%80%9C%E7%BB%87%E9%98%B5%E2%80%9D%E5%83%8F%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E6%80%AA%E5%BC%82%E7%9A%84%E2%80%9C%E4%BB%BF%E7%94%9F%E6%9C%BA%E5%99%A8%E2%80%9D%EF%BC%8C%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E5%A4%B1%E5%8E%BB%E4%BA%86%E5%AF%B9%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E7%9A%84%E5%88%B6%E7%BA%A6%EF%BC%8C%E8%A1%A8%E7%8E%B0%E5%87%BA%E6%9E%81%E5%A4%A7%E7%9A%84%E9%9A%8F%E6%84%8F%E6%80%A7%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="4）残破、扭曲、畸变。如盖里的自宅，设计力图造成一种不完美、残缺的形象。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E4%EF%BC%89%E6%AE%8B%E7%A0%B4%E3%80%81%E6%89%AD%E6%9B%B2%E3%80%81%E7%95%B8%E5%8F%98%E3%80%82%E5%A6%82%E7%9B%96%E9%87%8C%E7%9A%84%E8%87%AA%E5%AE%85%EF%BC%8C%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%8A%9B%E5%9B%BE%E9%80%A0%E6%88%90%E4%B8%80%E7%A7%8D%E4%B8%8D%E5%AE%8C%E7%BE%8E%E3%80%81%E6%AE%8B%E7%BC%BA%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%A2%E8%B1%A1%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="（2）多元化的创作倾向" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E5%A4%9A%E5%85%83%E5%8C%96%E7%9A%84%E5%88%9B%E4%BD%9C%E5%80%BE%E5%90%91%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="1）历史主义的倾向；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1%EF%BC%89%E5%8E%86%E5%8F%B2%E4%B8%BB%E4%B9%89%E7%9A%84%E5%80%BE%E5%90%91%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="2）乡土主义倾向；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2%EF%BC%89%E4%B9%A1%E5%9C%9F%E4%B8%BB%E4%B9%89%E5%80%BE%E5%90%91%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="3）追求高技术的倾向；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E3%EF%BC%89%E8%BF%BD%E6%B1%82%E9%AB%98%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E7%9A%84%E5%80%BE%E5%90%91%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="4）解构主义倾向；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E4%EF%BC%89%E8%A7%A3%E6%9E%84%E4%B8%BB%E4%B9%89%E5%80%BE%E5%90%91%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="5）有机综合和可持续发展。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E5%EF%BC%89%E6%9C%89%E6%9C%BA%E7%BB%BC%E5%90%88%E5%92%8C%E5%8F%AF%E6%8C%81%E7%BB%AD%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="第四节    室内设计原理" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%AC%AC%E5%9B%9B%E8%8A%82%20%20%20%20%E5%AE%A4%E5%86%85%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%8E%9F%E7%90%86%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="1.室内设计的演化（室内简史）" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1.%E5%AE%A4%E5%86%85%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E7%9A%84%E6%BC%94%E5%8C%96%EF%BC%88%E5%AE%A4%E5%86%85%E7%AE%80%E5%8F%B2%EF%BC%89%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="室内设计是与建筑设计同步产生的，两者的发展息息相关。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%AE%A4%E5%86%85%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%8E%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%90%8C%E6%AD%A5%E4%BA%A7%E7%94%9F%E7%9A%84%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%A4%E8%80%85%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E6%81%AF%E6%81%AF%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="室内设计的演化与两大因素有关：一是地理因素，二是文化因素。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%AE%A4%E5%86%85%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E7%9A%84%E6%BC%94%E5%8C%96%E4%B8%8E%E4%B8%A4%E5%A4%A7%E5%9B%A0%E7%B4%A0%E6%9C%89%E5%85%B3%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%80%E6%98%AF%E5%9C%B0%E7%90%86%E5%9B%A0%E7%B4%A0%EF%BC%8C%E4%BA%8C%E6%98%AF%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96%E5%9B%A0%E7%B4%A0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（一）室内设计基本概念" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%80%EF%BC%89%E5%AE%A4%E5%86%85%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%A6%82%E5%BF%B5%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="室内设计是指运用一定的物质技术手段与经济能力，根据对象所处的特定环境，对内部空间进行创造与组织，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%AE%A4%E5%86%85%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E6%98%AF%E6%8C%87%E8%BF%90%E7%94%A8%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%9A%E7%9A%84%E7%89%A9%E8%B4%A8%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E6%89%8B%E6%AE%B5%E4%B8%8E%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E8%83%BD%E5%8A%9B%EF%BC%8C%E6%A0%B9%E6%8D%AE%E5%AF%B9%E8%B1%A1%E6%89%80%E5%A4%84%E7%9A%84%E7%89%B9%E5%AE%9A%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%EF%BC%8C%E5%AF%B9%E5%86%85%E9%83%A8%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E5%88%9B%E9%80%A0%E4%B8%8E%E7%BB%84%E7%BB%87%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="形成安全、卫生、舒适、优美、生态的内部环境，满足人们对物质与精神生活的需要。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%BD%A2%E6%88%90%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E3%80%81%E5%8D%AB%E7%94%9F%E3%80%81%E8%88%92%E9%80%82%E3%80%81%E4%BC%98%E7%BE%8E%E3%80%81%E7%94%9F%E6%80%81%E7%9A%84%E5%86%85%E9%83%A8%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%EF%BC%8C%E6%BB%A1%E8%B6%B3%E4%BA%BA%E4%BB%AC%E5%AF%B9%E7%89%A9%E8%B4%A8%E4%B8%8E%E7%B2%BE%E7%A5%9E%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E7%9A%84%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（1）中国传统室内设计特征" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E4%BC%A0%E7%BB%9F%E5%AE%A4%E5%86%85%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E7%89%B9%E5%BE%81%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="中国传统室内设计的基本特征：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E4%BC%A0%E7%BB%9F%E5%AE%A4%E5%86%85%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E7%89%B9%E5%BE%81%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="内外空间一体化、" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%86%85%E5%A4%96%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E4%B8%80%E4%BD%93%E5%8C%96%E3%80%81%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="建筑布局灵活化、" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E7%81%B5%E6%B4%BB%E5%8C%96%E3%80%81%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="陈设多样化、" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%99%88%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%9A%E6%A0%B7%E5%8C%96%E3%80%81%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="构件装饰化、" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%9E%84%E4%BB%B6%E8%A3%85%E9%A5%B0%E5%8C%96%E3%80%81%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="图案象征化。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9B%BE%E6%A1%88%E8%B1%A1%E5%BE%81%E5%8C%96%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      </outline>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（2）西方室内设计学科的确立与发展" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E8%A5%BF%E6%96%B9%E5%AE%A4%E5%86%85%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%AD%A6%E7%A7%91%E7%9A%84%E7%A1%AE%E7%AB%8B%E4%B8%8E%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="西方室内设计涉及范围广泛，内容丰富多彩。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%A5%BF%E6%96%B9%E5%AE%A4%E5%86%85%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E6%B6%89%E5%8F%8A%E8%8C%83%E5%9B%B4%E5%B9%BF%E6%B3%9B%EF%BC%8C%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%E4%B8%B0%E5%AF%8C%E5%A4%9A%E5%BD%A9%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="20世纪初期，现代主义建筑运动兴起，室内设计也受到影响，终于从单纯装饰的束缚中解脱出来，并促成了室内设计的相对独立发展。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E20%E4%B8%96%E7%BA%AA%E5%88%9D%E6%9C%9F%EF%BC%8C%E7%8E%B0%E4%BB%A3%E4%B8%BB%E4%B9%89%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%BF%90%E5%8A%A8%E5%85%B4%E8%B5%B7%EF%BC%8C%E5%AE%A4%E5%86%85%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E4%B9%9F%E5%8F%97%E5%88%B0%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%EF%BC%8C%E7%BB%88%E4%BA%8E%E4%BB%8E%E5%8D%95%E7%BA%AF%E8%A3%85%E9%A5%B0%E7%9A%84%E6%9D%9F%E7%BC%9A%E4%B8%AD%E8%A7%A3%E8%84%B1%E5%87%BA%E6%9D%A5%EF%BC%8C%E5%B9%B6%E4%BF%83%E6%88%90%E4%BA%86%E5%AE%A4%E5%86%85%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E7%9A%84%E7%9B%B8%E5%AF%B9%E7%8B%AC%E7%AB%8B%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="1957年，美国室内设计师学会成立，标志着室内设计学科的确立。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1957%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%8C%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E5%AE%A4%E5%86%85%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%B8%88%E5%AD%A6%E4%BC%9A%E6%88%90%E7%AB%8B%EF%BC%8C%E6%A0%87%E5%BF%97%E7%9D%80%E5%AE%A4%E5%86%85%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%AD%A6%E7%A7%91%E7%9A%84%E7%A1%AE%E7%AB%8B%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（3）晚期现代主义对室内设计的影响" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E6%99%9A%E6%9C%9F%E7%8E%B0%E4%BB%A3%E4%B8%BB%E4%B9%89%E5%AF%B9%E5%AE%A4%E5%86%85%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="现代建筑从形式单一逐渐演变成形式的多样化，路易斯·康认为一个建筑应该由两部分构成一—“服务空间”和“被服务空间”，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%8E%B0%E4%BB%A3%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E4%BB%8E%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E5%8D%95%E4%B8%80%E9%80%90%E6%B8%90%E6%BC%94%E5%8F%98%E6%88%90%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%9A%E6%A0%B7%E5%8C%96%EF%BC%8C%E8%B7%AF%E6%98%93%E6%96%AF%C2%B7%E5%BA%B7%E8%AE%A4%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%BA%94%E8%AF%A5%E7%94%B1%E4%B8%A4%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E6%9E%84%E6%88%90%E4%B8%80%E2%80%94%E2%80%9C%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E2%80%9D%E5%92%8C%E2%80%9C%E8%A2%AB%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E2%80%9D%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="这种做法已经偏离了沙利文“形式追随功能”的初衷，把结构和构造转变为了一种装饰。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%BF%99%E7%A7%8D%E5%81%9A%E6%B3%95%E5%B7%B2%E7%BB%8F%E5%81%8F%E7%A6%BB%E4%BA%86%E6%B2%99%E5%88%A9%E6%96%87%E2%80%9C%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E8%BF%BD%E9%9A%8F%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E2%80%9D%E7%9A%84%E5%88%9D%E8%A1%B7%EF%BC%8C%E6%8A%8A%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E5%92%8C%E6%9E%84%E9%80%A0%E8%BD%AC%E5%8F%98%E4%B8%BA%E4%BA%86%E4%B8%80%E7%A7%8D%E8%A3%85%E9%A5%B0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="2.室内设计的程序" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2.%E5%AE%A4%E5%86%85%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E7%9A%84%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="室内设计的过程可分为以下个阶段，即：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%AE%A4%E5%86%85%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E7%9A%84%E8%BF%87%E7%A8%8B%E5%8F%AF%E5%88%86%E4%B8%BA%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8B%E4%B8%AA%E9%98%B6%E6%AE%B5%EF%BC%8C%E5%8D%B3%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="设计准备阶段、" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%87%86%E5%A4%87%E9%98%B6%E6%AE%B5%E3%80%81%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="方案设计阶段、" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E9%98%B6%E6%AE%B5%E3%80%81%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="深化设计（初步设计）阶段、" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%B7%B1%E5%8C%96%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%EF%BC%88%E5%88%9D%E6%AD%A5%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%EF%BC%89%E9%98%B6%E6%AE%B5%E3%80%81%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="施工图设阶段、" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%96%BD%E5%B7%A5%E5%9B%BE%E8%AE%BE%E9%98%B6%E6%AE%B5%E3%80%81%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="现场配合阶段、" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%8E%B0%E5%9C%BA%E9%85%8D%E5%90%88%E9%98%B6%E6%AE%B5%E3%80%81%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="评价阶段。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%AF%84%E4%BB%B7%E9%98%B6%E6%AE%B5%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      </outline>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（二）室内环境与设备控制" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%BA%8C%EF%BC%89%E5%AE%A4%E5%86%85%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E4%B8%8E%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="1.室内空间环境要素" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1.%E5%AE%A4%E5%86%85%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E8%A6%81%E7%B4%A0%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="室内空间环境要素包括：家具、陈设、绿化、标志等，除了实用功能外，还有组织空间、丰富空间和营造宜人环境的作用。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%AE%A4%E5%86%85%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E8%A6%81%E7%B4%A0%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%EF%BC%9A%E5%AE%B6%E5%85%B7%E3%80%81%E9%99%88%E8%AE%BE%E3%80%81%E7%BB%BF%E5%8C%96%E3%80%81%E6%A0%87%E5%BF%97%E7%AD%89%EF%BC%8C%E9%99%A4%E4%BA%86%E5%AE%9E%E7%94%A8%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E5%A4%96%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%98%E6%9C%89%E7%BB%84%E7%BB%87%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E3%80%81%E4%B8%B0%E5%AF%8C%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E5%92%8C%E8%90%A5%E9%80%A0%E5%AE%9C%E4%BA%BA%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%9C%E7%94%A8%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="2.室内的设备控制" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2.%E5%AE%A4%E5%86%85%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="室内各类设备的控制对保持室内环境质量有着重要的作用，如：温度、湿度、洁净度等。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%AE%A4%E5%86%85%E5%90%84%E7%B1%BB%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%E7%9A%84%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E5%AF%B9%E4%BF%9D%E6%8C%81%E5%AE%A4%E5%86%85%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E8%B4%A8%E9%87%8F%E6%9C%89%E7%9D%80%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%9C%E7%94%A8%EF%BC%8C%E5%A6%82%EF%BC%9A%E6%B8%A9%E5%BA%A6%E3%80%81%E6%B9%BF%E5%BA%A6%E3%80%81%E6%B4%81%E5%87%80%E5%BA%A6%E7%AD%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="需精准控制的主要设备系统包括：给排水系统、电气设备系统、空调系统等。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%9C%80%E7%B2%BE%E5%87%86%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%EF%BC%9A%E7%BB%99%E6%8E%92%E6%B0%B4%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E3%80%81%E7%94%B5%E6%B0%94%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E3%80%81%E7%A9%BA%E8%B0%83%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%AD%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="3.室内的声学要求" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E3.%E5%AE%A4%E5%86%85%E7%9A%84%E5%A3%B0%E5%AD%A6%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（1）在室内空间和界面设计方面应避免产生各种声学缺陷。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E5%9C%A8%E5%AE%A4%E5%86%85%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E5%92%8C%E7%95%8C%E9%9D%A2%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E6%96%B9%E9%9D%A2%E5%BA%94%E9%81%BF%E5%85%8D%E4%BA%A7%E7%94%9F%E5%90%84%E7%A7%8D%E5%A3%B0%E5%AD%A6%E7%BC%BA%E9%99%B7%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（2）在材料选择方面应该合理使用吸声材料，以便为室内空间创造舒适的声环境。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E5%9C%A8%E6%9D%90%E6%96%99%E9%80%89%E6%8B%A9%E6%96%B9%E9%9D%A2%E5%BA%94%E8%AF%A5%E5%90%88%E7%90%86%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E5%90%B8%E5%A3%B0%E6%9D%90%E6%96%99%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A5%E4%BE%BF%E4%B8%BA%E5%AE%A4%E5%86%85%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E5%88%9B%E9%80%A0%E8%88%92%E9%80%82%E7%9A%84%E5%A3%B0%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="4.室内的光学要求" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E4.%E5%AE%A4%E5%86%85%E7%9A%84%E5%85%89%E5%AD%A6%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="注：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%B3%A8%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="1.在美国，引领现代主义室内设计的三个主要学派：格罗皮乌斯领导下的哈佛学派、密斯指引下的国际式风格，以及克兰布鲁克艺术学院的所谓“匡溪学派”。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1.%E5%9C%A8%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%EF%BC%8C%E5%BC%95%E9%A2%86%E7%8E%B0%E4%BB%A3%E4%B8%BB%E4%B9%89%E5%AE%A4%E5%86%85%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%89%E4%B8%AA%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E5%AD%A6%E6%B4%BE%EF%BC%9A%E6%A0%BC%E7%BD%97%E7%9A%AE%E4%B9%8C%E6%96%AF%E9%A2%86%E5%AF%BC%E4%B8%8B%E7%9A%84%E5%93%88%E4%BD%9B%E5%AD%A6%E6%B4%BE%E3%80%81%E5%AF%86%E6%96%AF%E6%8C%87%E5%BC%95%E4%B8%8B%E7%9A%84%E5%9B%BD%E9%99%85%E5%BC%8F%E9%A3%8E%E6%A0%BC%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%8A%E5%85%8B%E5%85%B0%E5%B8%83%E9%B2%81%E5%85%8B%E8%89%BA%E6%9C%AF%E5%AD%A6%E9%99%A2%E7%9A%84%E6%89%80%E8%B0%93%E2%80%9C%E5%8C%A1%E6%BA%AA%E5%AD%A6%E6%B4%BE%E2%80%9D%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="2.其他室内设计风格或流派的具体内容，详见《建筑设计资料集1》（第三版）和《室内设计原理》。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2.%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E5%AE%A4%E5%86%85%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E9%A3%8E%E6%A0%BC%E6%88%96%E6%B5%81%E6%B4%BE%E7%9A%84%E5%85%B7%E4%BD%93%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%EF%BC%8C%E8%AF%A6%E8%A7%81%E3%80%8A%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E8%B5%84%E6%96%99%E9%9B%861%E3%80%8B%EF%BC%88%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%89%E7%89%88%EF%BC%89%E5%92%8C%E3%80%8A%E5%AE%A4%E5%86%85%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%8E%9F%E7%90%86%E3%80%8B%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="主要是采光和照明。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E6%98%AF%E9%87%87%E5%85%89%E5%92%8C%E7%85%A7%E6%98%8E%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（1）材料选择主要考虑：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E6%9D%90%E6%96%99%E9%80%89%E6%8B%A9%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E8%80%83%E8%99%91%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="室内空间特性（公共性、私密性）" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%AE%A4%E5%86%85%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E7%89%B9%E6%80%A7%EF%BC%88%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E6%80%A7%E3%80%81%E7%A7%81%E5%AF%86%E6%80%A7%EF%BC%89%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="材料性能（保温、吸声、隔声、防火、防水等）。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%9D%90%E6%96%99%E6%80%A7%E8%83%BD%EF%BC%88%E4%BF%9D%E6%B8%A9%E3%80%81%E5%90%B8%E5%A3%B0%E3%80%81%E9%9A%94%E5%A3%B0%E3%80%81%E9%98%B2%E7%81%AB%E3%80%81%E9%98%B2%E6%B0%B4%E7%AD%89%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（2）构造设计要注意：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E6%9E%84%E9%80%A0%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E8%A6%81%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="安全可靠、坚固适用；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E5%8F%AF%E9%9D%A0%E3%80%81%E5%9D%9A%E5%9B%BA%E9%80%82%E7%94%A8%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="造型美观、具有特色；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%80%A0%E5%9E%8B%E7%BE%8E%E8%A7%82%E3%80%81%E5%85%B7%E6%9C%89%E7%89%B9%E8%89%B2%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="造价合适、便于施工；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%80%A0%E4%BB%B7%E5%90%88%E9%80%82%E3%80%81%E4%BE%BF%E4%BA%8E%E6%96%BD%E5%B7%A5%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="考虑工业化、装配化。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%80%83%E8%99%91%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%9A%E5%8C%96%E3%80%81%E8%A3%85%E9%85%8D%E5%8C%96%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="5.材料与构造" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E5.%E6%9D%90%E6%96%99%E4%B8%8E%E6%9E%84%E9%80%A0%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（三）室内设计原则" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%89%EF%BC%89%E5%AE%A4%E5%86%85%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%8E%9F%E5%88%99%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="1.空间的组织" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1.%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%84%E7%BB%87%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="室内空间的限定与组织的主要处理方式：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%AE%A4%E5%86%85%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E7%9A%84%E9%99%90%E5%AE%9A%E4%B8%8E%E7%BB%84%E7%BB%87%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="围合、界面差异、界面升降、界面倾斜、多重限定、" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9B%B4%E5%90%88%E3%80%81%E7%95%8C%E9%9D%A2%E5%B7%AE%E5%BC%82%E3%80%81%E7%95%8C%E9%9D%A2%E5%8D%87%E9%99%8D%E3%80%81%E7%95%8C%E9%9D%A2%E5%80%BE%E6%96%9C%E3%80%81%E5%A4%9A%E9%87%8D%E9%99%90%E5%AE%9A%E3%80%81%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="并联、串联、中心放射、主从关系、包含、减法、变形、穿插等。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%B9%B6%E8%81%94%E3%80%81%E4%B8%B2%E8%81%94%E3%80%81%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%E6%94%BE%E5%B0%84%E3%80%81%E4%B8%BB%E4%BB%8E%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%E3%80%81%E5%8C%85%E5%90%AB%E3%80%81%E5%87%8F%E6%B3%95%E3%80%81%E5%8F%98%E5%BD%A2%E3%80%81%E7%A9%BF%E6%8F%92%E7%AD%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      </outline>
    </outline>
    <outline text="2.形式美的原则" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2.%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E7%BE%8E%E7%9A%84%E5%8E%9F%E5%88%99%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="多样统一是形式美的原则；具体来说，又包含以下几个方面：均衡与稳定，韵律与节奏，对比与微差，重点与一般。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%A4%9A%E6%A0%B7%E7%BB%9F%E4%B8%80%E6%98%AF%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E7%BE%8E%E7%9A%84%E5%8E%9F%E5%88%99%EF%BC%9B%E5%85%B7%E4%BD%93%E6%9D%A5%E8%AF%B4%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%88%E5%8C%85%E5%90%AB%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8B%E5%87%A0%E4%B8%AA%E6%96%B9%E9%9D%A2%EF%BC%9A%E5%9D%87%E8%A1%A1%E4%B8%8E%E7%A8%B3%E5%AE%9A%EF%BC%8C%E9%9F%B5%E5%BE%8B%E4%B8%8E%E8%8A%82%E5%A5%8F%EF%BC%8C%E5%AF%B9%E6%AF%94%E4%B8%8E%E5%BE%AE%E5%B7%AE%EF%BC%8C%E9%87%8D%E7%82%B9%E4%B8%8E%E4%B8%80%E8%88%AC%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（五）室内设计与心理学" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%BA%94%EF%BC%89%E5%AE%A4%E5%86%85%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E4%B8%8E%E5%BF%83%E7%90%86%E5%AD%A6%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（四）室内设计评价原则" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E5%9B%9B%EF%BC%89%E5%AE%A4%E5%86%85%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E8%AF%84%E4%BB%B7%E5%8E%9F%E5%88%99%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="室内设计评价在发达国家已经发展成比较成熟的体系，在我国还处于起步阶段。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%AE%A4%E5%86%85%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E8%AF%84%E4%BB%B7%E5%9C%A8%E5%8F%91%E8%BE%BE%E5%9B%BD%E5%AE%B6%E5%B7%B2%E7%BB%8F%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E6%88%90%E6%AF%94%E8%BE%83%E6%88%90%E7%86%9F%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%93%E7%B3%BB%EF%BC%8C%E5%9C%A8%E6%88%91%E5%9B%BD%E8%BF%98%E5%A4%84%E4%BA%8E%E8%B5%B7%E6%AD%A5%E9%98%B6%E6%AE%B5%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="评价的原则主要有：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%AF%84%E4%BB%B7%E7%9A%84%E5%8E%9F%E5%88%99%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E6%9C%89%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="功能原则、" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E5%8E%9F%E5%88%99%E3%80%81%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="美学原则、" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%BE%8E%E5%AD%A6%E5%8E%9F%E5%88%99%E3%80%81%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="技术经济原则、" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E5%8E%9F%E5%88%99%E3%80%81%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="人性化原则、" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BA%BA%E6%80%A7%E5%8C%96%E5%8E%9F%E5%88%99%E3%80%81%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="生态可持续原则、" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%94%9F%E6%80%81%E5%8F%AF%E6%8C%81%E7%BB%AD%E5%8E%9F%E5%88%99%E3%80%81%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="继承与创新原则等。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%BB%A7%E6%89%BF%E4%B8%8E%E5%88%9B%E6%96%B0%E5%8E%9F%E5%88%99%E7%AD%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      </outline>
    </outline>
    <outline text="1.马斯洛层次需求理论" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1.%E9%A9%AC%E6%96%AF%E6%B4%9B%E5%B1%82%E6%AC%A1%E9%9C%80%E6%B1%82%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="该理论是美国著名社会心理学家、第三代心理学的开创者亚伯拉罕·马斯洛（A.H.Maslow）提出的。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%AF%A5%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA%E6%98%AF%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E8%91%97%E5%90%8D%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E5%BF%83%E7%90%86%E5%AD%A6%E5%AE%B6%E3%80%81%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%89%E4%BB%A3%E5%BF%83%E7%90%86%E5%AD%A6%E7%9A%84%E5%BC%80%E5%88%9B%E8%80%85%E4%BA%9A%E4%BC%AF%E6%8B%89%E7%BD%95%C2%B7%E9%A9%AC%E6%96%AF%E6%B4%9B%EF%BC%88A.H.Maslow%EF%BC%89%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E7%9A%84%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="马斯洛认为人都潜藏着7种不同层次的需要：生理、安全、社交、尊重、认知、审美和自我实现。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%A9%AC%E6%96%AF%E6%B4%9B%E8%AE%A4%E4%B8%BA%E4%BA%BA%E9%83%BD%E6%BD%9C%E8%97%8F%E7%9D%807%E7%A7%8D%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E5%B1%82%E6%AC%A1%E7%9A%84%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%EF%BC%9A%E7%94%9F%E7%90%86%E3%80%81%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E3%80%81%E7%A4%BE%E4%BA%A4%E3%80%81%E5%B0%8A%E9%87%8D%E3%80%81%E8%AE%A4%E7%9F%A5%E3%80%81%E5%AE%A1%E7%BE%8E%E5%92%8C%E8%87%AA%E6%88%91%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="" _mubu_text="" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="2.气泡理论" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2.%E6%B0%94%E6%B3%A1%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="该理论是萨默（R.Sommer）提出的，包括：密切距离、个人距离、社会（社交）距离和公共（公众）距离。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%AF%A5%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA%E6%98%AF%E8%90%A8%E9%BB%98%EF%BC%88R.Sommer%EF%BC%89%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E7%9A%84%EF%BC%8C%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%EF%BC%9A%E5%AF%86%E5%88%87%E8%B7%9D%E7%A6%BB%E3%80%81%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E8%B7%9D%E7%A6%BB%E3%80%81%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%EF%BC%88%E7%A4%BE%E4%BA%A4%EF%BC%89%E8%B7%9D%E7%A6%BB%E5%92%8C%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%EF%BC%88%E5%85%AC%E4%BC%97%EF%BC%89%E8%B7%9D%E7%A6%BB%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="有关“环境心理学”的具体内容，详见本章第七节。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%9C%89%E5%85%B3%E2%80%9C%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%BF%83%E7%90%86%E5%AD%A6%E2%80%9D%E7%9A%84%E5%85%B7%E4%BD%93%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%EF%BC%8C%E8%AF%A6%E8%A7%81%E6%9C%AC%E7%AB%A0%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%83%E8%8A%82%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="第五节   建筑色彩知识" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%94%E8%8A%82%20%20%20%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="色彩是人眼所看见的光色和物色现象的产物，以电磁波的形式引起的视觉体验，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E6%98%AF%E4%BA%BA%E7%9C%BC%E6%89%80%E7%9C%8B%E8%A7%81%E7%9A%84%E5%85%89%E8%89%B2%E5%92%8C%E7%89%A9%E8%89%B2%E7%8E%B0%E8%B1%A1%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%A7%E7%89%A9%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A5%E7%94%B5%E7%A3%81%E6%B3%A2%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E5%BC%95%E8%B5%B7%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%86%E8%A7%89%E4%BD%93%E9%AA%8C%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="其中可见光只是整个电磁波中380~780nm的很小一部分（1nm=10~m）[参见：《建筑设计资料集1》（第三版）]。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%85%B6%E4%B8%AD%E5%8F%AF%E8%A7%81%E5%85%89%E5%8F%AA%E6%98%AF%E6%95%B4%E4%B8%AA%E7%94%B5%E7%A3%81%E6%B3%A2%E4%B8%AD380~780nm%E7%9A%84%E5%BE%88%E5%B0%8F%E4%B8%80%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%EF%BC%881nm=10~m%EF%BC%89%5B%E5%8F%82%E8%A7%81%EF%BC%9A%E3%80%8A%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E8%B5%84%E6%96%99%E9%9B%861%E3%80%8B%EF%BC%88%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%89%E7%89%88%EF%BC%89%5D%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（一）色彩的基础知识" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%80%EF%BC%89%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="1.光与色彩的关系" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1.%E5%85%89%E4%B8%8E%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E7%9A%84%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="所有色彩都是由可见光谱中不同波长的光波组成。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%89%80%E6%9C%89%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E9%83%BD%E6%98%AF%E7%94%B1%E5%8F%AF%E8%A7%81%E5%85%89%E8%B0%B1%E4%B8%AD%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E6%B3%A2%E9%95%BF%E7%9A%84%E5%85%89%E6%B3%A2%E7%BB%84%E6%88%90%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="当光照射到物体上时，一部分被吸收，一部分被反射，反射的光色即人眼所见到的物体表面的色彩。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%BD%93%E5%85%89%E7%85%A7%E5%B0%84%E5%88%B0%E7%89%A9%E4%BD%93%E4%B8%8A%E6%97%B6%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%80%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E8%A2%AB%E5%90%B8%E6%94%B6%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%80%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E8%A2%AB%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%84%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%84%E7%9A%84%E5%85%89%E8%89%B2%E5%8D%B3%E4%BA%BA%E7%9C%BC%E6%89%80%E8%A7%81%E5%88%B0%E7%9A%84%E7%89%A9%E4%BD%93%E8%A1%A8%E9%9D%A2%E7%9A%84%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="光色的混合称为加色混合。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%85%89%E8%89%B2%E7%9A%84%E6%B7%B7%E5%90%88%E7%A7%B0%E4%B8%BA%E5%8A%A0%E8%89%B2%E6%B7%B7%E5%90%88%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="两个光色混合时，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%A4%E4%B8%AA%E5%85%89%E8%89%B2%E6%B7%B7%E5%90%88%E6%97%B6%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="其色相在二色之间，明度是二色的明度之和，彩度弱于二色中的强色。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%85%B6%E8%89%B2%E7%9B%B8%E5%9C%A8%E4%BA%8C%E8%89%B2%E4%B9%8B%E9%97%B4%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%8E%E5%BA%A6%E6%98%AF%E4%BA%8C%E8%89%B2%E7%9A%84%E6%98%8E%E5%BA%A6%E4%B9%8B%E5%92%8C%EF%BC%8C%E5%BD%A9%E5%BA%A6%E5%BC%B1%E4%BA%8E%E4%BA%8C%E8%89%B2%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E5%BC%BA%E8%89%B2%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="光色三原色等量混合时为白色。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%85%89%E8%89%B2%E4%B8%89%E5%8E%9F%E8%89%B2%E7%AD%89%E9%87%8F%E6%B7%B7%E5%90%88%E6%97%B6%E4%B8%BA%E7%99%BD%E8%89%B2%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="2.光色与物色" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2.%E5%85%89%E8%89%B2%E4%B8%8E%E7%89%A9%E8%89%B2%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="色彩的三原色分为光色的三原色及物色的三原色。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%89%E5%8E%9F%E8%89%B2%E5%88%86%E4%B8%BA%E5%85%89%E8%89%B2%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%89%E5%8E%9F%E8%89%B2%E5%8F%8A%E7%89%A9%E8%89%B2%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%89%E5%8E%9F%E8%89%B2%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="两个光色原色的混合色与一个物色的原色相同。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%A4%E4%B8%AA%E5%85%89%E8%89%B2%E5%8E%9F%E8%89%B2%E7%9A%84%E6%B7%B7%E5%90%88%E8%89%B2%E4%B8%8E%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E7%89%A9%E8%89%B2%E7%9A%84%E5%8E%9F%E8%89%B2%E7%9B%B8%E5%90%8C%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="两个物色原色的混合色与一个光色的原色相同。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%A4%E4%B8%AA%E7%89%A9%E8%89%B2%E5%8E%9F%E8%89%B2%E7%9A%84%E6%B7%B7%E5%90%88%E8%89%B2%E4%B8%8E%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E5%85%89%E8%89%B2%E7%9A%84%E5%8E%9F%E8%89%B2%E7%9B%B8%E5%90%8C%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="颜色的混合称为减色混合。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%A2%9C%E8%89%B2%E7%9A%84%E6%B7%B7%E5%90%88%E7%A7%B0%E4%B8%BA%E5%87%8F%E8%89%B2%E6%B7%B7%E5%90%88%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="当两个颜色混合时，其色相在二色之间，明度低于二色，彩度不一定减弱。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%BD%93%E4%B8%A4%E4%B8%AA%E9%A2%9C%E8%89%B2%E6%B7%B7%E5%90%88%E6%97%B6%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%B6%E8%89%B2%E7%9B%B8%E5%9C%A8%E4%BA%8C%E8%89%B2%E4%B9%8B%E9%97%B4%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%8E%E5%BA%A6%E4%BD%8E%E4%BA%8E%E4%BA%8C%E8%89%B2%EF%BC%8C%E5%BD%A9%E5%BA%A6%E4%B8%8D%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%9A%E5%87%8F%E5%BC%B1%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="颜色三原色等量混合时为黑色或灰色。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%A2%9C%E8%89%B2%E4%B8%89%E5%8E%9F%E8%89%B2%E7%AD%89%E9%87%8F%E6%B7%B7%E5%90%88%E6%97%B6%E4%B8%BA%E9%BB%91%E8%89%B2%E6%88%96%E7%81%B0%E8%89%B2%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="用明度（V）、色相（H）、彩度（C）的物理量来衡量色彩。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%94%A8%E6%98%8E%E5%BA%A6%EF%BC%88V%EF%BC%89%E3%80%81%E8%89%B2%E7%9B%B8%EF%BC%88H%EF%BC%89%E3%80%81%E5%BD%A9%E5%BA%A6%EF%BC%88C%EF%BC%89%E7%9A%84%E7%89%A9%E7%90%86%E9%87%8F%E6%9D%A5%E8%A1%A1%E9%87%8F%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（1）明度：色彩的深浅或明暗程度称为明度。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E6%98%8E%E5%BA%A6%EF%BC%9A%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E7%9A%84%E6%B7%B1%E6%B5%85%E6%88%96%E6%98%8E%E6%9A%97%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%A6%E7%A7%B0%E4%B8%BA%E6%98%8E%E5%BA%A6%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（2）色相：红、橙、黄、绿、青、蓝、紫等色调称为色相。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E8%89%B2%E7%9B%B8%EF%BC%9A%E7%BA%A2%E3%80%81%E6%A9%99%E3%80%81%E9%BB%84%E3%80%81%E7%BB%BF%E3%80%81%E9%9D%92%E3%80%81%E8%93%9D%E3%80%81%E7%B4%AB%E7%AD%89%E8%89%B2%E8%B0%83%E7%A7%B0%E4%B8%BA%E8%89%B2%E7%9B%B8%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（3）彩度：色彩的纯度或鲜艳程度称为彩度。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E5%BD%A9%E5%BA%A6%EF%BC%9A%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E7%9A%84%E7%BA%AF%E5%BA%A6%E6%88%96%E9%B2%9C%E8%89%B3%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%A6%E7%A7%B0%E4%B8%BA%E5%BD%A9%E5%BA%A6%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="4.色彩系统与色卡" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E4.%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E4%B8%8E%E8%89%B2%E5%8D%A1%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="色彩大致可以分为两类，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E5%A4%A7%E8%87%B4%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E5%88%86%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%A4%E7%B1%BB%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="第一类是以色度学理论为基础的表色系统，如美国的孟塞尔颜色系统、CIE颜色系统、瑞典NCS色彩系统、中国CNCS色彩系统等。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E7%B1%BB%E6%98%AF%E4%BB%A5%E8%89%B2%E5%BA%A6%E5%AD%A6%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA%E4%B8%BA%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E7%9A%84%E8%A1%A8%E8%89%B2%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%EF%BC%8C%E5%A6%82%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E7%9A%84%E5%AD%9F%E5%A1%9E%E5%B0%94%E9%A2%9C%E8%89%B2%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E3%80%81CIE%E9%A2%9C%E8%89%B2%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E3%80%81%E7%91%9E%E5%85%B8NCS%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E3%80%81%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BDCNCS%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%AD%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="第二类是以应用为目的的各种实物的色卡体系，如德国的RAL工业标准色彩体系、美国的PANTONE色彩体系、日本的DIC色彩体系等。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E7%B1%BB%E6%98%AF%E4%BB%A5%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%E4%B8%BA%E7%9B%AE%E7%9A%84%E7%9A%84%E5%90%84%E7%A7%8D%E5%AE%9E%E7%89%A9%E7%9A%84%E8%89%B2%E5%8D%A1%E4%BD%93%E7%B3%BB%EF%BC%8C%E5%A6%82%E5%BE%B7%E5%9B%BD%E7%9A%84RAL%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%9A%E6%A0%87%E5%87%86%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E4%BD%93%E7%B3%BB%E3%80%81%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E7%9A%84PANTONE%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E4%BD%93%E7%B3%BB%E3%80%81%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E7%9A%84DIC%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E4%BD%93%E7%B3%BB%E7%AD%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      </outline>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（二）色彩的认知" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%BA%8C%EF%BC%89%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%A4%E7%9F%A5%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="不同的色彩并置时，由于人的视觉器官或视觉联想的作用，会给人带来不同的主观感受。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E7%9A%84%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E5%B9%B6%E7%BD%AE%E6%97%B6%EF%BC%8C%E7%94%B1%E4%BA%8E%E4%BA%BA%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%86%E8%A7%89%E5%99%A8%E5%AE%98%E6%88%96%E8%A7%86%E8%A7%89%E8%81%94%E6%83%B3%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%9C%E7%94%A8%EF%BC%8C%E4%BC%9A%E7%BB%99%E4%BA%BA%E5%B8%A6%E6%9D%A5%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%BB%E8%A7%82%E6%84%9F%E5%8F%97%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="1.色彩的温度感" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1.%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E7%9A%84%E6%B8%A9%E5%BA%A6%E6%84%9F%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="不同的色彩常会产生不同的温度感。例如红、黄色令人感觉温暖，青、绿色令人感觉寒冷。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E7%9A%84%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E5%B8%B8%E4%BC%9A%E4%BA%A7%E7%94%9F%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E7%9A%84%E6%B8%A9%E5%BA%A6%E6%84%9F%E3%80%82%E4%BE%8B%E5%A6%82%E7%BA%A2%E3%80%81%E9%BB%84%E8%89%B2%E4%BB%A4%E4%BA%BA%E6%84%9F%E8%A7%89%E6%B8%A9%E6%9A%96%EF%BC%8C%E9%9D%92%E3%80%81%E7%BB%BF%E8%89%B2%E4%BB%A4%E4%BA%BA%E6%84%9F%E8%A7%89%E5%AF%92%E5%86%B7%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="故前者称为暖色系，后者称为冷色系。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%95%85%E5%89%8D%E8%80%85%E7%A7%B0%E4%B8%BA%E6%9A%96%E8%89%B2%E7%B3%BB%EF%BC%8C%E5%90%8E%E8%80%85%E7%A7%B0%E4%B8%BA%E5%86%B7%E8%89%B2%E7%B3%BB%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="但色彩的冷暖又是相对的。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BD%86%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E7%9A%84%E5%86%B7%E6%9A%96%E5%8F%88%E6%98%AF%E7%9B%B8%E5%AF%B9%E7%9A%84%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="紫与橙并列，紫就倾向于冷色，紫与青并列紫就倾向于暖色。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%B4%AB%E4%B8%8E%E6%A9%99%E5%B9%B6%E5%88%97%EF%BC%8C%E7%B4%AB%E5%B0%B1%E5%80%BE%E5%90%91%E4%BA%8E%E5%86%B7%E8%89%B2%EF%BC%8C%E7%B4%AB%E4%B8%8E%E9%9D%92%E5%B9%B6%E5%88%97%E7%B4%AB%E5%B0%B1%E5%80%BE%E5%90%91%E4%BA%8E%E6%9A%96%E8%89%B2%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="绿、紫在高时近于冷色，而黄绿、紫红在彩度高时近于暖色。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%BB%BF%E3%80%81%E7%B4%AB%E5%9C%A8%E9%AB%98%E6%97%B6%E8%BF%91%E4%BA%8E%E5%86%B7%E8%89%B2%EF%BC%8C%E8%80%8C%E9%BB%84%E7%BB%BF%E3%80%81%E7%B4%AB%E7%BA%A2%E5%9C%A8%E5%BD%A9%E5%BA%A6%E9%AB%98%E6%97%B6%E8%BF%91%E4%BA%8E%E6%9A%96%E8%89%B2%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="3.色彩三要素" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E3.%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E4%B8%89%E8%A6%81%E7%B4%A0%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="当色彩的面积增大时，在感觉上有彩度增强、明度升高的现象，因此在确定大面积色彩时，不能以小面积色彩样板来决定。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%BD%93%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E7%9A%84%E9%9D%A2%E7%A7%AF%E5%A2%9E%E5%A4%A7%E6%97%B6%EF%BC%8C%E5%9C%A8%E6%84%9F%E8%A7%89%E4%B8%8A%E6%9C%89%E5%BD%A9%E5%BA%A6%E5%A2%9E%E5%BC%BA%E3%80%81%E6%98%8E%E5%BA%A6%E5%8D%87%E9%AB%98%E7%9A%84%E7%8E%B0%E8%B1%A1%EF%BC%8C%E5%9B%A0%E6%AD%A4%E5%9C%A8%E7%A1%AE%E5%AE%9A%E5%A4%A7%E9%9D%A2%E7%A7%AF%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E6%97%B6%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E4%BB%A5%E5%B0%8F%E9%9D%A2%E7%A7%AF%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E6%A0%B7%E6%9D%BF%E6%9D%A5%E5%86%B3%E5%AE%9A%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="在注视甲色20~30s后，迅速移视乙色时，感觉乙色带有甲色的补色。例如看了黄色墙壁后再看红花，感觉红花带有紫色。这种现象称为连续对比。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9C%A8%E6%B3%A8%E8%A7%86%E7%94%B2%E8%89%B220~30s%E5%90%8E%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%85%E9%80%9F%E7%A7%BB%E8%A7%86%E4%B9%99%E8%89%B2%E6%97%B6%EF%BC%8C%E6%84%9F%E8%A7%89%E4%B9%99%E8%89%B2%E5%B8%A6%E6%9C%89%E7%94%B2%E8%89%B2%E7%9A%84%E8%A1%A5%E8%89%B2%E3%80%82%E4%BE%8B%E5%A6%82%E7%9C%8B%E4%BA%86%E9%BB%84%E8%89%B2%E5%A2%99%E5%A3%81%E5%90%8E%E5%86%8D%E7%9C%8B%E7%BA%A2%E8%8A%B1%EF%BC%8C%E6%84%9F%E8%A7%89%E7%BA%A2%E8%8A%B1%E5%B8%A6%E6%9C%89%E7%B4%AB%E8%89%B2%E3%80%82%E8%BF%99%E7%A7%8D%E7%8E%B0%E8%B1%A1%E7%A7%B0%E4%B8%BA%E8%BF%9E%E7%BB%AD%E5%AF%B9%E6%AF%94%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="在注视一个色彩图形一段时间之后，忽然移视任意背景，即出现一个同样形状的补色图形，即补色的残像。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9C%A8%E6%B3%A8%E8%A7%86%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E5%9B%BE%E5%BD%A2%E4%B8%80%E6%AE%B5%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%E4%B9%8B%E5%90%8E%EF%BC%8C%E5%BF%BD%E7%84%B6%E7%A7%BB%E8%A7%86%E4%BB%BB%E6%84%8F%E8%83%8C%E6%99%AF%EF%BC%8C%E5%8D%B3%E5%87%BA%E7%8E%B0%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E5%90%8C%E6%A0%B7%E5%BD%A2%E7%8A%B6%E7%9A%84%E8%A1%A5%E8%89%B2%E5%9B%BE%E5%BD%A2%EF%BC%8C%E5%8D%B3%E8%A1%A5%E8%89%B2%E7%9A%84%E6%AE%8B%E5%83%8F%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="在建筑色彩设计时，要经常利用或避免这种现象，来提高视觉条件或消除视觉疲劳等。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9C%A8%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E6%97%B6%EF%BC%8C%E8%A6%81%E7%BB%8F%E5%B8%B8%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8%E6%88%96%E9%81%BF%E5%85%8D%E8%BF%99%E7%A7%8D%E7%8E%B0%E8%B1%A1%EF%BC%8C%E6%9D%A5%E6%8F%90%E9%AB%98%E8%A7%86%E8%A7%89%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%E6%88%96%E6%B6%88%E9%99%A4%E8%A7%86%E8%A7%89%E7%96%B2%E5%8A%B3%E7%AD%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="所产生的视觉残像。在医院中一般避免使用与紫色邻近的色彩，以防病人相视时，面部蒙上不健康的黄绿色。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%89%80%E4%BA%A7%E7%94%9F%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%86%E8%A7%89%E6%AE%8B%E5%83%8F%E3%80%82%E5%9C%A8%E5%8C%BB%E9%99%A2%E4%B8%AD%E4%B8%80%E8%88%AC%E9%81%BF%E5%85%8D%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E4%B8%8E%E7%B4%AB%E8%89%B2%E9%82%BB%E8%BF%91%E7%9A%84%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A5%E9%98%B2%E7%97%85%E4%BA%BA%E7%9B%B8%E8%A7%86%E6%97%B6%EF%BC%8C%E9%9D%A2%E9%83%A8%E8%92%99%E4%B8%8A%E4%B8%8D%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%E7%9A%84%E9%BB%84%E7%BB%BF%E8%89%B2%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="在手术室里为了避免医生在高照度下注视血色过久而产生的补色残像，宜采用淡青绿色（或淡青色）为室内背景。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9C%A8%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%AF%E5%AE%A4%E9%87%8C%E4%B8%BA%E4%BA%86%E9%81%BF%E5%85%8D%E5%8C%BB%E7%94%9F%E5%9C%A8%E9%AB%98%E7%85%A7%E5%BA%A6%E4%B8%8B%E6%B3%A8%E8%A7%86%E8%A1%80%E8%89%B2%E8%BF%87%E4%B9%85%E8%80%8C%E4%BA%A7%E7%94%9F%E7%9A%84%E8%A1%A5%E8%89%B2%E6%AE%8B%E5%83%8F%EF%BC%8C%E5%AE%9C%E9%87%87%E7%94%A8%E6%B7%A1%E9%9D%92%E7%BB%BF%E8%89%B2%EF%BC%88%E6%88%96%E6%B7%A1%E9%9D%92%E8%89%B2%EF%BC%89%E4%B8%BA%E5%AE%A4%E5%86%85%E8%83%8C%E6%99%AF%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="为了使运动员的动作看得更清晰，在体育馆内宜采用青绿色等的装修背景。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%BA%E4%BA%86%E4%BD%BF%E8%BF%90%E5%8A%A8%E5%91%98%E7%9A%84%E5%8A%A8%E4%BD%9C%E7%9C%8B%E5%BE%97%E6%9B%B4%E6%B8%85%E6%99%B0%EF%BC%8C%E5%9C%A8%E4%BD%93%E8%82%B2%E9%A6%86%E5%86%85%E5%AE%9C%E9%87%87%E7%94%A8%E9%9D%92%E7%BB%BF%E8%89%B2%E7%AD%89%E7%9A%84%E8%A3%85%E4%BF%AE%E8%83%8C%E6%99%AF%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="两色并列时的对比变化：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%A4%E8%89%B2%E5%B9%B6%E5%88%97%E6%97%B6%E7%9A%84%E5%AF%B9%E6%AF%94%E5%8F%98%E5%8C%96%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="明度对比：两个明暗不同的色彩并列时，明的更明，暗的更暗。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%98%8E%E5%BA%A6%E5%AF%B9%E6%AF%94%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%A4%E4%B8%AA%E6%98%8E%E6%9A%97%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E7%9A%84%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E5%B9%B6%E5%88%97%E6%97%B6%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%8E%E7%9A%84%E6%9B%B4%E6%98%8E%EF%BC%8C%E6%9A%97%E7%9A%84%E6%9B%B4%E6%9A%97%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="彩度对比：两个强弱不同的色彩并列时，强的更强，弱的更弱。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%BD%A9%E5%BA%A6%E5%AF%B9%E6%AF%94%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%A4%E4%B8%AA%E5%BC%BA%E5%BC%B1%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E7%9A%84%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E5%B9%B6%E5%88%97%E6%97%B6%EF%BC%8C%E5%BC%BA%E7%9A%84%E6%9B%B4%E5%BC%BA%EF%BC%8C%E5%BC%B1%E7%9A%84%E6%9B%B4%E5%BC%B1%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="彩度对比：两个强弱不同的色彩并列时，强的更强，弱的更弱。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%BD%A9%E5%BA%A6%E5%AF%B9%E6%AF%94%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%A4%E4%B8%AA%E5%BC%BA%E5%BC%B1%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E7%9A%84%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E5%B9%B6%E5%88%97%E6%97%B6%EF%BC%8C%E5%BC%BA%E7%9A%84%E6%9B%B4%E5%BC%BA%EF%BC%8C%E5%BC%B1%E7%9A%84%E6%9B%B4%E5%BC%B1%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="色相对比：两个色相不同的色彩并列时，在色相环上有分别向相反方向偏移的感觉。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%89%B2%E7%9B%B8%E5%AF%B9%E6%AF%94%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%A4%E4%B8%AA%E8%89%B2%E7%9B%B8%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E7%9A%84%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E5%B9%B6%E5%88%97%E6%97%B6%EF%BC%8C%E5%9C%A8%E8%89%B2%E7%9B%B8%E7%8E%AF%E4%B8%8A%E6%9C%89%E5%88%86%E5%88%AB%E5%90%91%E7%9B%B8%E5%8F%8D%E6%96%B9%E5%90%91%E5%81%8F%E7%A7%BB%E7%9A%84%E6%84%9F%E8%A7%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      </outline>
    </outline>
    <outline text="2.色彩的对比现象" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2.%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E7%9A%84%E5%AF%B9%E6%AF%94%E7%8E%B0%E8%B1%A1%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="同一色彩在背景色彩或相邻色彩不同，会产生不同的感觉，这种现象称为同时对比，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%90%8C%E4%B8%80%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E5%9C%A8%E8%83%8C%E6%99%AF%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E6%88%96%E7%9B%B8%E9%82%BB%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%EF%BC%8C%E4%BC%9A%E4%BA%A7%E7%94%9F%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E7%9A%84%E6%84%9F%E8%A7%89%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%99%E7%A7%8D%E7%8E%B0%E8%B1%A1%E7%A7%B0%E4%B8%BA%E5%90%8C%E6%97%B6%E5%AF%B9%E6%AF%94%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="在并列的两种色彩的接触边缘上最显著，故接触周边越长或面积相差越大时，影响越大。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9C%A8%E5%B9%B6%E5%88%97%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%A4%E7%A7%8D%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E7%9A%84%E6%8E%A5%E8%A7%A6%E8%BE%B9%E7%BC%98%E4%B8%8A%E6%9C%80%E6%98%BE%E8%91%97%EF%BC%8C%E6%95%85%E6%8E%A5%E8%A7%A6%E5%91%A8%E8%BE%B9%E8%B6%8A%E9%95%BF%E6%88%96%E9%9D%A2%E7%A7%AF%E7%9B%B8%E5%B7%AE%E8%B6%8A%E5%A4%A7%E6%97%B6%EF%BC%8C%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%E8%B6%8A%E5%A4%A7%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="一块色彩的明度高于背景，或与冷色背景互补时，这块色彩有扩大感，反之则有缩小感。此即所谓光渗现象。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%80%E5%9D%97%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E7%9A%84%E6%98%8E%E5%BA%A6%E9%AB%98%E4%BA%8E%E8%83%8C%E6%99%AF%EF%BC%8C%E6%88%96%E4%B8%8E%E5%86%B7%E8%89%B2%E8%83%8C%E6%99%AF%E4%BA%92%E8%A1%A5%E6%97%B6%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%99%E5%9D%97%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E6%9C%89%E6%89%A9%E5%A4%A7%E6%84%9F%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%8D%E4%B9%8B%E5%88%99%E6%9C%89%E7%BC%A9%E5%B0%8F%E6%84%9F%E3%80%82%E6%AD%A4%E5%8D%B3%E6%89%80%E8%B0%93%E5%85%89%E6%B8%97%E7%8E%B0%E8%B1%A1%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="将一个色彩图样置于另一个色彩背景上，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%B0%86%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E5%9B%BE%E6%A0%B7%E7%BD%AE%E4%BA%8E%E5%8F%A6%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E8%83%8C%E6%99%AF%E4%B8%8A%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="在观测条件相同时，能清楚地识别图样色彩的最大距离，称为色彩的识别距离。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9C%A8%E8%A7%82%E6%B5%8B%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%E7%9B%B8%E5%90%8C%E6%97%B6%EF%BC%8C%E8%83%BD%E6%B8%85%E6%A5%9A%E5%9C%B0%E8%AF%86%E5%88%AB%E5%9B%BE%E6%A0%B7%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7%E8%B7%9D%E7%A6%BB%EF%BC%8C%E7%A7%B0%E4%B8%BA%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E7%9A%84%E8%AF%86%E5%88%AB%E8%B7%9D%E7%A6%BB%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="它随着图样与背景两色之间的明度差、色相差及彩度差的增大而增大。其中以明度差的影响最大。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%AE%83%E9%9A%8F%E7%9D%80%E5%9B%BE%E6%A0%B7%E4%B8%8E%E8%83%8C%E6%99%AF%E4%B8%A4%E8%89%B2%E4%B9%8B%E9%97%B4%E7%9A%84%E6%98%8E%E5%BA%A6%E5%B7%AE%E3%80%81%E8%89%B2%E7%9B%B8%E5%B7%AE%E5%8F%8A%E5%BD%A9%E5%BA%A6%E5%B7%AE%E7%9A%84%E5%A2%9E%E5%A4%A7%E8%80%8C%E5%A2%9E%E5%A4%A7%E3%80%82%E5%85%B6%E4%B8%AD%E4%BB%A5%E6%98%8E%E5%BA%A6%E5%B7%AE%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="4.色彩的重量感" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E4.%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E7%9A%84%E9%87%8D%E9%87%8F%E6%84%9F%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="色彩的重量感以明度的影响最大，一般是暗色感觉重而明色感觉轻。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E7%9A%84%E9%87%8D%E9%87%8F%E6%84%9F%E4%BB%A5%E6%98%8E%E5%BA%A6%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%80%E8%88%AC%E6%98%AF%E6%9A%97%E8%89%B2%E6%84%9F%E8%A7%89%E9%87%8D%E8%80%8C%E6%98%8E%E8%89%B2%E6%84%9F%E8%A7%89%E8%BD%BB%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="同时彩度强的暖色感觉重，彩度弱的冷色感觉轻。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%90%8C%E6%97%B6%E5%BD%A9%E5%BA%A6%E5%BC%BA%E7%9A%84%E6%9A%96%E8%89%B2%E6%84%9F%E8%A7%89%E9%87%8D%EF%BC%8C%E5%BD%A9%E5%BA%A6%E5%BC%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%86%B7%E8%89%B2%E6%84%9F%E8%A7%89%E8%BD%BB%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="在建筑色彩设计中，为了达到安定、稳重的效果，宜采用重感色，如机械设备的基座及各种装修台座等。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9C%A8%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E4%B8%AD%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%BA%E4%BA%86%E8%BE%BE%E5%88%B0%E5%AE%89%E5%AE%9A%E3%80%81%E7%A8%B3%E9%87%8D%E7%9A%84%E6%95%88%E6%9E%9C%EF%BC%8C%E5%AE%9C%E9%87%87%E7%94%A8%E9%87%8D%E6%84%9F%E8%89%B2%EF%BC%8C%E5%A6%82%E6%9C%BA%E6%A2%B0%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%BA%E5%BA%A7%E5%8F%8A%E5%90%84%E7%A7%8D%E8%A3%85%E4%BF%AE%E5%8F%B0%E5%BA%A7%E7%AD%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="为了要达到灵活、轻快的效果，宜采用轻感色，如行走在车间上部的吊车、悬挂在顶棚上的灯具、风扇等。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%BA%E4%BA%86%E8%A6%81%E8%BE%BE%E5%88%B0%E7%81%B5%E6%B4%BB%E3%80%81%E8%BD%BB%E5%BF%AB%E7%9A%84%E6%95%88%E6%9E%9C%EF%BC%8C%E5%AE%9C%E9%87%87%E7%94%A8%E8%BD%BB%E6%84%9F%E8%89%B2%EF%BC%8C%E5%A6%82%E8%A1%8C%E8%B5%B0%E5%9C%A8%E8%BD%A6%E9%97%B4%E4%B8%8A%E9%83%A8%E7%9A%84%E5%90%8A%E8%BD%A6%E3%80%81%E6%82%AC%E6%8C%82%E5%9C%A8%E9%A1%B6%E6%A3%9A%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E7%81%AF%E5%85%B7%E3%80%81%E9%A3%8E%E6%89%87%E7%AD%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="通常室内的色彩处理多是自上而下，由轻到重的。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%80%9A%E5%B8%B8%E5%AE%A4%E5%86%85%E7%9A%84%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86%E5%A4%9A%E6%98%AF%E8%87%AA%E4%B8%8A%E8%80%8C%E4%B8%8B%EF%BC%8C%E7%94%B1%E8%BD%BB%E5%88%B0%E9%87%8D%E7%9A%84%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="5.色彩的醒目性" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E5.%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E7%9A%84%E9%86%92%E7%9B%AE%E6%80%A7%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="色彩的醒目性指其易于引起人们注意的性质，具有醒目性的色彩，从较远处就能识别出来。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E7%9A%84%E9%86%92%E7%9B%AE%E6%80%A7%E6%8C%87%E5%85%B6%E6%98%93%E4%BA%8E%E5%BC%95%E8%B5%B7%E4%BA%BA%E4%BB%AC%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F%E7%9A%84%E6%80%A7%E8%B4%A8%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%B7%E6%9C%89%E9%86%92%E7%9B%AE%E6%80%A7%E7%9A%84%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%8E%E8%BE%83%E8%BF%9C%E5%A4%84%E5%B0%B1%E8%83%BD%E8%AF%86%E5%88%AB%E5%87%BA%E6%9D%A5%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="建筑色彩的醒目性主要受其色相的影响，同时也取决于其与背景色之间的关系。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E7%9A%84%E9%86%92%E7%9B%AE%E6%80%A7%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E5%8F%97%E5%85%B6%E8%89%B2%E7%9B%B8%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%EF%BC%8C%E5%90%8C%E6%97%B6%E4%B9%9F%E5%8F%96%E5%86%B3%E4%BA%8E%E5%85%B6%E4%B8%8E%E8%83%8C%E6%99%AF%E8%89%B2%E4%B9%8B%E9%97%B4%E7%9A%84%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      </outline>
      <outline text="色彩的诱目性指在眼睛无意观看的情况下，易于引起注意的性质。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E7%9A%84%E8%AF%B1%E7%9B%AE%E6%80%A7%E6%8C%87%E5%9C%A8%E7%9C%BC%E7%9D%9B%E6%97%A0%E6%84%8F%E8%A7%82%E7%9C%8B%E7%9A%84%E6%83%85%E5%86%B5%E4%B8%8B%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%93%E4%BA%8E%E5%BC%95%E8%B5%B7%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F%E7%9A%84%E6%80%A7%E8%B4%A8%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="具有诱目性的色彩，从较远处能明显地识别出来。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%85%B7%E6%9C%89%E8%AF%B1%E7%9B%AE%E6%80%A7%E7%9A%84%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%8E%E8%BE%83%E8%BF%9C%E5%A4%84%E8%83%BD%E6%98%8E%E6%98%BE%E5%9C%B0%E8%AF%86%E5%88%AB%E5%87%BA%E6%9D%A5%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="建筑色彩的诱目性主要受其色相的影响。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E7%9A%84%E8%AF%B1%E7%9B%AE%E6%80%A7%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E5%8F%97%E5%85%B6%E8%89%B2%E7%9B%B8%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      </outline>
      <outline text="光色的诱目性顺序是红青&gt;黄&gt;绿一自；物体色的诱目性是红色&gt;橙色与黄色。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%85%89%E8%89%B2%E7%9A%84%E8%AF%B1%E7%9B%AE%E6%80%A7%E9%A1%BA%E5%BA%8F%E6%98%AF%E7%BA%A2%E9%9D%92&amp;gt;%E9%BB%84&amp;gt;%E7%BB%BF%E4%B8%80%E8%87%AA%EF%BC%9B%E7%89%A9%E4%BD%93%E8%89%B2%E7%9A%84%E8%AF%B1%E7%9B%AE%E6%80%A7%E6%98%AF%E7%BA%A2%E8%89%B2&amp;gt;%E6%A9%99%E8%89%B2%E4%B8%8E%E9%BB%84%E8%89%B2%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="例如：殿堂、牌楼等的红色柱子，走廊、楼梯间铺设的红色地毯等就特别诱目。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BE%8B%E5%A6%82%EF%BC%9A%E6%AE%BF%E5%A0%82%E3%80%81%E7%89%8C%E6%A5%BC%E7%AD%89%E7%9A%84%E7%BA%A2%E8%89%B2%E6%9F%B1%E5%AD%90%EF%BC%8C%E8%B5%B0%E5%BB%8A%E3%80%81%E6%A5%BC%E6%A2%AF%E9%97%B4%E9%93%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%9A%84%E7%BA%A2%E8%89%B2%E5%9C%B0%E6%AF%AF%E7%AD%89%E5%B0%B1%E7%89%B9%E5%88%AB%E8%AF%B1%E7%9B%AE%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      </outline>
      <outline text="建筑色彩的诱目性还取决于它本身和其背景色彩的关系，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E7%9A%84%E8%AF%B1%E7%9B%AE%E6%80%A7%E8%BF%98%E5%8F%96%E5%86%B3%E4%BA%8E%E5%AE%83%E6%9C%AC%E8%BA%AB%E5%92%8C%E5%85%B6%E8%83%8C%E6%99%AF%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E7%9A%84%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="例如在黑色或中灰色的背景下，诱目的顺序是黄、橙、红绿、青，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BE%8B%E5%A6%82%E5%9C%A8%E9%BB%91%E8%89%B2%E6%88%96%E4%B8%AD%E7%81%B0%E8%89%B2%E7%9A%84%E8%83%8C%E6%99%AF%E4%B8%8B%EF%BC%8C%E8%AF%B1%E7%9B%AE%E7%9A%84%E9%A1%BA%E5%BA%8F%E6%98%AF%E9%BB%84%E3%80%81%E6%A9%99%E3%80%81%E7%BA%A2%E7%BB%BF%E3%80%81%E9%9D%92%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="在白色背景下的顺序是青、绿、红、橙、黄。各种安全标志常利用色彩的诱目性。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9C%A8%E7%99%BD%E8%89%B2%E8%83%8C%E6%99%AF%E4%B8%8B%E7%9A%84%E9%A1%BA%E5%BA%8F%E6%98%AF%E9%9D%92%E3%80%81%E7%BB%BF%E3%80%81%E7%BA%A2%E3%80%81%E6%A9%99%E3%80%81%E9%BB%84%E3%80%82%E5%90%84%E7%A7%8D%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E6%A0%87%E5%BF%97%E5%B8%B8%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E7%9A%84%E8%AF%B1%E7%9B%AE%E6%80%A7%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      </outline>
    </outline>
    <outline text="3.色彩的空间感" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E3.%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E7%9A%84%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E6%84%9F%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="色彩的距离感觉，以色相和明度影响最大。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E7%9A%84%E8%B7%9D%E7%A6%BB%E6%84%9F%E8%A7%89%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A5%E8%89%B2%E7%9B%B8%E5%92%8C%E6%98%8E%E5%BA%A6%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="一般高明度的暖色系色彩感觉凸出、扩大，称为凸出色或近感色；低明度的冷色系色彩感觉后退、缩小，称为后退色或远感色。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%80%E8%88%AC%E9%AB%98%E6%98%8E%E5%BA%A6%E7%9A%84%E6%9A%96%E8%89%B2%E7%B3%BB%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E6%84%9F%E8%A7%89%E5%87%B8%E5%87%BA%E3%80%81%E6%89%A9%E5%A4%A7%EF%BC%8C%E7%A7%B0%E4%B8%BA%E5%87%B8%E5%87%BA%E8%89%B2%E6%88%96%E8%BF%91%E6%84%9F%E8%89%B2%EF%BC%9B%E4%BD%8E%E6%98%8E%E5%BA%A6%E7%9A%84%E5%86%B7%E8%89%B2%E7%B3%BB%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E6%84%9F%E8%A7%89%E5%90%8E%E9%80%80%E3%80%81%E7%BC%A9%E5%B0%8F%EF%BC%8C%E7%A7%B0%E4%B8%BA%E5%90%8E%E9%80%80%E8%89%B2%E6%88%96%E8%BF%9C%E6%84%9F%E8%89%B2%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="如白和黄的明度最高，凸出感也最强，青和紫的明度最低，后退感最显著。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%A6%82%E7%99%BD%E5%92%8C%E9%BB%84%E7%9A%84%E6%98%8E%E5%BA%A6%E6%9C%80%E9%AB%98%EF%BC%8C%E5%87%B8%E5%87%BA%E6%84%9F%E4%B9%9F%E6%9C%80%E5%BC%BA%EF%BC%8C%E9%9D%92%E5%92%8C%E7%B4%AB%E7%9A%84%E6%98%8E%E5%BA%A6%E6%9C%80%E4%BD%8E%EF%BC%8C%E5%90%8E%E9%80%80%E6%84%9F%E6%9C%80%E6%98%BE%E8%91%97%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="但色彩的距离感也是相对的，且与其背景色彩有关，如绿色在较暗处也有凸出的倾向。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BD%86%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E7%9A%84%E8%B7%9D%E7%A6%BB%E6%84%9F%E4%B9%9F%E6%98%AF%E7%9B%B8%E5%AF%B9%E7%9A%84%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%94%E4%B8%8E%E5%85%B6%E8%83%8C%E6%99%AF%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E6%9C%89%E5%85%B3%EF%BC%8C%E5%A6%82%E7%BB%BF%E8%89%B2%E5%9C%A8%E8%BE%83%E6%9A%97%E5%A4%84%E4%B9%9F%E6%9C%89%E5%87%B8%E5%87%BA%E7%9A%84%E5%80%BE%E5%90%91%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="在建筑色彩设计时，常利用色彩的距离感来调整建筑物的尺度感和距离感。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9C%A8%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E6%97%B6%EF%BC%8C%E5%B8%B8%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E7%9A%84%E8%B7%9D%E7%A6%BB%E6%84%9F%E6%9D%A5%E8%B0%83%E6%95%B4%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%89%A9%E7%9A%84%E5%B0%BA%E5%BA%A6%E6%84%9F%E5%92%8C%E8%B7%9D%E7%A6%BB%E6%84%9F%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      </outline>
    </outline>
    <outline text="6.照明效果" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E6.%E7%85%A7%E6%98%8E%E6%95%88%E6%9E%9C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="色彩在照度高的地方，明度升高，彩度增强；在照度低的地方，则明度感觉随着色相不同而变。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E5%9C%A8%E7%85%A7%E5%BA%A6%E9%AB%98%E7%9A%84%E5%9C%B0%E6%96%B9%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%8E%E5%BA%A6%E5%8D%87%E9%AB%98%EF%BC%8C%E5%BD%A9%E5%BA%A6%E5%A2%9E%E5%BC%BA%EF%BC%9B%E5%9C%A8%E7%85%A7%E5%BA%A6%E4%BD%8E%E7%9A%84%E5%9C%B0%E6%96%B9%EF%BC%8C%E5%88%99%E6%98%8E%E5%BA%A6%E6%84%9F%E8%A7%89%E9%9A%8F%E7%9D%80%E8%89%B2%E7%9B%B8%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E8%80%8C%E5%8F%98%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="一般绿、青绿及青色系的色彩显得明亮，而红、橙及黄色系的色彩发暗。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%80%E8%88%AC%E7%BB%BF%E3%80%81%E9%9D%92%E7%BB%BF%E5%8F%8A%E9%9D%92%E8%89%B2%E7%B3%BB%E7%9A%84%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E6%98%BE%E5%BE%97%E6%98%8E%E4%BA%AE%EF%BC%8C%E8%80%8C%E7%BA%A2%E3%80%81%E6%A9%99%E5%8F%8A%E9%BB%84%E8%89%B2%E7%B3%BB%E7%9A%84%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E5%8F%91%E6%9A%97%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="室内配色的明度对室内的照度影响很大，故可应用色彩（主要是明度）来调节室内的照度及照度分布，同时由于照度的不同，色彩的效果也不同。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%AE%A4%E5%86%85%E9%85%8D%E8%89%B2%E7%9A%84%E6%98%8E%E5%BA%A6%E5%AF%B9%E5%AE%A4%E5%86%85%E7%9A%84%E7%85%A7%E5%BA%A6%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%E5%BE%88%E5%A4%A7%EF%BC%8C%E6%95%85%E5%8F%AF%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E6%98%AF%E6%98%8E%E5%BA%A6%EF%BC%89%E6%9D%A5%E8%B0%83%E8%8A%82%E5%AE%A4%E5%86%85%E7%9A%84%E7%85%A7%E5%BA%A6%E5%8F%8A%E7%85%A7%E5%BA%A6%E5%88%86%E5%B8%83%EF%BC%8C%E5%90%8C%E6%97%B6%E7%94%B1%E4%BA%8E%E7%85%A7%E5%BA%A6%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%EF%BC%8C%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E7%9A%84%E6%95%88%E6%9E%9C%E4%B9%9F%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      </outline>
      <outline text="如中国古建筑的配色，墙、柱、门窗多为红色，而檐下额枋、雀替、斗棋都是青绿色，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%A6%82%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%8F%A4%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%9A%84%E9%85%8D%E8%89%B2%EF%BC%8C%E5%A2%99%E3%80%81%E6%9F%B1%E3%80%81%E9%97%A8%E7%AA%97%E5%A4%9A%E4%B8%BA%E7%BA%A2%E8%89%B2%EF%BC%8C%E8%80%8C%E6%AA%90%E4%B8%8B%E9%A2%9D%E6%9E%8B%E3%80%81%E9%9B%80%E6%9B%BF%E3%80%81%E6%96%97%E6%A3%8B%E9%83%BD%E6%98%AF%E9%9D%92%E7%BB%BF%E8%89%B2%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="晴天时明暗对比很强，青绿色使檐下不致漆黑，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%99%B4%E5%A4%A9%E6%97%B6%E6%98%8E%E6%9A%97%E5%AF%B9%E6%AF%94%E5%BE%88%E5%BC%BA%EF%BC%8C%E9%9D%92%E7%BB%BF%E8%89%B2%E4%BD%BF%E6%AA%90%E4%B8%8B%E4%B8%8D%E8%87%B4%E6%BC%86%E9%BB%91%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="阴天时青绿色有深远的效果，能增强立体感。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%98%B4%E5%A4%A9%E6%97%B6%E9%9D%92%E7%BB%BF%E8%89%B2%E6%9C%89%E6%B7%B1%E8%BF%9C%E7%9A%84%E6%95%88%E6%9E%9C%EF%BC%8C%E8%83%BD%E5%A2%9E%E5%BC%BA%E7%AB%8B%E4%BD%93%E6%84%9F%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      </outline>
    </outline>
    <outline text="7.色彩疲劳感" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E7.%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E7%96%B2%E5%8A%B3%E6%84%9F%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="色彩的彩度越强，对人的刺激越大，就越易使人疲劳。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%A9%E5%BA%A6%E8%B6%8A%E5%BC%BA%EF%BC%8C%E5%AF%B9%E4%BA%BA%E7%9A%84%E5%88%BA%E6%BF%80%E8%B6%8A%E5%A4%A7%EF%BC%8C%E5%B0%B1%E8%B6%8A%E6%98%93%E4%BD%BF%E4%BA%BA%E7%96%B2%E5%8A%B3%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="一般暖色系的色彩，疲劳感较冷色系的色彩大，绿色则不显著。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%80%E8%88%AC%E6%9A%96%E8%89%B2%E7%B3%BB%E7%9A%84%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%EF%BC%8C%E7%96%B2%E5%8A%B3%E6%84%9F%E8%BE%83%E5%86%B7%E8%89%B2%E7%B3%BB%E7%9A%84%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E5%A4%A7%EF%BC%8C%E7%BB%BF%E8%89%B2%E5%88%99%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%BE%E8%91%97%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="许多色相在一起，明度差或彩度差较大时，易感觉疲劳。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%AE%B8%E5%A4%9A%E8%89%B2%E7%9B%B8%E5%9C%A8%E4%B8%80%E8%B5%B7%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%8E%E5%BA%A6%E5%B7%AE%E6%88%96%E5%BD%A9%E5%BA%A6%E5%B7%AE%E8%BE%83%E5%A4%A7%E6%97%B6%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%93%E6%84%9F%E8%A7%89%E7%96%B2%E5%8A%B3%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="故建筑色彩设计时，色相数不宜过多，彩度不宜过高。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%95%85%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E6%97%B6%EF%BC%8C%E8%89%B2%E7%9B%B8%E6%95%B0%E4%B8%8D%E5%AE%9C%E8%BF%87%E5%A4%9A%EF%BC%8C%E5%BD%A9%E5%BA%A6%E4%B8%8D%E5%AE%9C%E8%BF%87%E9%AB%98%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="色彩的疲劳感能引起彩度减弱，明度升高，逐渐呈灰色（略带黄），此为色觉的褪色现象。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E7%9A%84%E7%96%B2%E5%8A%B3%E6%84%9F%E8%83%BD%E5%BC%95%E8%B5%B7%E5%BD%A9%E5%BA%A6%E5%87%8F%E5%BC%B1%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%8E%E5%BA%A6%E5%8D%87%E9%AB%98%EF%BC%8C%E9%80%90%E6%B8%90%E5%91%88%E7%81%B0%E8%89%B2%EF%BC%88%E7%95%A5%E5%B8%A6%E9%BB%84%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%8C%E6%AD%A4%E4%B8%BA%E8%89%B2%E8%A7%89%E7%9A%84%E8%A4%AA%E8%89%B2%E7%8E%B0%E8%B1%A1%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="8.混色效果" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E8.%E6%B7%B7%E8%89%B2%E6%95%88%E6%9E%9C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="将不同的色彩交错均匀布置时，从远处看去，呈现此二色的混合感觉。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%B0%86%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E7%9A%84%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E4%BA%A4%E9%94%99%E5%9D%87%E5%8C%80%E5%B8%83%E7%BD%AE%E6%97%B6%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%8E%E8%BF%9C%E5%A4%84%E7%9C%8B%E5%8E%BB%EF%BC%8C%E5%91%88%E7%8E%B0%E6%AD%A4%E4%BA%8C%E8%89%B2%E7%9A%84%E6%B7%B7%E5%90%88%E6%84%9F%E8%A7%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="在建筑色彩设计时，要考虑远近相宜的色彩组合，如黑白石子掺和的水刷石呈现灰色，青砖勾红缝的清水砖墙呈现紫褐色等。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9C%A8%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E6%97%B6%EF%BC%8C%E8%A6%81%E8%80%83%E8%99%91%E8%BF%9C%E8%BF%91%E7%9B%B8%E5%AE%9C%E7%9A%84%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E7%BB%84%E5%90%88%EF%BC%8C%E5%A6%82%E9%BB%91%E7%99%BD%E7%9F%B3%E5%AD%90%E6%8E%BA%E5%92%8C%E7%9A%84%E6%B0%B4%E5%88%B7%E7%9F%B3%E5%91%88%E7%8E%B0%E7%81%B0%E8%89%B2%EF%BC%8C%E9%9D%92%E7%A0%96%E5%8B%BE%E7%BA%A2%E7%BC%9D%E7%9A%84%E6%B8%85%E6%B0%B4%E7%A0%96%E5%A2%99%E5%91%88%E7%8E%B0%E7%B4%AB%E8%A4%90%E8%89%B2%E7%AD%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="9.安全色" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E9.%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E8%89%B2%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="安全色是表达安全信息含义的颜色，能使人迅速发现或分辨安全标志和提醒注意，以防发生事故。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E8%89%B2%E6%98%AF%E8%A1%A8%E8%BE%BE%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E5%90%AB%E4%B9%89%E7%9A%84%E9%A2%9C%E8%89%B2%EF%BC%8C%E8%83%BD%E4%BD%BF%E4%BA%BA%E8%BF%85%E9%80%9F%E5%8F%91%E7%8E%B0%E6%88%96%E5%88%86%E8%BE%A8%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E6%A0%87%E5%BF%97%E5%92%8C%E6%8F%90%E9%86%92%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A5%E9%98%B2%E5%8F%91%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%8B%E6%95%85%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="适用于各类公共建筑及场所、工矿企业、交通运输等。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%80%82%E7%94%A8%E4%BA%8E%E5%90%84%E7%B1%BB%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%8F%8A%E5%9C%BA%E6%89%80%E3%80%81%E5%B7%A5%E7%9F%BF%E4%BC%81%E4%B8%9A%E3%80%81%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%90%E8%BE%93%E7%AD%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="但不适用于灯光、荧光颜色和航空、航海、内河航运及其他目的而使用的颜色。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BD%86%E4%B8%8D%E9%80%82%E7%94%A8%E4%BA%8E%E7%81%AF%E5%85%89%E3%80%81%E8%8D%A7%E5%85%89%E9%A2%9C%E8%89%B2%E5%92%8C%E8%88%AA%E7%A9%BA%E3%80%81%E8%88%AA%E6%B5%B7%E3%80%81%E5%86%85%E6%B2%B3%E8%88%AA%E8%BF%90%E5%8F%8A%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E7%9B%AE%E7%9A%84%E8%80%8C%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E7%9A%84%E9%A2%9C%E8%89%B2%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="安全色的含义及使用范围：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E8%89%B2%E7%9A%84%E5%90%AB%E4%B9%89%E5%8F%8A%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E8%8C%83%E5%9B%B4%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（1）红色" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E7%BA%A2%E8%89%B2%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="含义为：禁止、停止、防火和危险" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%90%AB%E4%B9%89%E4%B8%BA%EF%BC%9A%E7%A6%81%E6%AD%A2%E3%80%81%E5%81%9C%E6%AD%A2%E3%80%81%E9%98%B2%E7%81%AB%E5%92%8C%E5%8D%B1%E9%99%A9%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="使用范围：禁止标志、停止信号、消防设施" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E8%8C%83%E5%9B%B4%EF%BC%9A%E7%A6%81%E6%AD%A2%E6%A0%87%E5%BF%97%E3%80%81%E5%81%9C%E6%AD%A2%E4%BF%A1%E5%8F%B7%E3%80%81%E6%B6%88%E9%98%B2%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（2）蓝色" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E8%93%9D%E8%89%B2%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="含义为：指令、必须遵守的规定" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%90%AB%E4%B9%89%E4%B8%BA%EF%BC%9A%E6%8C%87%E4%BB%A4%E3%80%81%E5%BF%85%E9%A1%BB%E9%81%B5%E5%AE%88%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%84%E5%AE%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="使用范围：指令标志" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E8%8C%83%E5%9B%B4%EF%BC%9A%E6%8C%87%E4%BB%A4%E6%A0%87%E5%BF%97%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（3）黄色" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E9%BB%84%E8%89%B2%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="含义为：警告、注意" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%90%AB%E4%B9%89%E4%B8%BA%EF%BC%9A%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A%E3%80%81%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="使用范围：警告标志、行车道中线、起重设备的外伸、悬吊部分、警戒标志、安全帽" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E8%8C%83%E5%9B%B4%EF%BC%9A%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A%E6%A0%87%E5%BF%97%E3%80%81%E8%A1%8C%E8%BD%A6%E9%81%93%E4%B8%AD%E7%BA%BF%E3%80%81%E8%B5%B7%E9%87%8D%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%96%E4%BC%B8%E3%80%81%E6%82%AC%E5%90%8A%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E3%80%81%E8%AD%A6%E6%88%92%E6%A0%87%E5%BF%97%E3%80%81%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E5%B8%BD%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（4）绿色" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%884%EF%BC%89%E7%BB%BF%E8%89%B2%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="含义为：提示、安全状态、通行" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%90%AB%E4%B9%89%E4%B8%BA%EF%BC%9A%E6%8F%90%E7%A4%BA%E3%80%81%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E7%8A%B6%E6%80%81%E3%80%81%E9%80%9A%E8%A1%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="使用范围：提示标志、车间内安全通道、安全防护设备的位置" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E8%8C%83%E5%9B%B4%EF%BC%9A%E6%8F%90%E7%A4%BA%E6%A0%87%E5%BF%97%E3%80%81%E8%BD%A6%E9%97%B4%E5%86%85%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E9%80%9A%E9%81%93%E3%80%81%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E9%98%B2%E6%8A%A4%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%8D%E7%BD%AE%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="" _mubu_text="" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="第六节      生态可持续建筑" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%AC%AC%E5%85%AD%E8%8A%82%20%20%20%20%20%20%E7%94%9F%E6%80%81%E5%8F%AF%E6%8C%81%E7%BB%AD%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="考试大纲对本专题的考核要求是：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%80%83%E8%AF%95%E5%A4%A7%E7%BA%B2%E5%AF%B9%E6%9C%AC%E4%B8%93%E9%A2%98%E7%9A%84%E8%80%83%E6%A0%B8%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E6%98%AF%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="理解建筑与室内外环境、建筑与技术、建筑与人的行为方式的关系”的要求。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%90%86%E8%A7%A3%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E4%B8%8E%E5%AE%A4%E5%86%85%E5%A4%96%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E3%80%81%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E4%B8%8E%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E3%80%81%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E4%B8%8E%E4%BA%BA%E7%9A%84%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%BA%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%E7%9A%84%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%E2%80%9D%E7%9A%84%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="同时在主要参考书目里新增《生态可持续建筑》和《环境心理学》两本教材。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%90%8C%E6%97%B6%E5%9C%A8%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E5%8F%82%E8%80%83%E4%B9%A6%E7%9B%AE%E9%87%8C%E6%96%B0%E5%A2%9E%E3%80%8A%E7%94%9F%E6%80%81%E5%8F%AF%E6%8C%81%E7%BB%AD%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E3%80%8B%E5%92%8C%E3%80%8A%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%BF%83%E7%90%86%E5%AD%A6%E3%80%8B%E4%B8%A4%E6%9C%AC%E6%95%99%E6%9D%90%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="与节能、太阳能和生态可持续建筑有关的内容详见本节，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%8E%E8%8A%82%E8%83%BD%E3%80%81%E5%A4%AA%E9%98%B3%E8%83%BD%E5%92%8C%E7%94%9F%E6%80%81%E5%8F%AF%E6%8C%81%E7%BB%AD%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E6%9C%89%E5%85%B3%E7%9A%84%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%E8%AF%A6%E8%A7%81%E6%9C%AC%E8%8A%82%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="人的行为心理和环境之间关系的内容详见第七节。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BA%BA%E7%9A%84%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%BA%E5%BF%83%E7%90%86%E5%92%8C%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E4%B9%8B%E9%97%B4%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%E7%9A%84%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%E8%AF%A6%E8%A7%81%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%83%E8%8A%82%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="安全色规定为红、蓝、黄、绿四种颜色。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E8%89%B2%E8%A7%84%E5%AE%9A%E4%B8%BA%E7%BA%A2%E3%80%81%E8%93%9D%E3%80%81%E9%BB%84%E3%80%81%E7%BB%BF%E5%9B%9B%E7%A7%8D%E9%A2%9C%E8%89%B2%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="太阳能是一种典型的可持续能源，具有清洁、安全、长期性的特征。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%A4%AA%E9%98%B3%E8%83%BD%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%80%E7%A7%8D%E5%85%B8%E5%9E%8B%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%AF%E6%8C%81%E7%BB%AD%E8%83%BD%E6%BA%90%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%B7%E6%9C%89%E6%B8%85%E6%B4%81%E3%80%81%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E3%80%81%E9%95%BF%E6%9C%9F%E6%80%A7%E7%9A%84%E7%89%B9%E5%BE%81%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="太阳能建筑是指经过良好的设计，达到优化利用太阳能效果的建筑。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%A4%AA%E9%98%B3%E8%83%BD%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E6%98%AF%E6%8C%87%E7%BB%8F%E8%BF%87%E8%89%AF%E5%A5%BD%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%EF%BC%8C%E8%BE%BE%E5%88%B0%E4%BC%98%E5%8C%96%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8%E5%A4%AA%E9%98%B3%E8%83%BD%E6%95%88%E6%9E%9C%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（一）节能建筑和太阳能建筑" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%80%EF%BC%89%E8%8A%82%E8%83%BD%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%92%8C%E5%A4%AA%E9%98%B3%E8%83%BD%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="20世纪70年代，全球范围的“能源危机”导致了节能建筑的出现。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E20%E4%B8%96%E7%BA%AA70%E5%B9%B4%E4%BB%A3%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E8%8C%83%E5%9B%B4%E7%9A%84%E2%80%9C%E8%83%BD%E6%BA%90%E5%8D%B1%E6%9C%BA%E2%80%9D%E5%AF%BC%E8%87%B4%E4%BA%86%E8%8A%82%E8%83%BD%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%9A%84%E5%87%BA%E7%8E%B0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="节能的含义：狭义的理解是节约传统能源；广义的理解是“开发利用可持续能源”和“有效用能”。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%8A%82%E8%83%BD%E7%9A%84%E5%90%AB%E4%B9%89%EF%BC%9A%E7%8B%AD%E4%B9%89%E7%9A%84%E7%90%86%E8%A7%A3%E6%98%AF%E8%8A%82%E7%BA%A6%E4%BC%A0%E7%BB%9F%E8%83%BD%E6%BA%90%EF%BC%9B%E5%B9%BF%E4%B9%89%E7%9A%84%E7%90%86%E8%A7%A3%E6%98%AF%E2%80%9C%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8%E5%8F%AF%E6%8C%81%E7%BB%AD%E8%83%BD%E6%BA%90%E2%80%9D%E5%92%8C%E2%80%9C%E6%9C%89%E6%95%88%E7%94%A8%E8%83%BD%E2%80%9D%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="节能建筑在技术处理上有两种处理方式，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%8A%82%E8%83%BD%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%9C%A8%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86%E4%B8%8A%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%A4%E7%A7%8D%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="一类是加强围护结构的绝热性能，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%80%E7%B1%BB%E6%98%AF%E5%8A%A0%E5%BC%BA%E5%9B%B4%E6%8A%A4%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%9D%E7%83%AD%E6%80%A7%E8%83%BD%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="另一类是利用太阳能。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%8F%A6%E4%B8%80%E7%B1%BB%E6%98%AF%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8%E5%A4%AA%E9%98%B3%E8%83%BD%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      </outline>
    </outline>
    <outline text="以供暖为主的太阳能建筑可分为主动系统和被动系统两大类。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BB%A5%E4%BE%9B%E6%9A%96%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%BB%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%AA%E9%98%B3%E8%83%BD%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%8F%AF%E5%88%86%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%BB%E5%8A%A8%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E5%92%8C%E8%A2%AB%E5%8A%A8%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E4%B8%A4%E5%A4%A7%E7%B1%BB%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="1.主动系统" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1.%E4%B8%BB%E5%8A%A8%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="主动式供暖系统主要由集热器、管道、储热物质以及散热器等组成。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%BB%E5%8A%A8%E5%BC%8F%E4%BE%9B%E6%9A%96%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E7%94%B1%E9%9B%86%E7%83%AD%E5%99%A8%E3%80%81%E7%AE%A1%E9%81%93%E3%80%81%E5%82%A8%E7%83%AD%E7%89%A9%E8%B4%A8%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%8A%E6%95%A3%E7%83%AD%E5%99%A8%E7%AD%89%E7%BB%84%E6%88%90%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="系统的循环动力由水泵或风机提供。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%9A%84%E5%BE%AA%E7%8E%AF%E5%8A%A8%E5%8A%9B%E7%94%B1%E6%B0%B4%E6%B3%B5%E6%88%96%E9%A3%8E%E6%9C%BA%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="这种系统初次投资较大，单纯采暖时较少采用，可用于提供热水或兼作采暖系统。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%BF%99%E7%A7%8D%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E5%88%9D%E6%AC%A1%E6%8A%95%E8%B5%84%E8%BE%83%E5%A4%A7%EF%BC%8C%E5%8D%95%E7%BA%AF%E9%87%87%E6%9A%96%E6%97%B6%E8%BE%83%E5%B0%91%E9%87%87%E7%94%A8%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%AF%E7%94%A8%E4%BA%8E%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E7%83%AD%E6%B0%B4%E6%88%96%E5%85%BC%E4%BD%9C%E9%87%87%E6%9A%96%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（1）间接得热系统有：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E9%97%B4%E6%8E%A5%E5%BE%97%E7%83%AD%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E6%9C%89%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="特朗伯（Trombe）集热墙、水墙、载水墙（充水墙）和毗连日光间或温室四种类型。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E4%BC%AF%EF%BC%88Trombe%EF%BC%89%E9%9B%86%E7%83%AD%E5%A2%99%E3%80%81%E6%B0%B4%E5%A2%99%E3%80%81%E8%BD%BD%E6%B0%B4%E5%A2%99%EF%BC%88%E5%85%85%E6%B0%B4%E5%A2%99%EF%BC%89%E5%92%8C%E6%AF%97%E8%BF%9E%E6%97%A5%E5%85%89%E9%97%B4%E6%88%96%E6%B8%A9%E5%AE%A4%E5%9B%9B%E7%A7%8D%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="1）特朗伯墙的主要构造为：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1%EF%BC%89%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E4%BC%AF%E5%A2%99%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E6%9E%84%E9%80%A0%E4%B8%BA%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="在建筑物向阳面设400mm厚的混凝土集热墙，墙的向阳面涂以深色涂层，以加强吸热。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9C%A8%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%89%A9%E5%90%91%E9%98%B3%E9%9D%A2%E8%AE%BE400mm%E5%8E%9A%E7%9A%84%E6%B7%B7%E5%87%9D%E5%9C%9F%E9%9B%86%E7%83%AD%E5%A2%99%EF%BC%8C%E5%A2%99%E7%9A%84%E5%90%91%E9%98%B3%E9%9D%A2%E6%B6%82%E4%BB%A5%E6%B7%B1%E8%89%B2%E6%B6%82%E5%B1%82%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A5%E5%8A%A0%E5%BC%BA%E5%90%B8%E7%83%AD%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="墙的上、下设可关闭的通风口，从而构成主要的集热、储热和散热器。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%A2%99%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%8A%E3%80%81%E4%B8%8B%E8%AE%BE%E5%8F%AF%E5%85%B3%E9%97%AD%E7%9A%84%E9%80%9A%E9%A3%8E%E5%8F%A3%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%8E%E8%80%8C%E6%9E%84%E6%88%90%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E7%9A%84%E9%9B%86%E7%83%AD%E3%80%81%E5%82%A8%E7%83%AD%E5%92%8C%E6%95%A3%E7%83%AD%E5%99%A8%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="为保证集热效果，并保护墙面不受室外环境污染与侵蚀，在集热墙外80mm处装玻璃或透明材料，以构成空气间层。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%BA%E4%BF%9D%E8%AF%81%E9%9B%86%E7%83%AD%E6%95%88%E6%9E%9C%EF%BC%8C%E5%B9%B6%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4%E5%A2%99%E9%9D%A2%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%97%E5%AE%A4%E5%A4%96%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E6%B1%A1%E6%9F%93%E4%B8%8E%E4%BE%B5%E8%9A%80%EF%BC%8C%E5%9C%A8%E9%9B%86%E7%83%AD%E5%A2%99%E5%A4%9680mm%E5%A4%84%E8%A3%85%E7%8E%BB%E7%92%83%E6%88%96%E9%80%8F%E6%98%8E%E6%9D%90%E6%96%99%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A5%E6%9E%84%E6%88%90%E7%A9%BA%E6%B0%94%E9%97%B4%E5%B1%82%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="2）水墙是利用水的比热较混凝土大得多的特点，以其取代混凝土作储热体的一种做法。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2%EF%BC%89%E6%B0%B4%E5%A2%99%E6%98%AF%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8%E6%B0%B4%E7%9A%84%E6%AF%94%E7%83%AD%E8%BE%83%E6%B7%B7%E5%87%9D%E5%9C%9F%E5%A4%A7%E5%BE%97%E5%A4%9A%E7%9A%84%E7%89%B9%E7%82%B9%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A5%E5%85%B6%E5%8F%96%E4%BB%A3%E6%B7%B7%E5%87%9D%E5%9C%9F%E4%BD%9C%E5%82%A8%E7%83%AD%E4%BD%93%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%80%E7%A7%8D%E5%81%9A%E6%B3%95%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="由于水具有对流传热的性能，会把所吸收的太阳辐射热较快地传到墙体内表面，造成室温的较大波动，故储热性能不如混凝土稳定。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%94%B1%E4%BA%8E%E6%B0%B4%E5%85%B7%E6%9C%89%E5%AF%B9%E6%B5%81%E4%BC%A0%E7%83%AD%E7%9A%84%E6%80%A7%E8%83%BD%EF%BC%8C%E4%BC%9A%E6%8A%8A%E6%89%80%E5%90%B8%E6%94%B6%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%AA%E9%98%B3%E8%BE%90%E5%B0%84%E7%83%AD%E8%BE%83%E5%BF%AB%E5%9C%B0%E4%BC%A0%E5%88%B0%E5%A2%99%E4%BD%93%E5%86%85%E8%A1%A8%E9%9D%A2%EF%BC%8C%E9%80%A0%E6%88%90%E5%AE%A4%E6%B8%A9%E7%9A%84%E8%BE%83%E5%A4%A7%E6%B3%A2%E5%8A%A8%EF%BC%8C%E6%95%85%E5%82%A8%E7%83%AD%E6%80%A7%E8%83%BD%E4%B8%8D%E5%A6%82%E6%B7%B7%E5%87%9D%E5%9C%9F%E7%A8%B3%E5%AE%9A%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="2.被动系统" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2.%E8%A2%AB%E5%8A%A8%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="其特点是，将建筑物的全部或一部分既作为集热器，又作为贮热器和散热器，无需管道和风机、水泵。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%85%B6%E7%89%B9%E7%82%B9%E6%98%AF%EF%BC%8C%E5%B0%86%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%89%A9%E7%9A%84%E5%85%A8%E9%83%A8%E6%88%96%E4%B8%80%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E6%97%A2%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%BA%E9%9B%86%E7%83%AD%E5%99%A8%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%88%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%BA%E8%B4%AE%E7%83%AD%E5%99%A8%E5%92%8C%E6%95%A3%E7%83%AD%E5%99%A8%EF%BC%8C%E6%97%A0%E9%9C%80%E7%AE%A1%E9%81%93%E5%92%8C%E9%A3%8E%E6%9C%BA%E3%80%81%E6%B0%B4%E6%B3%B5%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="被动式系统又分为间接得热系统和直接得热系统两类。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%A2%AB%E5%8A%A8%E5%BC%8F%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E5%8F%88%E5%88%86%E4%B8%BA%E9%97%B4%E6%8E%A5%E5%BE%97%E7%83%AD%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E5%92%8C%E7%9B%B4%E6%8E%A5%E5%BE%97%E7%83%AD%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E4%B8%A4%E7%B1%BB%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（2）毗连日光间既可以提高主要空间的使用效果，又可大幅度减少房屋的热损失；此外，日光间还可以构成良好的生态环境。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E6%AF%97%E8%BF%9E%E6%97%A5%E5%85%89%E9%97%B4%E6%97%A2%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E6%8F%90%E9%AB%98%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E6%95%88%E6%9E%9C%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%88%E5%8F%AF%E5%A4%A7%E5%B9%85%E5%BA%A6%E5%87%8F%E5%B0%91%E6%88%BF%E5%B1%8B%E7%9A%84%E7%83%AD%E6%8D%9F%E5%A4%B1%EF%BC%9B%E6%AD%A4%E5%A4%96%EF%BC%8C%E6%97%A5%E5%85%89%E9%97%B4%E8%BF%98%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E6%9E%84%E6%88%90%E8%89%AF%E5%A5%BD%E7%9A%84%E7%94%9F%E6%80%81%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="夏季，日光间可以开窗通风并采用遮阳措施，避免室内过热；因而具有较好的推广前景。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%A4%8F%E5%AD%A3%EF%BC%8C%E6%97%A5%E5%85%89%E9%97%B4%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E5%BC%80%E7%AA%97%E9%80%9A%E9%A3%8E%E5%B9%B6%E9%87%87%E7%94%A8%E9%81%AE%E9%98%B3%E6%8E%AA%E6%96%BD%EF%BC%8C%E9%81%BF%E5%85%8D%E5%AE%A4%E5%86%85%E8%BF%87%E7%83%AD%EF%BC%9B%E5%9B%A0%E8%80%8C%E5%85%B7%E6%9C%89%E8%BE%83%E5%A5%BD%E7%9A%84%E6%8E%A8%E5%B9%BF%E5%89%8D%E6%99%AF%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（3）直接得热系统一般利用向阳面的玻璃窗直接得到太阳辐射热，是一种最简单的太阳能建筑形式。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E7%9B%B4%E6%8E%A5%E5%BE%97%E7%83%AD%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E4%B8%80%E8%88%AC%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8%E5%90%91%E9%98%B3%E9%9D%A2%E7%9A%84%E7%8E%BB%E7%92%83%E7%AA%97%E7%9B%B4%E6%8E%A5%E5%BE%97%E5%88%B0%E5%A4%AA%E9%98%B3%E8%BE%90%E5%B0%84%E7%83%AD%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%80%E7%A7%8D%E6%9C%80%E7%AE%80%E5%8D%95%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%AA%E9%98%B3%E8%83%BD%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="为了减少热损失，夜间应覆盖绝热窗帘。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%BA%E4%BA%86%E5%87%8F%E5%B0%91%E7%83%AD%E6%8D%9F%E5%A4%B1%EF%BC%8C%E5%A4%9C%E9%97%B4%E5%BA%94%E8%A6%86%E7%9B%96%E7%BB%9D%E7%83%AD%E7%AA%97%E5%B8%98%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="夏季白天可将采光部位以外的透明部分用绝热材料覆盖，以减少进热；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%A4%8F%E5%AD%A3%E7%99%BD%E5%A4%A9%E5%8F%AF%E5%B0%86%E9%87%87%E5%85%89%E9%83%A8%E4%BD%8D%E4%BB%A5%E5%A4%96%E7%9A%84%E9%80%8F%E6%98%8E%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E7%94%A8%E7%BB%9D%E7%83%AD%E6%9D%90%E6%96%99%E8%A6%86%E7%9B%96%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A5%E5%87%8F%E5%B0%91%E8%BF%9B%E7%83%AD%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="夜间则将绝热层全部移除，以利于向外散热。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%A4%9C%E9%97%B4%E5%88%99%E5%B0%86%E7%BB%9D%E7%83%AD%E5%B1%82%E5%85%A8%E9%83%A8%E7%A7%BB%E9%99%A4%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A5%E5%88%A9%E4%BA%8E%E5%90%91%E5%A4%96%E6%95%A3%E7%83%AD%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="对于居住建筑，窗面积与地面面积比（窗地比）应为1/5~1/3。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%AF%B9%E4%BA%8E%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%EF%BC%8C%E7%AA%97%E9%9D%A2%E7%A7%AF%E4%B8%8E%E5%9C%B0%E9%9D%A2%E9%9D%A2%E7%A7%AF%E6%AF%94%EF%BC%88%E7%AA%97%E5%9C%B0%E6%AF%94%EF%BC%89%E5%BA%94%E4%B8%BA1/5~1/3%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="墙、地板以及其他储热构件的表面面积至少应5倍于向阳面玻璃的面积。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%A2%99%E3%80%81%E5%9C%B0%E6%9D%BF%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%8A%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E5%82%A8%E7%83%AD%E6%9E%84%E4%BB%B6%E7%9A%84%E8%A1%A8%E9%9D%A2%E9%9D%A2%E7%A7%AF%E8%87%B3%E5%B0%91%E5%BA%945%E5%80%8D%E4%BA%8E%E5%90%91%E9%98%B3%E9%9D%A2%E7%8E%BB%E7%92%83%E7%9A%84%E9%9D%A2%E7%A7%AF%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="3）载水墙（充水墙）采用向混凝土墙的空腔内充水的办法，兼有水的储热容量大和固体材料无对流传热两方面的集热优势。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E3%EF%BC%89%E8%BD%BD%E6%B0%B4%E5%A2%99%EF%BC%88%E5%85%85%E6%B0%B4%E5%A2%99%EF%BC%89%E9%87%87%E7%94%A8%E5%90%91%E6%B7%B7%E5%87%9D%E5%9C%9F%E5%A2%99%E7%9A%84%E7%A9%BA%E8%85%94%E5%86%85%E5%85%85%E6%B0%B4%E7%9A%84%E5%8A%9E%E6%B3%95%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%BC%E6%9C%89%E6%B0%B4%E7%9A%84%E5%82%A8%E7%83%AD%E5%AE%B9%E9%87%8F%E5%A4%A7%E5%92%8C%E5%9B%BA%E4%BD%93%E6%9D%90%E6%96%99%E6%97%A0%E5%AF%B9%E6%B5%81%E4%BC%A0%E7%83%AD%E4%B8%A4%E6%96%B9%E9%9D%A2%E7%9A%84%E9%9B%86%E7%83%AD%E4%BC%98%E5%8A%BF%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（二）节能、节地与环境保护的关系" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%BA%8C%EF%BC%89%E8%8A%82%E8%83%BD%E3%80%81%E8%8A%82%E5%9C%B0%E4%B8%8E%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4%E7%9A%84%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="目前人类还在大量使用有污染的能源。因此节约能耗必然减少污染而有利于环保。绿化是保护环境生态的重要措施。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%9B%AE%E5%89%8D%E4%BA%BA%E7%B1%BB%E8%BF%98%E5%9C%A8%E5%A4%A7%E9%87%8F%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E6%9C%89%E6%B1%A1%E6%9F%93%E7%9A%84%E8%83%BD%E6%BA%90%E3%80%82%E5%9B%A0%E6%AD%A4%E8%8A%82%E7%BA%A6%E8%83%BD%E8%80%97%E5%BF%85%E7%84%B6%E5%87%8F%E5%B0%91%E6%B1%A1%E6%9F%93%E8%80%8C%E6%9C%89%E5%88%A9%E4%BA%8E%E7%8E%AF%E4%BF%9D%E3%80%82%E7%BB%BF%E5%8C%96%E6%98%AF%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E7%94%9F%E6%80%81%E7%9A%84%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81%E6%8E%AA%E6%96%BD%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="节约建设用地可以提供更多的绿化用地；发展立体绿化而不直接占用土地进行绿化可以进一步节约用地；这就是节地与环保的关系。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%8A%82%E7%BA%A6%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E6%9B%B4%E5%A4%9A%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%BF%E5%8C%96%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%9B%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E7%AB%8B%E4%BD%93%E7%BB%BF%E5%8C%96%E8%80%8C%E4%B8%8D%E7%9B%B4%E6%8E%A5%E5%8D%A0%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%9F%E5%9C%B0%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E7%BB%BF%E5%8C%96%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E8%BF%9B%E4%B8%80%E6%AD%A5%E8%8A%82%E7%BA%A6%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%9B%E8%BF%99%E5%B0%B1%E6%98%AF%E8%8A%82%E5%9C%B0%E4%B8%8E%E7%8E%AF%E4%BF%9D%E7%9A%84%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="致力于改善人类生存环境的建筑工作者，应当十分关注建筑节能和节地问题。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%87%B4%E5%8A%9B%E4%BA%8E%E6%94%B9%E5%96%84%E4%BA%BA%E7%B1%BB%E7%94%9F%E5%AD%98%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E8%80%85%EF%BC%8C%E5%BA%94%E5%BD%93%E5%8D%81%E5%88%86%E5%85%B3%E6%B3%A8%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%8A%82%E8%83%BD%E5%92%8C%E8%8A%82%E5%9C%B0%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="1.建筑围护结构的节能" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1.%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%9B%B4%E6%8A%A4%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E7%9A%84%E8%8A%82%E8%83%BD%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="通过对围护结构散热公式的分析可知，一个有着足够总热阻的房屋，只需一盏40W灯泡所产生的余热就可以在冬季保持室内适宜的温度。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87%E5%AF%B9%E5%9B%B4%E6%8A%A4%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E6%95%A3%E7%83%AD%E5%85%AC%E5%BC%8F%E7%9A%84%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E5%8F%AF%E7%9F%A5%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E6%9C%89%E7%9D%80%E8%B6%B3%E5%A4%9F%E6%80%BB%E7%83%AD%E9%98%BB%E7%9A%84%E6%88%BF%E5%B1%8B%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%AA%E9%9C%80%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%8F40W%E7%81%AF%E6%B3%A1%E6%89%80%E4%BA%A7%E7%94%9F%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%99%E7%83%AD%E5%B0%B1%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E5%9C%A8%E5%86%AC%E5%AD%A3%E4%BF%9D%E6%8C%81%E5%AE%A4%E5%86%85%E9%80%82%E5%AE%9C%E7%9A%84%E6%B8%A9%E5%BA%A6%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="由此说明，提高围护结构的总热阻具有很大的节能潜力，这是建筑节能首先应解决的问题。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%94%B1%E6%AD%A4%E8%AF%B4%E6%98%8E%EF%BC%8C%E6%8F%90%E9%AB%98%E5%9B%B4%E6%8A%A4%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E7%9A%84%E6%80%BB%E7%83%AD%E9%98%BB%E5%85%B7%E6%9C%89%E5%BE%88%E5%A4%A7%E7%9A%84%E8%8A%82%E8%83%BD%E6%BD%9C%E5%8A%9B%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%99%E6%98%AF%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%8A%82%E8%83%BD%E9%A6%96%E5%85%88%E5%BA%94%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E7%9A%84%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="2.建筑平面形式的节能" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2.%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B9%B3%E9%9D%A2%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E7%9A%84%E8%8A%82%E8%83%BD%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（2）太阳能建筑的体形系数" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E5%A4%AA%E9%98%B3%E8%83%BD%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%93%E5%BD%A2%E7%B3%BB%E6%95%B0%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="太阳能建筑的体形系数应该考虑方向性，即应当分析不同方向的外围面积与建筑体积的比值与建筑节能的关系。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%A4%AA%E9%98%B3%E8%83%BD%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%93%E5%BD%A2%E7%B3%BB%E6%95%B0%E5%BA%94%E8%AF%A5%E8%80%83%E8%99%91%E6%96%B9%E5%90%91%E6%80%A7%EF%BC%8C%E5%8D%B3%E5%BA%94%E5%BD%93%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E6%96%B9%E5%90%91%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%96%E5%9B%B4%E9%9D%A2%E7%A7%AF%E4%B8%8E%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E4%BD%93%E7%A7%AF%E7%9A%84%E6%AF%94%E5%80%BC%E4%B8%8E%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%8A%82%E8%83%BD%E7%9A%84%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="例如，一座供白天使用的东西向建筑，东向体形系数大一些好，因为可以早得太阳热、多得太阳热，便于上午直接使用，并可贮热下午用。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BE%8B%E5%A6%82%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%80%E5%BA%A7%E4%BE%9B%E7%99%BD%E5%A4%A9%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%9C%E8%A5%BF%E5%90%91%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%9C%E5%90%91%E4%BD%93%E5%BD%A2%E7%B3%BB%E6%95%B0%E5%A4%A7%E4%B8%80%E4%BA%9B%E5%A5%BD%EF%BC%8C%E5%9B%A0%E4%B8%BA%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E6%97%A9%E5%BE%97%E5%A4%AA%E9%98%B3%E7%83%AD%E3%80%81%E5%A4%9A%E5%BE%97%E5%A4%AA%E9%98%B3%E7%83%AD%EF%BC%8C%E4%BE%BF%E4%BA%8E%E4%B8%8A%E5%8D%88%E7%9B%B4%E6%8E%A5%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%EF%BC%8C%E5%B9%B6%E5%8F%AF%E8%B4%AE%E7%83%AD%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%88%E7%94%A8%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="同理，如果是晚上使用为主的居住建筑，西向体形系数大些会更有利。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%90%8C%E7%90%86%EF%BC%8C%E5%A6%82%E6%9E%9C%E6%98%AF%E6%99%9A%E4%B8%8A%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%BB%E7%9A%84%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%EF%BC%8C%E8%A5%BF%E5%90%91%E4%BD%93%E5%BD%A2%E7%B3%BB%E6%95%B0%E5%A4%A7%E4%BA%9B%E4%BC%9A%E6%9B%B4%E6%9C%89%E5%88%A9%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（3）建筑容积系数" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%AE%B9%E7%A7%AF%E7%B3%BB%E6%95%B0%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="对于太阳能建筑而言，还应当考虑建筑容积系数，即考虑建筑物的散热外表面积与建筑的内部容积的比值。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%AF%B9%E4%BA%8E%E5%A4%AA%E9%98%B3%E8%83%BD%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%80%8C%E8%A8%80%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%98%E5%BA%94%E5%BD%93%E8%80%83%E8%99%91%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%AE%B9%E7%A7%AF%E7%B3%BB%E6%95%B0%EF%BC%8C%E5%8D%B3%E8%80%83%E8%99%91%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%89%A9%E7%9A%84%E6%95%A3%E7%83%AD%E5%A4%96%E8%A1%A8%E9%9D%A2%E7%A7%AF%E4%B8%8E%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%9A%84%E5%86%85%E9%83%A8%E5%AE%B9%E7%A7%AF%E7%9A%84%E6%AF%94%E5%80%BC%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="建筑容积等于建筑体积减去围护结构体积。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%AE%B9%E7%A7%AF%E7%AD%89%E4%BA%8E%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E4%BD%93%E7%A7%AF%E5%87%8F%E5%8E%BB%E5%9B%B4%E6%8A%A4%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E4%BD%93%E7%A7%AF%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="在体形系数相等的情况下，容积系数大的使用空间小、围护结构体积大，也就是使用面积小，结构面积大，构造方案欠佳。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9C%A8%E4%BD%93%E5%BD%A2%E7%B3%BB%E6%95%B0%E7%9B%B8%E7%AD%89%E7%9A%84%E6%83%85%E5%86%B5%E4%B8%8B%EF%BC%8C%E5%AE%B9%E7%A7%AF%E7%B3%BB%E6%95%B0%E5%A4%A7%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E5%B0%8F%E3%80%81%E5%9B%B4%E6%8A%A4%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E4%BD%93%E7%A7%AF%E5%A4%A7%EF%BC%8C%E4%B9%9F%E5%B0%B1%E6%98%AF%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E9%9D%A2%E7%A7%AF%E5%B0%8F%EF%BC%8C%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E9%9D%A2%E7%A7%AF%E5%A4%A7%EF%BC%8C%E6%9E%84%E9%80%A0%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%E6%AC%A0%E4%BD%B3%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（1）建筑体形系数" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E4%BD%93%E5%BD%A2%E7%B3%BB%E6%95%B0%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="建筑热工学将建筑物的散热面积与建筑体积之比值称为该建筑的“体形系数”。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%83%AD%E5%B7%A5%E5%AD%A6%E5%B0%86%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%89%A9%E7%9A%84%E6%95%A3%E7%83%AD%E9%9D%A2%E7%A7%AF%E4%B8%8E%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E4%BD%93%E7%A7%AF%E4%B9%8B%E6%AF%94%E5%80%BC%E7%A7%B0%E4%B8%BA%E8%AF%A5%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%9A%84%E2%80%9C%E4%BD%93%E5%BD%A2%E7%B3%BB%E6%95%B0%E2%80%9D%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="体形系数越小越有利于节能。从建筑平面形式看，圆形最有利于节能；正方形也是良好的节能型平面；长宽比大的是耗能型平面。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BD%93%E5%BD%A2%E7%B3%BB%E6%95%B0%E8%B6%8A%E5%B0%8F%E8%B6%8A%E6%9C%89%E5%88%A9%E4%BA%8E%E8%8A%82%E8%83%BD%E3%80%82%E4%BB%8E%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B9%B3%E9%9D%A2%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E7%9C%8B%EF%BC%8C%E5%9C%86%E5%BD%A2%E6%9C%80%E6%9C%89%E5%88%A9%E4%BA%8E%E8%8A%82%E8%83%BD%EF%BC%9B%E6%AD%A3%E6%96%B9%E5%BD%A2%E4%B9%9F%E6%98%AF%E8%89%AF%E5%A5%BD%E7%9A%84%E8%8A%82%E8%83%BD%E5%9E%8B%E5%B9%B3%E9%9D%A2%EF%BC%9B%E9%95%BF%E5%AE%BD%E6%AF%94%E5%A4%A7%E7%9A%84%E6%98%AF%E8%80%97%E8%83%BD%E5%9E%8B%E5%B9%B3%E9%9D%A2%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="这一点，无论从冬季失热还是从夏季得热的角度，分析的结果都是一样的。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%BF%99%E4%B8%80%E7%82%B9%EF%BC%8C%E6%97%A0%E8%AE%BA%E4%BB%8E%E5%86%AC%E5%AD%A3%E5%A4%B1%E7%83%AD%E8%BF%98%E6%98%AF%E4%BB%8E%E5%A4%8F%E5%AD%A3%E5%BE%97%E7%83%AD%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%92%E5%BA%A6%EF%BC%8C%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%9C%E9%83%BD%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%80%E6%A0%B7%E7%9A%84%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="耗能型平面的建筑，从总图上看相对的周边长度大，占地较多；围护结构消耗的材料、人工等费用相对也高。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%80%97%E8%83%BD%E5%9E%8B%E5%B9%B3%E9%9D%A2%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%8E%E6%80%BB%E5%9B%BE%E4%B8%8A%E7%9C%8B%E7%9B%B8%E5%AF%B9%E7%9A%84%E5%91%A8%E8%BE%B9%E9%95%BF%E5%BA%A6%E5%A4%A7%EF%BC%8C%E5%8D%A0%E5%9C%B0%E8%BE%83%E5%A4%9A%EF%BC%9B%E5%9B%B4%E6%8A%A4%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E6%B6%88%E8%80%97%E7%9A%84%E6%9D%90%E6%96%99%E3%80%81%E4%BA%BA%E5%B7%A5%E7%AD%89%E8%B4%B9%E7%94%A8%E7%9B%B8%E5%AF%B9%E4%B9%9F%E9%AB%98%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="3.建筑群体布局的节能" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E3.%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%BE%A4%E4%BD%93%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E7%9A%84%E8%8A%82%E8%83%BD%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（1）通过简单分析可知，在面积与体积相同的情况下，分散布置的建筑外墙面积是集中布置的建筑外墙面积的3倍，因而两种布置的建筑能耗比也是3：1。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87%E7%AE%80%E5%8D%95%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E5%8F%AF%E7%9F%A5%EF%BC%8C%E5%9C%A8%E9%9D%A2%E7%A7%AF%E4%B8%8E%E4%BD%93%E7%A7%AF%E7%9B%B8%E5%90%8C%E7%9A%84%E6%83%85%E5%86%B5%E4%B8%8B%EF%BC%8C%E5%88%86%E6%95%A3%E5%B8%83%E7%BD%AE%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%A4%96%E5%A2%99%E9%9D%A2%E7%A7%AF%E6%98%AF%E9%9B%86%E4%B8%AD%E5%B8%83%E7%BD%AE%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%A4%96%E5%A2%99%E9%9D%A2%E7%A7%AF%E7%9A%843%E5%80%8D%EF%BC%8C%E5%9B%A0%E8%80%8C%E4%B8%A4%E7%A7%8D%E5%B8%83%E7%BD%AE%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%83%BD%E8%80%97%E6%AF%94%E4%B9%9F%E6%98%AF3%EF%BC%9A1%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（2）分散布置的建筑，人流、物流路线较长，交通运输的能耗较大。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E5%88%86%E6%95%A3%E5%B8%83%E7%BD%AE%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%EF%BC%8C%E4%BA%BA%E6%B5%81%E3%80%81%E7%89%A9%E6%B5%81%E8%B7%AF%E7%BA%BF%E8%BE%83%E9%95%BF%EF%BC%8C%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%90%E8%BE%93%E7%9A%84%E8%83%BD%E8%80%97%E8%BE%83%E5%A4%A7%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（3）集中布置的建筑在用地、耗材和造价等方面均低手分散布置的建筑。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E9%9B%86%E4%B8%AD%E5%B8%83%E7%BD%AE%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%9C%A8%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%81%E8%80%97%E6%9D%90%E5%92%8C%E9%80%A0%E4%BB%B7%E7%AD%89%E6%96%B9%E9%9D%A2%E5%9D%87%E4%BD%8E%E6%89%8B%E5%88%86%E6%95%A3%E5%B8%83%E7%BD%AE%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（4）两种布置方案在噪声控制和自然通风组织上的差别并不明显，集中布置的方案完全可以处理好，从而获得很好的效益。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%884%EF%BC%89%E4%B8%A4%E7%A7%8D%E5%B8%83%E7%BD%AE%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%E5%9C%A8%E5%99%AA%E5%A3%B0%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E5%92%8C%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6%E9%80%9A%E9%A3%8E%E7%BB%84%E7%BB%87%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%B7%AE%E5%88%AB%E5%B9%B6%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%8E%E6%98%BE%EF%BC%8C%E9%9B%86%E4%B8%AD%E5%B8%83%E7%BD%AE%E7%9A%84%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%E5%AE%8C%E5%85%A8%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86%E5%A5%BD%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%8E%E8%80%8C%E8%8E%B7%E5%BE%97%E5%BE%88%E5%A5%BD%E7%9A%84%E6%95%88%E7%9B%8A%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（5）集中布置建筑占地少，可以争取较大的绿地面积：污染性能源消耗少，对环境的污染也少；所以集中布置有利环保。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%885%EF%BC%89%E9%9B%86%E4%B8%AD%E5%B8%83%E7%BD%AE%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%8D%A0%E5%9C%B0%E5%B0%91%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E4%BA%89%E5%8F%96%E8%BE%83%E5%A4%A7%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%BF%E5%9C%B0%E9%9D%A2%E7%A7%AF%EF%BC%9A%E6%B1%A1%E6%9F%93%E6%80%A7%E8%83%BD%E6%BA%90%E6%B6%88%E8%80%97%E5%B0%91%EF%BC%8C%E5%AF%B9%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E7%9A%84%E6%B1%A1%E6%9F%93%E4%B9%9F%E5%B0%91%EF%BC%9B%E6%89%80%E4%BB%A5%E9%9B%86%E4%B8%AD%E5%B8%83%E7%BD%AE%E6%9C%89%E5%88%A9%E7%8E%AF%E4%BF%9D%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（三）生态可持续建筑" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%89%EF%BC%89%E7%94%9F%E6%80%81%E5%8F%AF%E6%8C%81%E7%BB%AD%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="20世纪80年代后期，由于人口能源、土地、环境等危机日益突显，危及全球的生态平衡和可持续发展，迫使人们系求新的对策。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E20%E4%B8%96%E7%BA%AA80%E5%B9%B4%E4%BB%A3%E5%90%8E%E6%9C%9F%EF%BC%8C%E7%94%B1%E4%BA%8E%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E8%83%BD%E6%BA%90%E3%80%81%E5%9C%9F%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%81%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E7%AD%89%E5%8D%B1%E6%9C%BA%E6%97%A5%E7%9B%8A%E7%AA%81%E6%98%BE%EF%BC%8C%E5%8D%B1%E5%8F%8A%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E7%9A%84%E7%94%9F%E6%80%81%E5%B9%B3%E8%A1%A1%E5%92%8C%E5%8F%AF%E6%8C%81%E7%BB%AD%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%AB%E4%BD%BF%E4%BA%BA%E4%BB%AC%E7%B3%BB%E6%B1%82%E6%96%B0%E7%9A%84%E5%AF%B9%E7%AD%96%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="生态可持续建筑主要涉及综合用能、多能转换、三向发展、增效资源、自然空调、立体绿化、生态平衡、智能运行、持续发展、卫生、安全等。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%94%9F%E6%80%81%E5%8F%AF%E6%8C%81%E7%BB%AD%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E6%B6%89%E5%8F%8A%E7%BB%BC%E5%90%88%E7%94%A8%E8%83%BD%E3%80%81%E5%A4%9A%E8%83%BD%E8%BD%AC%E6%8D%A2%E3%80%81%E4%B8%89%E5%90%91%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E3%80%81%E5%A2%9E%E6%95%88%E8%B5%84%E6%BA%90%E3%80%81%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6%E7%A9%BA%E8%B0%83%E3%80%81%E7%AB%8B%E4%BD%93%E7%BB%BF%E5%8C%96%E3%80%81%E7%94%9F%E6%80%81%E5%B9%B3%E8%A1%A1%E3%80%81%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E3%80%81%E6%8C%81%E7%BB%AD%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E3%80%81%E5%8D%AB%E7%94%9F%E3%80%81%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E7%AD%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="注：生态通常是指生物的生活状态，即生物在一定的自然环境下生存和发展的状态。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%B3%A8%EF%BC%9A%E7%94%9F%E6%80%81%E9%80%9A%E5%B8%B8%E6%98%AF%E6%8C%87%E7%94%9F%E7%89%A9%E7%9A%84%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E7%8A%B6%E6%80%81%EF%BC%8C%E5%8D%B3%E7%94%9F%E7%89%A9%E5%9C%A8%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%9A%E7%9A%84%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E4%B8%8B%E7%94%9F%E5%AD%98%E5%92%8C%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E7%9A%84%E7%8A%B6%E6%80%81%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
