    </outline>
    <outline text="2.绿色建筑" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2.%E7%BB%BF%E8%89%B2%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="绿色建筑是指：在建筑的全寿命周期内，最大限度地节约资源（节能、节地、节水、节材），保护环境和减少污染，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%BB%BF%E8%89%B2%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E6%98%AF%E6%8C%87%EF%BC%9A%E5%9C%A8%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%9A%84%E5%85%A8%E5%AF%BF%E5%91%BD%E5%91%A8%E6%9C%9F%E5%86%85%EF%BC%8C%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%90%E5%BA%A6%E5%9C%B0%E8%8A%82%E7%BA%A6%E8%B5%84%E6%BA%90%EF%BC%88%E8%8A%82%E8%83%BD%E3%80%81%E8%8A%82%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%81%E8%8A%82%E6%B0%B4%E3%80%81%E8%8A%82%E6%9D%90%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%8C%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%92%8C%E5%87%8F%E5%B0%91%E6%B1%A1%E6%9F%93%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="为人们提供健康、适用、高效的使用空间，与自然和谐共生的建筑。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%BA%E4%BA%BA%E4%BB%AC%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%E3%80%81%E9%80%82%E7%94%A8%E3%80%81%E9%AB%98%E6%95%88%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8E%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6%E5%92%8C%E8%B0%90%E5%85%B1%E7%94%9F%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      </outline>
      <outline text="为贯彻国家相关的技术经济政策，节约资源，保护环境，规范绿色建筑的评价，推进可持续发展，国家制定了《绿色建筑评价标准》GB/T50378-2014。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%BA%E8%B4%AF%E5%BD%BB%E5%9B%BD%E5%AE%B6%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3%E7%9A%84%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E6%94%BF%E7%AD%96%EF%BC%8C%E8%8A%82%E7%BA%A6%E8%B5%84%E6%BA%90%EF%BC%8C%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%EF%BC%8C%E8%A7%84%E8%8C%83%E7%BB%BF%E8%89%B2%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%9A%84%E8%AF%84%E4%BB%B7%EF%BC%8C%E6%8E%A8%E8%BF%9B%E5%8F%AF%E6%8C%81%E7%BB%AD%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%EF%BC%8C%E5%9B%BD%E5%AE%B6%E5%88%B6%E5%AE%9A%E4%BA%86%E3%80%8A%E7%BB%BF%E8%89%B2%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%AF%84%E4%BB%B7%E6%A0%87%E5%87%86%E3%80%8BGB/T50378-2014%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="绿色建筑的评价应以单栋建筑或建筑群作为评价对象。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%BB%BF%E8%89%B2%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%9A%84%E8%AF%84%E4%BB%B7%E5%BA%94%E4%BB%A5%E5%8D%95%E6%A0%8B%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E6%88%96%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%BE%A4%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%BA%E8%AF%84%E4%BB%B7%E5%AF%B9%E8%B1%A1%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="评价体系由7类指标组成，每类指标均包括控制项与评分项；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%AF%84%E4%BB%B7%E4%BD%93%E7%B3%BB%E7%94%B17%E7%B1%BB%E6%8C%87%E6%A0%87%E7%BB%84%E6%88%90%EF%BC%8C%E6%AF%8F%E7%B1%BB%E6%8C%87%E6%A0%87%E5%9D%87%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E9%A1%B9%E4%B8%8E%E8%AF%84%E5%88%86%E9%A1%B9%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="评价指标体系还统一设置了加分项（详见本书第七章）。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%AF%84%E4%BB%B7%E6%8C%87%E6%A0%87%E4%BD%93%E7%B3%BB%E8%BF%98%E7%BB%9F%E4%B8%80%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE%E4%BA%86%E5%8A%A0%E5%88%86%E9%A1%B9%EF%BC%88%E8%AF%A6%E8%A7%81%E6%9C%AC%E4%B9%A6%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%83%E7%AB%A0%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="" _mubu_text="" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="“环境心理学”首先由心理学家普洛尚斯基（H.Proshansky）和伊特尔森（W.H.Ittelson）等提出。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%BF%83%E7%90%86%E5%AD%A6%E2%80%9D%E9%A6%96%E5%85%88%E7%94%B1%E5%BF%83%E7%90%86%E5%AD%A6%E5%AE%B6%E6%99%AE%E6%B4%9B%E5%B0%9A%E6%96%AF%E5%9F%BA%EF%BC%88H.Proshansky%EF%BC%89%E5%92%8C%E4%BC%8A%E7%89%B9%E5%B0%94%E6%A3%AE%EF%BC%88W.H.Ittelson%EF%BC%89%E7%AD%89%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="因涉及多个学科，所以“环境心理学”有多个指称：建筑心理学、环境设计研究、环境与行为、人与环境研究等。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9B%A0%E6%B6%89%E5%8F%8A%E5%A4%9A%E4%B8%AA%E5%AD%A6%E7%A7%91%EF%BC%8C%E6%89%80%E4%BB%A5%E2%80%9C%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%BF%83%E7%90%86%E5%AD%A6%E2%80%9D%E6%9C%89%E5%A4%9A%E4%B8%AA%E6%8C%87%E7%A7%B0%EF%BC%9A%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%BF%83%E7%90%86%E5%AD%A6%E3%80%81%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E3%80%81%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E4%B8%8E%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%BA%E3%80%81%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%8E%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E7%AD%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="其中英国是起步最早的国家，主要代表人物是特伦斯·李（Terence Lee）和戴维·坎特（David Canter）等。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%85%B6%E4%B8%AD%E8%8B%B1%E5%9B%BD%E6%98%AF%E8%B5%B7%E6%AD%A5%E6%9C%80%E6%97%A9%E7%9A%84%E5%9B%BD%E5%AE%B6%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E4%BA%BA%E7%89%A9%E6%98%AF%E7%89%B9%E4%BC%A6%E6%96%AF%C2%B7%E6%9D%8E%EF%BC%88Terence%20Lee%EF%BC%89%E5%92%8C%E6%88%B4%E7%BB%B4%C2%B7%E5%9D%8E%E7%89%B9%EF%BC%88David%20Canter%EF%BC%89%E7%AD%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="该学科研究人的行为与人所处的物质环境之间的相互关系，并应用这方面的知识改善物质环境。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%AF%A5%E5%AD%A6%E7%A7%91%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E4%BA%BA%E7%9A%84%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%8E%E4%BA%BA%E6%89%80%E5%A4%84%E7%9A%84%E7%89%A9%E8%B4%A8%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E4%B9%8B%E9%97%B4%E7%9A%84%E7%9B%B8%E4%BA%92%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%EF%BC%8C%E5%B9%B6%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%E8%BF%99%E6%96%B9%E9%9D%A2%E7%9A%84%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86%E6%94%B9%E5%96%84%E7%89%A9%E8%B4%A8%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="提高人类的生活质量是环境心理学的基本任务。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%8F%90%E9%AB%98%E4%BA%BA%E7%B1%BB%E7%9A%84%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E8%B4%A8%E9%87%8F%E6%98%AF%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%BF%83%E7%90%86%E5%AD%A6%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E4%BB%BB%E5%8A%A1%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="提高人类对自身及其所处环境的认识，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%8F%90%E9%AB%98%E4%BA%BA%E7%B1%BB%E5%AF%B9%E8%87%AA%E8%BA%AB%E5%8F%8A%E5%85%B6%E6%89%80%E5%A4%84%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%A4%E8%AF%86%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="建立和谐的人与环境之间的关系，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%BB%BA%E7%AB%8B%E5%92%8C%E8%B0%90%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%8E%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E4%B9%8B%E9%97%B4%E7%9A%84%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="是“环境一行为研究”的永恒主题，也是建筑师必须关注的课题之一。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%98%AF%E2%80%9C%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E4%B8%80%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%BA%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E2%80%9D%E7%9A%84%E6%B0%B8%E6%81%92%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%EF%BC%8C%E4%B9%9F%E6%98%AF%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%88%E5%BF%85%E9%A1%BB%E5%85%B3%E6%B3%A8%E7%9A%84%E8%AF%BE%E9%A2%98%E4%B9%8B%E4%B8%80%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（一）环境心理学的主要特点" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%80%EF%BC%89%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%BF%83%E7%90%86%E5%AD%A6%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E7%89%B9%E7%82%B9%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="1.学科的主要特点" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1.%E5%AD%A6%E7%A7%91%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E7%89%B9%E7%82%B9%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（1）把“环境一行为关系”作为一个整体加以研究，强调的是一种交互作用的关系。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E6%8A%8A%E2%80%9C%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E4%B8%80%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%BA%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%E2%80%9D%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E6%95%B4%E4%BD%93%E5%8A%A0%E4%BB%A5%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%EF%BC%8C%E5%BC%BA%E8%B0%83%E7%9A%84%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%80%E7%A7%8D%E4%BA%A4%E4%BA%92%E4%BD%9C%E7%94%A8%E7%9A%84%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（2）几乎所有的研究课题都以实际问题为导向，其基础理论和内容都来源于实际。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E5%87%A0%E4%B9%8E%E6%89%80%E6%9C%89%E7%9A%84%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E8%AF%BE%E9%A2%98%E9%83%BD%E4%BB%A5%E5%AE%9E%E9%99%85%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E4%B8%BA%E5%AF%BC%E5%90%91%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%B6%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA%E5%92%8C%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%E9%83%BD%E6%9D%A5%E6%BA%90%E4%BA%8E%E5%AE%9E%E9%99%85%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="第七节     环境心理学" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%83%E8%8A%82%20%20%20%20%20%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%BF%83%E7%90%86%E5%AD%A6%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="20世纪50~60年代，西方国家的城市环境严重恶化，对人的身心健康和行为产生了各种消极影响，引起多个学科领域研究者的密切关注。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E20%E4%B8%96%E7%BA%AA50~60%E5%B9%B4%E4%BB%A3%EF%BC%8C%E8%A5%BF%E6%96%B9%E5%9B%BD%E5%AE%B6%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E4%B8%A5%E9%87%8D%E6%81%B6%E5%8C%96%EF%BC%8C%E5%AF%B9%E4%BA%BA%E7%9A%84%E8%BA%AB%E5%BF%83%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%E5%92%8C%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%BA%E4%BA%A7%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%86%E5%90%84%E7%A7%8D%E6%B6%88%E6%9E%81%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%EF%BC%8C%E5%BC%95%E8%B5%B7%E5%A4%9A%E4%B8%AA%E5%AD%A6%E7%A7%91%E9%A2%86%E5%9F%9F%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E8%80%85%E7%9A%84%E5%AF%86%E5%88%87%E5%85%B3%E6%B3%A8%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="“环境一行为研究”起源于20世纪60年代的北美，此后在欧洲（英国、法国、瑞典等国）展开并逐步扩大到世界其他地方；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E4%B8%80%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%BA%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E2%80%9D%E8%B5%B7%E6%BA%90%E4%BA%8E20%E4%B8%96%E7%BA%AA60%E5%B9%B4%E4%BB%A3%E7%9A%84%E5%8C%97%E7%BE%8E%EF%BC%8C%E6%AD%A4%E5%90%8E%E5%9C%A8%E6%AC%A7%E6%B4%B2%EF%BC%88%E8%8B%B1%E5%9B%BD%E3%80%81%E6%B3%95%E5%9B%BD%E3%80%81%E7%91%9E%E5%85%B8%E7%AD%89%E5%9B%BD%EF%BC%89%E5%B1%95%E5%BC%80%E5%B9%B6%E9%80%90%E6%AD%A5%E6%89%A9%E5%A4%A7%E5%88%B0%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E5%9C%B0%E6%96%B9%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="最终形成了“环境心理学”这门新兴的独立学科。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%9C%80%E7%BB%88%E5%BD%A2%E6%88%90%E4%BA%86%E2%80%9C%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%BF%83%E7%90%86%E5%AD%A6%E2%80%9D%E8%BF%99%E9%97%A8%E6%96%B0%E5%85%B4%E7%9A%84%E7%8B%AC%E7%AB%8B%E5%AD%A6%E7%A7%91%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="2.新的研究方向" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2.%E6%96%B0%E7%9A%84%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E6%96%B9%E5%90%91%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（1）自然环境对行为的积极影响。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%AF%B9%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%BA%E7%9A%84%E7%A7%AF%E6%9E%81%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（2）亲环境行为研究（指对环境表示友好的行为，具体有环境保护、节约能源……）。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E4%BA%B2%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%BA%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%EF%BC%88%E6%8C%87%E5%AF%B9%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E8%A1%A8%E7%A4%BA%E5%8F%8B%E5%A5%BD%E7%9A%84%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%BA%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%B7%E4%BD%93%E6%9C%89%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4%E3%80%81%E8%8A%82%E7%BA%A6%E8%83%BD%E6%BA%90%E2%80%A6%E2%80%A6%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（3）景观的偏爱与评价。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E6%99%AF%E8%A7%82%E7%9A%84%E5%81%8F%E7%88%B1%E4%B8%8E%E8%AF%84%E4%BB%B7%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（4）各类特殊场所中的环境行为问题。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%884%EF%BC%89%E5%90%84%E7%B1%BB%E7%89%B9%E6%AE%8A%E5%9C%BA%E6%89%80%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%BA%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（二）感觉、知觉与认知" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%BA%8C%EF%BC%89%E6%84%9F%E8%A7%89%E3%80%81%E7%9F%A5%E8%A7%89%E4%B8%8E%E8%AE%A4%E7%9F%A5%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="1.感觉" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1.%E6%84%9F%E8%A7%89%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="人的认识活动从感觉开始，通过感觉我们能了解客观事物的各种属性，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BA%BA%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%A4%E8%AF%86%E6%B4%BB%E5%8A%A8%E4%BB%8E%E6%84%9F%E8%A7%89%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8B%EF%BC%8C%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87%E6%84%9F%E8%A7%89%E6%88%91%E4%BB%AC%E8%83%BD%E4%BA%86%E8%A7%A3%E5%AE%A2%E8%A7%82%E4%BA%8B%E7%89%A9%E7%9A%84%E5%90%84%E7%A7%8D%E5%B1%9E%E6%80%A7%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="如物体的形状、颜色、气味、质感等。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%A6%82%E7%89%A9%E4%BD%93%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%A2%E7%8A%B6%E3%80%81%E9%A2%9C%E8%89%B2%E3%80%81%E6%B0%94%E5%91%B3%E3%80%81%E8%B4%A8%E6%84%9F%E7%AD%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="感觉是意识和心理活动的重要依据，也是人脑与外部世界的直接联系。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%84%9F%E8%A7%89%E6%98%AF%E6%84%8F%E8%AF%86%E5%92%8C%E5%BF%83%E7%90%86%E6%B4%BB%E5%8A%A8%E7%9A%84%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81%E4%BE%9D%E6%8D%AE%EF%BC%8C%E4%B9%9F%E6%98%AF%E4%BA%BA%E8%84%91%E4%B8%8E%E5%A4%96%E9%83%A8%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E7%9A%84%E7%9B%B4%E6%8E%A5%E8%81%94%E7%B3%BB%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（3）具有浓厚的多学科性质，以现场研究为主，采用来自多学科的、富有创新精神的折中研究方法。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E5%85%B7%E6%9C%89%E6%B5%93%E5%8E%9A%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%9A%E5%AD%A6%E7%A7%91%E6%80%A7%E8%B4%A8%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A5%E7%8E%B0%E5%9C%BA%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%BB%EF%BC%8C%E9%87%87%E7%94%A8%E6%9D%A5%E8%87%AA%E5%A4%9A%E5%AD%A6%E7%A7%91%E7%9A%84%E3%80%81%E5%AF%8C%E6%9C%89%E5%88%9B%E6%96%B0%E7%B2%BE%E7%A5%9E%E7%9A%84%E6%8A%98%E4%B8%AD%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="3.认知" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E3.%E8%AE%A4%E7%9F%A5%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="认知是指获得知识的过程，包括感知、表象、记忆、思维等；而思维是它的核心。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%AE%A4%E7%9F%A5%E6%98%AF%E6%8C%87%E8%8E%B7%E5%BE%97%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86%E7%9A%84%E8%BF%87%E7%A8%8B%EF%BC%8C%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E6%84%9F%E7%9F%A5%E3%80%81%E8%A1%A8%E8%B1%A1%E3%80%81%E8%AE%B0%E5%BF%86%E3%80%81%E6%80%9D%E7%BB%B4%E7%AD%89%EF%BC%9B%E8%80%8C%E6%80%9D%E7%BB%B4%E6%98%AF%E5%AE%83%E7%9A%84%E6%A0%B8%E5%BF%83%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="让·皮亚杰（J.Piaget）提出了发生认知论，强调“图式”的作用。在皮亚杰的理论中，动作的结构或组织（即固有的知识或经验）被称为“图式”。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%AE%A9%C2%B7%E7%9A%AE%E4%BA%9A%E6%9D%B0%EF%BC%88J.Piaget%EF%BC%89%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E4%BA%86%E5%8F%91%E7%94%9F%E8%AE%A4%E7%9F%A5%E8%AE%BA%EF%BC%8C%E5%BC%BA%E8%B0%83%E2%80%9C%E5%9B%BE%E5%BC%8F%E2%80%9D%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%9C%E7%94%A8%E3%80%82%E5%9C%A8%E7%9A%AE%E4%BA%9A%E6%9D%B0%E7%9A%84%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA%E4%B8%AD%EF%BC%8C%E5%8A%A8%E4%BD%9C%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E6%88%96%E7%BB%84%E7%BB%87%EF%BC%88%E5%8D%B3%E5%9B%BA%E6%9C%89%E7%9A%84%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86%E6%88%96%E7%BB%8F%E9%AA%8C%EF%BC%89%E8%A2%AB%E7%A7%B0%E4%B8%BA%E2%80%9C%E5%9B%BE%E5%BC%8F%E2%80%9D%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="图式的形成是以时间为代价的。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9B%BE%E5%BC%8F%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%A2%E6%88%90%E6%98%AF%E4%BB%A5%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%E4%B8%BA%E4%BB%A3%E4%BB%B7%E7%9A%84%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      </outline>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（三）环境知觉" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%89%EF%BC%89%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E7%9F%A5%E8%A7%89%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="环境知觉研究的是人（群体）对来自真实环境的刺激所产生的即时而又直接的反应。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E7%9F%A5%E8%A7%89%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E7%9A%84%E6%98%AF%E4%BA%BA%EF%BC%88%E7%BE%A4%E4%BD%93%EF%BC%89%E5%AF%B9%E6%9D%A5%E8%87%AA%E7%9C%9F%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E7%9A%84%E5%88%BA%E6%BF%80%E6%89%80%E4%BA%A7%E7%94%9F%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%B3%E6%97%B6%E8%80%8C%E5%8F%88%E7%9B%B4%E6%8E%A5%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%8D%E5%BA%94%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="即时（时间）、在场（空间）和直接是三个必要充分条件。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%8D%B3%E6%97%B6%EF%BC%88%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%EF%BC%89%E3%80%81%E5%9C%A8%E5%9C%BA%EF%BC%88%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%EF%BC%89%E5%92%8C%E7%9B%B4%E6%8E%A5%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%89%E4%B8%AA%E5%BF%85%E8%A6%81%E5%85%85%E5%88%86%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="环境心理学有4种比较流行的理论：源自康德哲学思想的格式塔知觉理论、概率知觉理论、生态知觉理论，以及基于多学科研究的环境知觉理论。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%BF%83%E7%90%86%E5%AD%A6%E6%9C%894%E7%A7%8D%E6%AF%94%E8%BE%83%E6%B5%81%E8%A1%8C%E7%9A%84%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA%EF%BC%9A%E6%BA%90%E8%87%AA%E5%BA%B7%E5%BE%B7%E5%93%B2%E5%AD%A6%E6%80%9D%E6%83%B3%E7%9A%84%E6%A0%BC%E5%BC%8F%E5%A1%94%E7%9F%A5%E8%A7%89%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA%E3%80%81%E6%A6%82%E7%8E%87%E7%9F%A5%E8%A7%89%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA%E3%80%81%E7%94%9F%E6%80%81%E7%9F%A5%E8%A7%89%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%8A%E5%9F%BA%E4%BA%8E%E5%A4%9A%E5%AD%A6%E7%A7%91%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E7%9A%84%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E7%9F%A5%E8%A7%89%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="1.格式塔（Gestalt）知觉理论" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1.%E6%A0%BC%E5%BC%8F%E5%A1%94%EF%BC%88Gestalt%EF%BC%89%E7%9F%A5%E8%A7%89%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="早在1890年，奥地利哲学家、心理学家厄棱费尔（Christian Freiherr Von Ehren-fels）就写了《论格式塔性质》的论文。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%97%A9%E5%9C%A81890%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%8C%E5%A5%A5%E5%9C%B0%E5%88%A9%E5%93%B2%E5%AD%A6%E5%AE%B6%E3%80%81%E5%BF%83%E7%90%86%E5%AD%A6%E5%AE%B6%E5%8E%84%E6%A3%B1%E8%B4%B9%E5%B0%94%EF%BC%88Christian%20Freiherr%20Von%20Ehren-fels%EF%BC%89%E5%B0%B1%E5%86%99%E4%BA%86%E3%80%8A%E8%AE%BA%E6%A0%BC%E5%BC%8F%E5%A1%94%E6%80%A7%E8%B4%A8%E3%80%8B%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%BA%E6%96%87%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="他认为证方形由四条直线组成……因为这四条直线本身只具有直线的性质，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BB%96%E8%AE%A4%E4%B8%BA%E8%AF%81%E6%96%B9%E5%BD%A2%E7%94%B1%E5%9B%9B%E6%9D%A1%E7%9B%B4%E7%BA%BF%E7%BB%84%E6%88%90%E2%80%A6%E2%80%A6%E5%9B%A0%E4%B8%BA%E8%BF%99%E5%9B%9B%E6%9D%A1%E7%9B%B4%E7%BA%BF%E6%9C%AC%E8%BA%AB%E5%8F%AA%E5%85%B7%E6%9C%89%E7%9B%B4%E7%BA%BF%E7%9A%84%E6%80%A7%E8%B4%A8%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="而正方形是经过重新组织结合而成的崭新整体……他把这种整体所具有的性质称为格式塔”。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%80%8C%E6%AD%A3%E6%96%B9%E5%BD%A2%E6%98%AF%E7%BB%8F%E8%BF%87%E9%87%8D%E6%96%B0%E7%BB%84%E7%BB%87%E7%BB%93%E5%90%88%E8%80%8C%E6%88%90%E7%9A%84%E5%B4%AD%E6%96%B0%E6%95%B4%E4%BD%93%E2%80%A6%E2%80%A6%E4%BB%96%E6%8A%8A%E8%BF%99%E7%A7%8D%E6%95%B4%E4%BD%93%E6%89%80%E5%85%B7%E6%9C%89%E7%9A%84%E6%80%A7%E8%B4%A8%E7%A7%B0%E4%B8%BA%E6%A0%BC%E5%BC%8F%E5%A1%94%E2%80%9D%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      </outline>
    </outline>
    <outline text="1910年，惠泰海默研究了“似动现象”，电影就是利用这一原理摄制和放映的。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1910%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%8C%E6%83%A0%E6%B3%B0%E6%B5%B7%E9%BB%98%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E4%BA%86%E2%80%9C%E4%BC%BC%E5%8A%A8%E7%8E%B0%E8%B1%A1%E2%80%9D%EF%BC%8C%E7%94%B5%E5%BD%B1%E5%B0%B1%E6%98%AF%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8%E8%BF%99%E4%B8%80%E5%8E%9F%E7%90%86%E6%91%84%E5%88%B6%E5%92%8C%E6%94%BE%E6%98%A0%E7%9A%84%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="1912年兴起，其主要代表人物为马克斯·韦特海默（Max Wertheimer）、库尔特·考夫卡（Kurt Koffka）等。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1912%E5%B9%B4%E5%85%B4%E8%B5%B7%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%B6%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E4%BA%BA%E7%89%A9%E4%B8%BA%E9%A9%AC%E5%85%8B%E6%96%AF%C2%B7%E9%9F%A6%E7%89%B9%E6%B5%B7%E9%BB%98%EF%BC%88Max%20Wertheimer%EF%BC%89%E3%80%81%E5%BA%93%E5%B0%94%E7%89%B9%C2%B7%E8%80%83%E5%A4%AB%E5%8D%A1%EF%BC%88Kurt%20Koffka%EF%BC%89%E7%AD%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="2.知觉" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2.%E7%9F%A5%E8%A7%89%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="把感觉到的所有个别属性的信息进行综合，加上经验的参与，就形成了一个对事物的整体印象，这种信息整合的过程就是知觉；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%8A%8A%E6%84%9F%E8%A7%89%E5%88%B0%E7%9A%84%E6%89%80%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%AA%E5%88%AB%E5%B1%9E%E6%80%A7%E7%9A%84%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E7%BB%BC%E5%90%88%EF%BC%8C%E5%8A%A0%E4%B8%8A%E7%BB%8F%E9%AA%8C%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%82%E4%B8%8E%EF%BC%8C%E5%B0%B1%E5%BD%A2%E6%88%90%E4%BA%86%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E5%AF%B9%E4%BA%8B%E7%89%A9%E7%9A%84%E6%95%B4%E4%BD%93%E5%8D%B0%E8%B1%A1%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%99%E7%A7%8D%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E6%95%B4%E5%90%88%E7%9A%84%E8%BF%87%E7%A8%8B%E5%B0%B1%E6%98%AF%E7%9F%A5%E8%A7%89%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="知觉的产生是以各种形式感觉的存在为前提的。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%9F%A5%E8%A7%89%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%A7%E7%94%9F%E6%98%AF%E4%BB%A5%E5%90%84%E7%A7%8D%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E6%84%9F%E8%A7%89%E7%9A%84%E5%AD%98%E5%9C%A8%E4%B8%BA%E5%89%8D%E6%8F%90%E7%9A%84%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="德语“格式塔”是指形式或图形，还有组织的含义，引申为“有组织的整体”。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%BE%B7%E8%AF%AD%E2%80%9C%E6%A0%BC%E5%BC%8F%E5%A1%94%E2%80%9D%E6%98%AF%E6%8C%87%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E6%88%96%E5%9B%BE%E5%BD%A2%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%98%E6%9C%89%E7%BB%84%E7%BB%87%E7%9A%84%E5%90%AB%E4%B9%89%EF%BC%8C%E5%BC%95%E7%94%B3%E4%B8%BA%E2%80%9C%E6%9C%89%E7%BB%84%E7%BB%87%E7%9A%84%E6%95%B4%E4%BD%93%E2%80%9D%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（1）基本观点：主要有“知觉的整体性”“同型论”“场作用力”。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E8%A7%82%E7%82%B9%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E6%9C%89%E2%80%9C%E7%9F%A5%E8%A7%89%E7%9A%84%E6%95%B4%E4%BD%93%E6%80%A7%E2%80%9D%E2%80%9C%E5%90%8C%E5%9E%8B%E8%AE%BA%E2%80%9D%E2%80%9C%E5%9C%BA%E4%BD%9C%E7%94%A8%E5%8A%9B%E2%80%9D%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（2）组织原则：“图形与背景”（俗称图底之分）“群化原则”和“简化原则”。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E7%BB%84%E7%BB%87%E5%8E%9F%E5%88%99%EF%BC%9A%E2%80%9C%E5%9B%BE%E5%BD%A2%E4%B8%8E%E8%83%8C%E6%99%AF%E2%80%9D%EF%BC%88%E4%BF%97%E7%A7%B0%E5%9B%BE%E5%BA%95%E4%B9%8B%E5%88%86%EF%BC%89%E2%80%9C%E7%BE%A4%E5%8C%96%E5%8E%9F%E5%88%99%E2%80%9D%E5%92%8C%E2%80%9C%E7%AE%80%E5%8C%96%E5%8E%9F%E5%88%99%E2%80%9D%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（3）图底关系在环境设计中具有重要的意义，易成图形的主要条件如下：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E5%9B%BE%E5%BA%95%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%E5%9C%A8%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%B7%E6%9C%89%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81%E7%9A%84%E6%84%8F%E4%B9%89%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%93%E6%88%90%E5%9B%BE%E5%BD%A2%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%E5%A6%82%E4%B8%8B%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="1）小面积比大面积易成图形；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1%EF%BC%89%E5%B0%8F%E9%9D%A2%E7%A7%AF%E6%AF%94%E5%A4%A7%E9%9D%A2%E7%A7%AF%E6%98%93%E6%88%90%E5%9B%BE%E5%BD%A2%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="2）水平和垂直形态比斜向形态易成图形；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2%EF%BC%89%E6%B0%B4%E5%B9%B3%E5%92%8C%E5%9E%82%E7%9B%B4%E5%BD%A2%E6%80%81%E6%AF%94%E6%96%9C%E5%90%91%E5%BD%A2%E6%80%81%E6%98%93%E6%88%90%E5%9B%BE%E5%BD%A2%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="3）对称形态易成图形；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E3%EF%BC%89%E5%AF%B9%E7%A7%B0%E5%BD%A2%E6%80%81%E6%98%93%E6%88%90%E5%9B%BE%E5%BD%A2%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="4）封闭形态比开放形态易成图形；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E4%EF%BC%89%E5%B0%81%E9%97%AD%E5%BD%A2%E6%80%81%E6%AF%94%E5%BC%80%E6%94%BE%E5%BD%A2%E6%80%81%E6%98%93%E6%88%90%E5%9B%BE%E5%BD%A2%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="5）单个的凸出形态比凹人形态易成图形；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E5%EF%BC%89%E5%8D%95%E4%B8%AA%E7%9A%84%E5%87%B8%E5%87%BA%E5%BD%A2%E6%80%81%E6%AF%94%E5%87%B9%E4%BA%BA%E5%BD%A2%E6%80%81%E6%98%93%E6%88%90%E5%9B%BE%E5%BD%A2%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="6）动态比静态的对象易成图形；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E6%EF%BC%89%E5%8A%A8%E6%80%81%E6%AF%94%E9%9D%99%E6%80%81%E7%9A%84%E5%AF%B9%E8%B1%A1%E6%98%93%E6%88%90%E5%9B%BE%E5%BD%A2%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="7）整体性强的易成图形；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E7%EF%BC%89%E6%95%B4%E4%BD%93%E6%80%A7%E5%BC%BA%E7%9A%84%E6%98%93%E6%88%90%E5%9B%BE%E5%BD%A2%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="9）有明确意义的形态易成图形。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E9%EF%BC%89%E6%9C%89%E6%98%8E%E7%A1%AE%E6%84%8F%E4%B9%89%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%A2%E6%80%81%E6%98%93%E6%88%90%E5%9B%BE%E5%BD%A2%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="2.概率知觉理论" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2.%E6%A6%82%E7%8E%87%E7%9F%A5%E8%A7%89%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="格式塔知觉理论主要强调视知觉的直觉作用，而由埃贡·布伦斯维克（Egon Bruns-wick）提出的概率知觉理论则更重视在真实环境实验中所得出的结论，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%A0%BC%E5%BC%8F%E5%A1%94%E7%9F%A5%E8%A7%89%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E5%BC%BA%E8%B0%83%E8%A7%86%E7%9F%A5%E8%A7%89%E7%9A%84%E7%9B%B4%E8%A7%89%E4%BD%9C%E7%94%A8%EF%BC%8C%E8%80%8C%E7%94%B1%E5%9F%83%E8%B4%A1%C2%B7%E5%B8%83%E4%BC%A6%E6%96%AF%E7%BB%B4%E5%85%8B%EF%BC%88Egon%20Bruns-wick%EF%BC%89%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E7%9A%84%E6%A6%82%E7%8E%87%E7%9F%A5%E8%A7%89%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA%E5%88%99%E6%9B%B4%E9%87%8D%E8%A7%86%E5%9C%A8%E7%9C%9F%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%AE%9E%E9%AA%8C%E4%B8%AD%E6%89%80%E5%BE%97%E5%87%BA%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%93%E8%AE%BA%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="更重视后天知识、经验和学习的作用。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%9B%B4%E9%87%8D%E8%A7%86%E5%90%8E%E5%A4%A9%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86%E3%80%81%E7%BB%8F%E9%AA%8C%E5%92%8C%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%9C%E7%94%A8%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="3.生态知觉理论" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E3.%E7%94%9F%E6%80%81%E7%9F%A5%E8%A7%89%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="生态知觉理论主要强调机体先天的本能和环境所提供信息的准确性。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%94%9F%E6%80%81%E7%9F%A5%E8%A7%89%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E5%BC%BA%E8%B0%83%E6%9C%BA%E4%BD%93%E5%85%88%E5%A4%A9%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%AC%E8%83%BD%E5%92%8C%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E6%89%80%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E7%9A%84%E5%87%86%E7%A1%AE%E6%80%A7%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="吉布森（James J.Gibson）与布伦斯维克的观点相反，更强调人的生存适应，本能的行为习性，缘自本能的情感反应。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%90%89%E5%B8%83%E6%A3%AE%EF%BC%88James%20J.Gibson%EF%BC%89%E4%B8%8E%E5%B8%83%E4%BC%A6%E6%96%AF%E7%BB%B4%E5%85%8B%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%82%E7%82%B9%E7%9B%B8%E5%8F%8D%EF%BC%8C%E6%9B%B4%E5%BC%BA%E8%B0%83%E4%BA%BA%E7%9A%84%E7%94%9F%E5%AD%98%E9%80%82%E5%BA%94%EF%BC%8C%E6%9C%AC%E8%83%BD%E7%9A%84%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%BA%E4%B9%A0%E6%80%A7%EF%BC%8C%E7%BC%98%E8%87%AA%E6%9C%AC%E8%83%BD%E7%9A%84%E6%83%85%E6%84%9F%E5%8F%8D%E5%BA%94%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="我们的基本情感反应—愉悦和恐惧，这是物种对祖先经验的集体记忆。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%88%91%E4%BB%AC%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%83%85%E6%84%9F%E5%8F%8D%E5%BA%94%E2%80%94%E6%84%89%E6%82%A6%E5%92%8C%E6%81%90%E6%83%A7%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%99%E6%98%AF%E7%89%A9%E7%A7%8D%E5%AF%B9%E7%A5%96%E5%85%88%E7%BB%8F%E9%AA%8C%E7%9A%84%E9%9B%86%E4%BD%93%E8%AE%B0%E5%BF%86%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="4.基于多学科研究的环境知觉理论" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E4.%E5%9F%BA%E4%BA%8E%E5%A4%9A%E5%AD%A6%E7%A7%91%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E7%9A%84%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E7%9F%A5%E8%A7%89%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="环境知觉是一个复杂的心理过程，涉及环境信息的特点、与情绪反应有关的主观偏爱、感知者的遗传基因、生理和心理特点、社会文化背景、接受信息的渠道和方式，以及人与环境信息的交互作用等。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E7%9F%A5%E8%A7%89%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E5%A4%8D%E6%9D%82%E7%9A%84%E5%BF%83%E7%90%86%E8%BF%87%E7%A8%8B%EF%BC%8C%E6%B6%89%E5%8F%8A%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E7%9A%84%E7%89%B9%E7%82%B9%E3%80%81%E4%B8%8E%E6%83%85%E7%BB%AA%E5%8F%8D%E5%BA%94%E6%9C%89%E5%85%B3%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%BB%E8%A7%82%E5%81%8F%E7%88%B1%E3%80%81%E6%84%9F%E7%9F%A5%E8%80%85%E7%9A%84%E9%81%97%E4%BC%A0%E5%9F%BA%E5%9B%A0%E3%80%81%E7%94%9F%E7%90%86%E5%92%8C%E5%BF%83%E7%90%86%E7%89%B9%E7%82%B9%E3%80%81%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96%E8%83%8C%E6%99%AF%E3%80%81%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%97%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E7%9A%84%E6%B8%A0%E9%81%93%E5%92%8C%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%8A%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%8E%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%A4%E4%BA%92%E4%BD%9C%E7%94%A8%E7%AD%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="8）奇异的或与众不同的易成图形；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E8%EF%BC%89%E5%A5%87%E5%BC%82%E7%9A%84%E6%88%96%E4%B8%8E%E4%BC%97%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E7%9A%84%E6%98%93%E6%88%90%E5%9B%BE%E5%BD%A2%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（四）环境认知" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E5%9B%9B%EF%BC%89%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E8%AE%A4%E7%9F%A5%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="环境认知是研究人如何在环境中定向、找路、寻址、判断距离远近、时间长短，并理解环境所包含的意义。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E8%AE%A4%E7%9F%A5%E6%98%AF%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E4%BA%BA%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E5%9C%A8%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E4%B8%AD%E5%AE%9A%E5%90%91%E3%80%81%E6%89%BE%E8%B7%AF%E3%80%81%E5%AF%BB%E5%9D%80%E3%80%81%E5%88%A4%E6%96%AD%E8%B7%9D%E7%A6%BB%E8%BF%9C%E8%BF%91%E3%80%81%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%E9%95%BF%E7%9F%AD%EF%BC%8C%E5%B9%B6%E7%90%86%E8%A7%A3%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E6%89%80%E5%8C%85%E5%90%AB%E7%9A%84%E6%84%8F%E4%B9%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="人识别和理解环境有赖于在记忆中重现空间环境的形象。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BA%BA%E8%AF%86%E5%88%AB%E5%92%8C%E7%90%86%E8%A7%A3%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E6%9C%89%E8%B5%96%E4%BA%8E%E5%9C%A8%E8%AE%B0%E5%BF%86%E4%B8%AD%E9%87%8D%E7%8E%B0%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%A2%E8%B1%A1%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="曾经感知过的事物在记忆中重现的形象被称为“意象”或“表象”，具体空间环境的意象被称为“认知地图”，是环境意象的主要组成部分。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%9B%BE%E7%BB%8F%E6%84%9F%E7%9F%A5%E8%BF%87%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%8B%E7%89%A9%E5%9C%A8%E8%AE%B0%E5%BF%86%E4%B8%AD%E9%87%8D%E7%8E%B0%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%A2%E8%B1%A1%E8%A2%AB%E7%A7%B0%E4%B8%BA%E2%80%9C%E6%84%8F%E8%B1%A1%E2%80%9D%E6%88%96%E2%80%9C%E8%A1%A8%E8%B1%A1%E2%80%9D%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%B7%E4%BD%93%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E7%9A%84%E6%84%8F%E8%B1%A1%E8%A2%AB%E7%A7%B0%E4%B8%BA%E2%80%9C%E8%AE%A4%E7%9F%A5%E5%9C%B0%E5%9B%BE%E2%80%9D%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%AF%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E6%84%8F%E8%B1%A1%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E7%BB%84%E6%88%90%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="1.城市认知地围" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1.%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%AE%A4%E7%9F%A5%E5%9C%B0%E5%9B%B4%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="美国城市规划专家凯文·林奇（Kevin Lynch）提出城市认知地图由5个基本要素组成，即：路径、标志、节点、区域和边界。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E4%B8%93%E5%AE%B6%E5%87%AF%E6%96%87%C2%B7%E6%9E%97%E5%A5%87%EF%BC%88Kevin%20Lynch%EF%BC%89%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%AE%A4%E7%9F%A5%E5%9C%B0%E5%9B%BE%E7%94%B15%E4%B8%AA%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E8%A6%81%E7%B4%A0%E7%BB%84%E6%88%90%EF%BC%8C%E5%8D%B3%EF%BC%9A%E8%B7%AF%E5%BE%84%E3%80%81%E6%A0%87%E5%BF%97%E3%80%81%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9%E3%80%81%E5%8C%BA%E5%9F%9F%E5%92%8C%E8%BE%B9%E7%95%8C%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="3.认知距离" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E3.%E8%AE%A4%E7%9F%A5%E8%B7%9D%E7%A6%BB%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="人心中所意识到的距离与实际距离是有差别的，认知距离就是研究人们怎样在头脑中凭记忆判断距离的长短，也称为“全观距离”。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BA%BA%E5%BF%83%E4%B8%AD%E6%89%80%E6%84%8F%E8%AF%86%E5%88%B0%E7%9A%84%E8%B7%9D%E7%A6%BB%E4%B8%8E%E5%AE%9E%E9%99%85%E8%B7%9D%E7%A6%BB%E6%98%AF%E6%9C%89%E5%B7%AE%E5%88%AB%E7%9A%84%EF%BC%8C%E8%AE%A4%E7%9F%A5%E8%B7%9D%E7%A6%BB%E5%B0%B1%E6%98%AF%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E4%BA%BA%E4%BB%AC%E6%80%8E%E6%A0%B7%E5%9C%A8%E5%A4%B4%E8%84%91%E4%B8%AD%E5%87%AD%E8%AE%B0%E5%BF%86%E5%88%A4%E6%96%AD%E8%B7%9D%E7%A6%BB%E7%9A%84%E9%95%BF%E7%9F%AD%EF%BC%8C%E4%B9%9F%E7%A7%B0%E4%B8%BA%E2%80%9C%E5%85%A8%E8%A7%82%E8%B7%9D%E7%A6%BB%E2%80%9D%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="2.空间定向" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2.%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E5%AE%9A%E5%90%91%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="要了解不同场所在空间中的位置，并从集一场所前往另一场所，就要建立定向系统，包括位置感、方向感和距离感。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%A6%81%E4%BA%86%E8%A7%A3%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E5%9C%BA%E6%89%80%E5%9C%A8%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%8D%E7%BD%AE%EF%BC%8C%E5%B9%B6%E4%BB%8E%E9%9B%86%E4%B8%80%E5%9C%BA%E6%89%80%E5%89%8D%E5%BE%80%E5%8F%A6%E4%B8%80%E5%9C%BA%E6%89%80%EF%BC%8C%E5%B0%B1%E8%A6%81%E5%BB%BA%E7%AB%8B%E5%AE%9A%E5%90%91%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%EF%BC%8C%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E4%BD%8D%E7%BD%AE%E6%84%9F%E3%80%81%E6%96%B9%E5%90%91%E6%84%9F%E5%92%8C%E8%B7%9D%E7%A6%BB%E6%84%9F%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="定向系统存在文化差异，并受自然环境特征的影响。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%AE%9A%E5%90%91%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E5%AD%98%E5%9C%A8%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96%E5%B7%AE%E5%BC%82%EF%BC%8C%E5%B9%B6%E5%8F%97%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E7%89%B9%E5%BE%81%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（五）环境一行为关系的理论" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%BA%94%EF%BC%89%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E4%B8%80%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%BA%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%E7%9A%84%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="环境心理学是一门多学科交叉的新兴的学科领域，许多理论研究成果并不成熟，目前还没有一种理论能够解释所有的环境一行为现象。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%BF%83%E7%90%86%E5%AD%A6%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%80%E9%97%A8%E5%A4%9A%E5%AD%A6%E7%A7%91%E4%BA%A4%E5%8F%89%E7%9A%84%E6%96%B0%E5%85%B4%E7%9A%84%E5%AD%A6%E7%A7%91%E9%A2%86%E5%9F%9F%EF%BC%8C%E8%AE%B8%E5%A4%9A%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E6%88%90%E6%9E%9C%E5%B9%B6%E4%B8%8D%E6%88%90%E7%86%9F%EF%BC%8C%E7%9B%AE%E5%89%8D%E8%BF%98%E6%B2%A1%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%80%E7%A7%8D%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA%E8%83%BD%E5%A4%9F%E8%A7%A3%E9%87%8A%E6%89%80%E6%9C%89%E7%9A%84%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E4%B8%80%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%BA%E7%8E%B0%E8%B1%A1%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="以环境刺激对人的影响出发，主要有下列理论：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BB%A5%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%88%BA%E6%BF%80%E5%AF%B9%E4%BA%BA%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%E5%87%BA%E5%8F%91%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%8B%E5%88%97%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（1）唤醒理论。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E5%94%A4%E9%86%92%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（2）环境应激理论。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%BA%94%E6%BF%80%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（3）对于个体行为与环境的关系的研究，有环境负荷理论、适应水平理论、行为约束理论等。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E5%AF%B9%E4%BA%8E%E4%B8%AA%E4%BD%93%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%8E%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E7%9A%84%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%E7%9A%84%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%EF%BC%8C%E6%9C%89%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E8%B4%9F%E8%8D%B7%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA%E3%80%81%E9%80%82%E5%BA%94%E6%B0%B4%E5%B9%B3%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA%E3%80%81%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%BA%E7%BA%A6%E6%9D%9F%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA%E7%AD%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（4）对于非个体行为与环境关系的研究，有行为场景理论。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%884%EF%BC%89%E5%AF%B9%E4%BA%8E%E9%9D%9E%E4%B8%AA%E4%BD%93%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%8E%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%E7%9A%84%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%EF%BC%8C%E6%9C%89%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%BA%E5%9C%BA%E6%99%AF%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（1）个人空间是个人心理上所需要的最小的空间范围。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%BF%83%E7%90%86%E4%B8%8A%E6%89%80%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%80%E5%B0%8F%E7%9A%84%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E8%8C%83%E5%9B%B4%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="个人空间起着自我保护作用，是一个针对来自情绪和身体两方面潜在危险的缓冲圈，以避免过多的刺激，导致应激的过度唤醒、私密性不足或身体受到他人攻击。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E8%B5%B7%E7%9D%80%E8%87%AA%E6%88%91%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4%E4%BD%9C%E7%94%A8%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E9%92%88%E5%AF%B9%E6%9D%A5%E8%87%AA%E6%83%85%E7%BB%AA%E5%92%8C%E8%BA%AB%E4%BD%93%E4%B8%A4%E6%96%B9%E9%9D%A2%E6%BD%9C%E5%9C%A8%E5%8D%B1%E9%99%A9%E7%9A%84%E7%BC%93%E5%86%B2%E5%9C%88%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A5%E9%81%BF%E5%85%8D%E8%BF%87%E5%A4%9A%E7%9A%84%E5%88%BA%E6%BF%80%EF%BC%8C%E5%AF%BC%E8%87%B4%E5%BA%94%E6%BF%80%E7%9A%84%E8%BF%87%E5%BA%A6%E5%94%A4%E9%86%92%E3%80%81%E7%A7%81%E5%AF%86%E6%80%A7%E4%B8%8D%E8%B6%B3%E6%88%96%E8%BA%AB%E4%BD%93%E5%8F%97%E5%88%B0%E4%BB%96%E4%BA%BA%E6%94%BB%E5%87%BB%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="人际距离决定交往方式，人际距离可分为：密切距离（0~0.45m），个人距离（0.45~1.20m），社会距离（1.20~3.60m）和公共距离（3.60~7.60m）。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BA%BA%E9%99%85%E8%B7%9D%E7%A6%BB%E5%86%B3%E5%AE%9A%E4%BA%A4%E5%BE%80%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%EF%BC%8C%E4%BA%BA%E9%99%85%E8%B7%9D%E7%A6%BB%E5%8F%AF%E5%88%86%E4%B8%BA%EF%BC%9A%E5%AF%86%E5%88%87%E8%B7%9D%E7%A6%BB%EF%BC%880~0.45m%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E8%B7%9D%E7%A6%BB%EF%BC%880.45~1.20m%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%8C%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E8%B7%9D%E7%A6%BB%EF%BC%881.20~3.60m%EF%BC%89%E5%92%8C%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E8%B7%9D%E7%A6%BB%EF%BC%883.60~7.60m%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（2）私密性是指对生活方式和交往方式的选择与控制。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E7%A7%81%E5%AF%86%E6%80%A7%E6%98%AF%E6%8C%87%E5%AF%B9%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%E5%92%8C%E4%BA%A4%E5%BE%80%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%E7%9A%84%E9%80%89%E6%8B%A9%E4%B8%8E%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="需要物质环境从空间大小、边界的封闭与开放等方面，为人们的离合聚散提供不同层次和多种灵活机动条件的特性。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E7%89%A9%E8%B4%A8%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E4%BB%8E%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E5%A4%A7%E5%B0%8F%E3%80%81%E8%BE%B9%E7%95%8C%E7%9A%84%E5%B0%81%E9%97%AD%E4%B8%8E%E5%BC%80%E6%94%BE%E7%AD%89%E6%96%B9%E9%9D%A2%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%BA%E4%BA%BA%E4%BB%AC%E7%9A%84%E7%A6%BB%E5%90%88%E8%81%9A%E6%95%A3%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E5%B1%82%E6%AC%A1%E5%92%8C%E5%A4%9A%E7%A7%8D%E7%81%B5%E6%B4%BB%E6%9C%BA%E5%8A%A8%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%E7%9A%84%E7%89%B9%E6%80%A7%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（3）领域性是个人或群体为满足某种需要，拥有或占用一个场所或区域，并对其加以人格化和防卫的行为模式，是所有高等动物的天性。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E9%A2%86%E5%9F%9F%E6%80%A7%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E6%88%96%E7%BE%A4%E4%BD%93%E4%B8%BA%E6%BB%A1%E8%B6%B3%E6%9F%90%E7%A7%8D%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%EF%BC%8C%E6%8B%A5%E6%9C%89%E6%88%96%E5%8D%A0%E7%94%A8%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E5%9C%BA%E6%89%80%E6%88%96%E5%8C%BA%E5%9F%9F%EF%BC%8C%E5%B9%B6%E5%AF%B9%E5%85%B6%E5%8A%A0%E4%BB%A5%E4%BA%BA%E6%A0%BC%E5%8C%96%E5%92%8C%E9%98%B2%E5%8D%AB%E7%9A%84%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%BA%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%AF%E6%89%80%E6%9C%89%E9%AB%98%E7%AD%89%E5%8A%A8%E7%89%A9%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%A9%E6%80%A7%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="领域可分为主要领域、次要领域和公共领域三类。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%A2%86%E5%9F%9F%E5%8F%AF%E5%88%86%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E9%A2%86%E5%9F%9F%E3%80%81%E6%AC%A1%E8%A6%81%E9%A2%86%E5%9F%9F%E5%92%8C%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E9%A2%86%E5%9F%9F%E4%B8%89%E7%B1%BB%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="领域具有组织功能、私密性和控制感，并有安全防卫功能。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%A2%86%E5%9F%9F%E5%85%B7%E6%9C%89%E7%BB%84%E7%BB%87%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E3%80%81%E7%A7%81%E5%AF%86%E6%80%A7%E5%92%8C%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E6%84%9F%EF%BC%8C%E5%B9%B6%E6%9C%89%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E9%98%B2%E5%8D%AB%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（六）个人空间、私密性和领域性" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E5%85%AD%EF%BC%89%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E3%80%81%E7%A7%81%E5%AF%86%E6%80%A7%E5%92%8C%E9%A2%86%E5%9F%9F%E6%80%A7%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（七）城市外部公共空间活动研究" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%83%EF%BC%89%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%A4%96%E9%83%A8%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E6%B4%BB%E5%8A%A8%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="1.外部空间中的行为习性" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1.%E5%A4%96%E9%83%A8%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%BA%E4%B9%A0%E6%80%A7%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（1）动作性行为习性：抄近路、逆时针转向、依靠性等。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E5%8A%A8%E4%BD%9C%E6%80%A7%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%BA%E4%B9%A0%E6%80%A7%EF%BC%9A%E6%8A%84%E8%BF%91%E8%B7%AF%E3%80%81%E9%80%86%E6%97%B6%E9%92%88%E8%BD%AC%E5%90%91%E3%80%81%E4%BE%9D%E9%9D%A0%E6%80%A7%E7%AD%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（2）体验性行为习性：看人也为人所看、围观、安静与凝思等。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E4%BD%93%E9%AA%8C%E6%80%A7%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%BA%E4%B9%A0%E6%80%A7%EF%BC%9A%E7%9C%8B%E4%BA%BA%E4%B9%9F%E4%B8%BA%E4%BA%BA%E6%89%80%E7%9C%8B%E3%80%81%E5%9B%B4%E8%A7%82%E3%80%81%E5%AE%89%E9%9D%99%E4%B8%8E%E5%87%9D%E6%80%9D%E7%AD%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（3）认知性行为习性：靠右（左）侧通行、归巢性和兜圈子行为、探索性行为。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E8%AE%A4%E7%9F%A5%E6%80%A7%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%BA%E4%B9%A0%E6%80%A7%EF%BC%9A%E9%9D%A0%E5%8F%B3%EF%BC%88%E5%B7%A6%EF%BC%89%E4%BE%A7%E9%80%9A%E8%A1%8C%E3%80%81%E5%BD%92%E5%B7%A2%E6%80%A7%E5%92%8C%E5%85%9C%E5%9C%88%E5%AD%90%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%BA%E3%80%81%E6%8E%A2%E7%B4%A2%E6%80%A7%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%BA%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（4）行为习性的差异：情境、群体、文化和亚文化差异。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%884%EF%BC%89%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%BA%E4%B9%A0%E6%80%A7%E7%9A%84%E5%B7%AE%E5%BC%82%EF%BC%9A%E6%83%85%E5%A2%83%E3%80%81%E7%BE%A4%E4%BD%93%E3%80%81%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96%E5%92%8C%E4%BA%9A%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96%E5%B7%AE%E5%BC%82%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="2.基于行为的设计建议" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2.%E5%9F%BA%E4%BA%8E%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%BA%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%AE%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（1）寻求公共性和私密性的平衡。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E5%AF%BB%E6%B1%82%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E6%80%A7%E5%92%8C%E7%A7%81%E5%AF%86%E6%80%A7%E7%9A%84%E5%B9%B3%E8%A1%A1%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（2）注重外部空间的生态联系。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E6%B3%A8%E9%87%8D%E5%A4%96%E9%83%A8%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E7%9A%84%E7%94%9F%E6%80%81%E8%81%94%E7%B3%BB%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（3）合理满足人的行为习性。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E5%90%88%E7%90%86%E6%BB%A1%E8%B6%B3%E4%BA%BA%E7%9A%84%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%BA%E4%B9%A0%E6%80%A7%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（4）预防和减少不良破坏行为。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%884%EF%BC%89%E9%A2%84%E9%98%B2%E5%92%8C%E5%87%8F%E5%B0%91%E4%B8%8D%E8%89%AF%E7%A0%B4%E5%9D%8F%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%BA%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（八）城市环境的影响与讨论简述" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E5%85%AB%EF%BC%89%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%E4%B8%8E%E8%AE%A8%E8%AE%BA%E7%AE%80%E8%BF%B0%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="城市环境的积极影响多于消极影响，有关人员提出了一些理论与假设，包括超载假设、城市环境应激、行为约束和多场分析。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E7%9A%84%E7%A7%AF%E6%9E%81%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%E5%A4%9A%E4%BA%8E%E6%B6%88%E6%9E%81%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%EF%BC%8C%E6%9C%89%E5%85%B3%E4%BA%BA%E5%91%98%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E4%BA%86%E4%B8%80%E4%BA%9B%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA%E4%B8%8E%E5%81%87%E8%AE%BE%EF%BC%8C%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E8%B6%85%E8%BD%BD%E5%81%87%E8%AE%BE%E3%80%81%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%BA%94%E6%BF%80%E3%80%81%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%BA%E7%BA%A6%E6%9D%9F%E5%92%8C%E5%A4%9A%E5%9C%BA%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="而城市的实际问题包括城市区域的安全防卫、社会网络、场所依恋和城市更新。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%80%8C%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%9E%E9%99%85%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%8C%BA%E5%9F%9F%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E9%98%B2%E5%8D%AB%E3%80%81%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E3%80%81%E5%9C%BA%E6%89%80%E4%BE%9D%E6%81%8B%E5%92%8C%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="1.城市区域安全防卫" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1.%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%8C%BA%E5%9F%9F%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E9%98%B2%E5%8D%AB%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="20世纪60年代，美国建筑师简·雅各布斯（Jane Jacobs）在《美国大城市的死与生》一书中把城市规划与安全防卫联系起来，认为维护安全是城市居住区和街道的基本功能之一。美国建筑师奥斯卡纽曼（Oscar Newman）提出了“能防卫的空间”的概念并著有《可防御空间》一书。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E20%E4%B8%96%E7%BA%AA60%E5%B9%B4%E4%BB%A3%EF%BC%8C%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%88%E7%AE%80%C2%B7%E9%9B%85%E5%90%84%E5%B8%83%E6%96%AF%EF%BC%88Jane%20Jacobs%EF%BC%89%E5%9C%A8%E3%80%8A%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E5%A4%A7%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%9A%84%E6%AD%BB%E4%B8%8E%E7%94%9F%E3%80%8B%E4%B8%80%E4%B9%A6%E4%B8%AD%E6%8A%8A%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E4%B8%8E%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E9%98%B2%E5%8D%AB%E8%81%94%E7%B3%BB%E8%B5%B7%E6%9D%A5%EF%BC%8C%E8%AE%A4%E4%B8%BA%E7%BB%B4%E6%8A%A4%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E6%98%AF%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E5%8C%BA%E5%92%8C%E8%A1%97%E9%81%93%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E4%B9%8B%E4%B8%80%E3%80%82%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%88%E5%A5%A5%E6%96%AF%E5%8D%A1%E7%BA%BD%E6%9B%BC%EF%BC%88Oscar%20Newman%EF%BC%89%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E4%BA%86%E2%80%9C%E8%83%BD%E9%98%B2%E5%8D%AB%E7%9A%84%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E2%80%9D%E7%9A%84%E6%A6%82%E5%BF%B5%E5%B9%B6%E8%91%97%E6%9C%89%E3%80%8A%E5%8F%AF%E9%98%B2%E5%BE%A1%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E3%80%8B%E4%B8%80%E4%B9%A6%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="城市区域安全防卫的四项原则：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%8C%BA%E5%9F%9F%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E9%98%B2%E5%8D%AB%E7%9A%84%E5%9B%9B%E9%A1%B9%E5%8E%9F%E5%88%99%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（1）形成易于被感知并有助于防卫的领域。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E5%BD%A2%E6%88%90%E6%98%93%E4%BA%8E%E8%A2%AB%E6%84%9F%E7%9F%A5%E5%B9%B6%E6%9C%89%E5%8A%A9%E4%BA%8E%E9%98%B2%E5%8D%AB%E7%9A%84%E9%A2%86%E5%9F%9F%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（2）自然的监视。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6%E7%9A%84%E7%9B%91%E8%A7%86%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（3）形成有利于安全防卫的建筑意象。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E5%BD%A2%E6%88%90%E6%9C%89%E5%88%A9%E4%BA%8E%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E9%98%B2%E5%8D%AB%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E6%84%8F%E8%B1%A1%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（4）改善居住区的社会环境。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%884%EF%BC%89%E6%94%B9%E5%96%84%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E5%8C%BA%E7%9A%84%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="国内对城市更新（又称旧城改造或再开发）有两种意见，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9B%BD%E5%86%85%E5%AF%B9%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0%EF%BC%88%E5%8F%88%E7%A7%B0%E6%97%A7%E5%9F%8E%E6%94%B9%E9%80%A0%E6%88%96%E5%86%8D%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%EF%BC%89%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%A4%E7%A7%8D%E6%84%8F%E8%A7%81%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="一种是拆除旧城建筑再重建；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%80%E7%A7%8D%E6%98%AF%E6%8B%86%E9%99%A4%E6%97%A7%E5%9F%8E%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%86%8D%E9%87%8D%E5%BB%BA%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="另一种是迁走工厂，在郊区进行“再工业化”；或舍弃原有中心，然后择地进行“再中心化”等。最终演变成大规模的“造城运动”。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%8F%A6%E4%B8%80%E7%A7%8D%E6%98%AF%E8%BF%81%E8%B5%B0%E5%B7%A5%E5%8E%82%EF%BC%8C%E5%9C%A8%E9%83%8A%E5%8C%BA%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E2%80%9C%E5%86%8D%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%9A%E5%8C%96%E2%80%9D%EF%BC%9B%E6%88%96%E8%88%8D%E5%BC%83%E5%8E%9F%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%EF%BC%8C%E7%84%B6%E5%90%8E%E6%8B%A9%E5%9C%B0%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E2%80%9C%E5%86%8D%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%E5%8C%96%E2%80%9D%E7%AD%89%E3%80%82%E6%9C%80%E7%BB%88%E6%BC%94%E5%8F%98%E6%88%90%E5%A4%A7%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%E7%9A%84%E2%80%9C%E9%80%A0%E5%9F%8E%E8%BF%90%E5%8A%A8%E2%80%9D%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="从全局看，城市更新是用来解决城市问题的有效手段，但对被迫搬迁的居民来说，付出的代价往往太大。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BB%8E%E5%85%A8%E5%B1%80%E7%9C%8B%EF%BC%8C%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0%E6%98%AF%E7%94%A8%E6%9D%A5%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%89%E6%95%88%E6%89%8B%E6%AE%B5%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%86%E5%AF%B9%E8%A2%AB%E8%BF%AB%E6%90%AC%E8%BF%81%E7%9A%84%E5%B1%85%E6%B0%91%E6%9D%A5%E8%AF%B4%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%98%E5%87%BA%E7%9A%84%E4%BB%A3%E4%BB%B7%E5%BE%80%E5%BE%80%E5%A4%AA%E5%A4%A7%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="2.城市更新与造城运动" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2.%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0%E4%B8%8E%E9%80%A0%E5%9F%8E%E8%BF%90%E5%8A%A8%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="城市更新可定义为“为了在环境、经济、社会三个方面维护和改善城市区域，并使之达到正常状态，而对环境所作的大量实际改变”。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0%E5%8F%AF%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%E4%B8%BA%E2%80%9C%E4%B8%BA%E4%BA%86%E5%9C%A8%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E3%80%81%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E3%80%81%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E4%B8%89%E4%B8%AA%E6%96%B9%E9%9D%A2%E7%BB%B4%E6%8A%A4%E5%92%8C%E6%94%B9%E5%96%84%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%8C%BA%E5%9F%9F%EF%BC%8C%E5%B9%B6%E4%BD%BF%E4%B9%8B%E8%BE%BE%E5%88%B0%E6%AD%A3%E5%B8%B8%E7%8A%B6%E6%80%81%EF%BC%8C%E8%80%8C%E5%AF%B9%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E6%89%80%E4%BD%9C%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%A7%E9%87%8F%E5%AE%9E%E9%99%85%E6%94%B9%E5%8F%98%E2%80%9D%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="由美国建筑师雅马萨奇（又译作山崎实，M.Yamasaki）设计并在1954年建成的圣路易斯市的普鲁伊特-艾格（Pruitt-lgoe）住宅区是这方面的典型，住宅区于1970年被拆除，拆除的原因成为多学科探讨的课题。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%94%B1%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%88%E9%9B%85%E9%A9%AC%E8%90%A8%E5%A5%87%EF%BC%88%E5%8F%88%E8%AF%91%E4%BD%9C%E5%B1%B1%E5%B4%8E%E5%AE%9E%EF%BC%8CM.Yamasaki%EF%BC%89%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%B9%B6%E5%9C%A81954%E5%B9%B4%E5%BB%BA%E6%88%90%E7%9A%84%E5%9C%A3%E8%B7%AF%E6%98%93%E6%96%AF%E5%B8%82%E7%9A%84%E6%99%AE%E9%B2%81%E4%BC%8A%E7%89%B9-%E8%89%BE%E6%A0%BC%EF%BC%88Pruitt-lgoe%EF%BC%89%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%85%E5%8C%BA%E6%98%AF%E8%BF%99%E6%96%B9%E9%9D%A2%E7%9A%84%E5%85%B8%E5%9E%8B%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%85%E5%8C%BA%E4%BA%8E1970%E5%B9%B4%E8%A2%AB%E6%8B%86%E9%99%A4%EF%BC%8C%E6%8B%86%E9%99%A4%E7%9A%84%E5%8E%9F%E5%9B%A0%E6%88%90%E4%B8%BA%E5%A4%9A%E5%AD%A6%E7%A7%91%E6%8E%A2%E8%AE%A8%E7%9A%84%E8%AF%BE%E9%A2%98%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（九）建筑环境与行为" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%B9%9D%EF%BC%89%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E4%B8%8E%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%BA%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="20世纪80年代，环境心理学在建筑学中的应用，又称为“环境一行为研究”。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E20%E4%B8%96%E7%BA%AA80%E5%B9%B4%E4%BB%A3%EF%BC%8C%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%BF%83%E7%90%86%E5%AD%A6%E5%9C%A8%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%AD%A6%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%88%E7%A7%B0%E4%B8%BA%E2%80%9C%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E4%B8%80%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%BA%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E2%80%9D%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="从建筑设计原理的角度来看，环境一行为研究是“适用”的现代术语。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BB%8E%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%8E%9F%E7%90%86%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%92%E5%BA%A6%E6%9D%A5%E7%9C%8B%EF%BC%8C%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E4%B8%80%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%BA%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E6%98%AF%E2%80%9C%E9%80%82%E7%94%A8%E2%80%9D%E7%9A%84%E7%8E%B0%E4%BB%A3%E6%9C%AF%E8%AF%AD%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="这种以使用者为出发点的建筑审美研究——“体验美学”或称“符号美学”，是对传统的建筑“形式美学”的重要补充。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%BF%99%E7%A7%8D%E4%BB%A5%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E8%80%85%E4%B8%BA%E5%87%BA%E5%8F%91%E7%82%B9%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%AE%A1%E7%BE%8E%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E2%80%9C%E4%BD%93%E9%AA%8C%E7%BE%8E%E5%AD%A6%E2%80%9D%E6%88%96%E7%A7%B0%E2%80%9C%E7%AC%A6%E5%8F%B7%E7%BE%8E%E5%AD%A6%E2%80%9D%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%AF%E5%AF%B9%E4%BC%A0%E7%BB%9F%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E2%80%9C%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E7%BE%8E%E5%AD%A6%E2%80%9D%E7%9A%84%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81%E8%A1%A5%E5%85%85%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="1.基于行为的建筑设计过程" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1.%E5%9F%BA%E4%BA%8E%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%BA%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E8%BF%87%E7%A8%8B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="环境心理学家提出过许多改进的建筑设计过程，其中以蔡塞尔（J.Ziesel）归纳出的“设计循环模型”为代表。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%BF%83%E7%90%86%E5%AD%A6%E5%AE%B6%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E8%BF%87%E8%AE%B8%E5%A4%9A%E6%94%B9%E8%BF%9B%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E8%BF%87%E7%A8%8B%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%B6%E4%B8%AD%E4%BB%A5%E8%94%A1%E5%A1%9E%E5%B0%94%EF%BC%88J.Ziesel%EF%BC%89%E5%BD%92%E7%BA%B3%E5%87%BA%E7%9A%84%E2%80%9C%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%BE%AA%E7%8E%AF%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B%E2%80%9D%E4%B8%BA%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="它特别强调三点：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%AE%83%E7%89%B9%E5%88%AB%E5%BC%BA%E8%B0%83%E4%B8%89%E7%82%B9%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（1）初步设计阶段，着重收集包括环境一行为信息在内的设计资料，并制定相应的设计标准。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E5%88%9D%E6%AD%A5%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E9%98%B6%E6%AE%B5%EF%BC%8C%E7%9D%80%E9%87%8D%E6%94%B6%E9%9B%86%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E4%B8%80%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%BA%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E5%9C%A8%E5%86%85%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E8%B5%84%E6%96%99%EF%BC%8C%E5%B9%B6%E5%88%B6%E5%AE%9A%E7%9B%B8%E5%BA%94%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E6%A0%87%E5%87%86%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（2）在工程竣工并使用一段时间后进行使用后的评价（POE），并将评价结果“诊断资料”反馈应用于下一个设计项目。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E5%9C%A8%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E7%AB%A3%E5%B7%A5%E5%B9%B6%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E4%B8%80%E6%AE%B5%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%E5%90%8E%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E5%90%8E%E7%9A%84%E8%AF%84%E4%BB%B7%EF%BC%88POE%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%8C%E5%B9%B6%E5%B0%86%E8%AF%84%E4%BB%B7%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%9C%E2%80%9C%E8%AF%8A%E6%96%AD%E8%B5%84%E6%96%99%E2%80%9D%E5%8F%8D%E9%A6%88%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%E4%BA%8E%E4%B8%8B%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（3）持续实施“假设一实施一验证一反馈”这一循环模式，形成系统的设计资料。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E6%8C%81%E7%BB%AD%E5%AE%9E%E6%96%BD%E2%80%9C%E5%81%87%E8%AE%BE%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%9E%E6%96%BD%E4%B8%80%E9%AA%8C%E8%AF%81%E4%B8%80%E5%8F%8D%E9%A6%88%E2%80%9D%E8%BF%99%E4%B8%80%E5%BE%AA%E7%8E%AF%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F%EF%BC%8C%E5%BD%A2%E6%88%90%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E8%B5%84%E6%96%99%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="注：使用后的评价参见本书第一章“建筑策划”部分。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%B3%A8%EF%BC%9A%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E5%90%8E%E7%9A%84%E8%AF%84%E4%BB%B7%E5%8F%82%E8%A7%81%E6%9C%AC%E4%B9%A6%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E7%AB%A0%E2%80%9C%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%AD%96%E5%88%92%E2%80%9D%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="2.建筑体验研究" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2.%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E4%BD%93%E9%AA%8C%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（1）知觉理论与建筑体验，在知觉理论中，对建筑体验影响较大的主要有视错觉" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E7%9F%A5%E8%A7%89%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA%E4%B8%8E%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E4%BD%93%E9%AA%8C%EF%BC%8C%E5%9C%A8%E7%9F%A5%E8%A7%89%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA%E4%B8%AD%EF%BC%8C%E5%AF%B9%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E4%BD%93%E9%AA%8C%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%E8%BE%83%E5%A4%A7%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E6%9C%89%E8%A7%86%E9%94%99%E8%A7%89%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="[线段的横竖错觉、缪勒-莱耶错觉（Muler Lyer Illusion）、德勃夫错觉（Dolboef Illusion）、赫氏方格等]，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%5B%E7%BA%BF%E6%AE%B5%E7%9A%84%E6%A8%AA%E7%AB%96%E9%94%99%E8%A7%89%E3%80%81%E7%BC%AA%E5%8B%92-%E8%8E%B1%E8%80%B6%E9%94%99%E8%A7%89%EF%BC%88Muler%20Lyer%20Illusion%EF%BC%89%E3%80%81%E5%BE%B7%E5%8B%83%E5%A4%AB%E9%94%99%E8%A7%89%EF%BC%88Dolboef%20Illusion%EF%BC%89%E3%80%81%E8%B5%AB%E6%B0%8F%E6%96%B9%E6%A0%BC%E7%AD%89%5D%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="格式塔的视觉组织规律和生态知觉理论。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%A0%BC%E5%BC%8F%E5%A1%94%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%86%E8%A7%89%E7%BB%84%E7%BB%87%E8%A7%84%E5%BE%8B%E5%92%8C%E7%94%9F%E6%80%81%E7%9F%A5%E8%A7%89%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="古希腊哲学家亚里士多德说过：“人们来到城市，是为了生活；人们留在城市，是为了更好的生活”。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%8F%A4%E5%B8%8C%E8%85%8A%E5%93%B2%E5%AD%A6%E5%AE%B6%E4%BA%9A%E9%87%8C%E5%A3%AB%E5%A4%9A%E5%BE%B7%E8%AF%B4%E8%BF%87%EF%BC%9A%E2%80%9C%E4%BA%BA%E4%BB%AC%E6%9D%A5%E5%88%B0%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%BA%E4%BA%86%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%EF%BC%9B%E4%BA%BA%E4%BB%AC%E7%95%99%E5%9C%A8%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%BA%E4%BA%86%E6%9B%B4%E5%A5%BD%E7%9A%84%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E2%80%9D%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（2）建筑体验的研究方法有：多项分类、SD法、问卷、实验室实验、历史资料调查等。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E4%BD%93%E9%AA%8C%E7%9A%84%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%89%EF%BC%9A%E5%A4%9A%E9%A1%B9%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB%E3%80%81SD%E6%B3%95%E3%80%81%E9%97%AE%E5%8D%B7%E3%80%81%E5%AE%9E%E9%AA%8C%E5%AE%A4%E5%AE%9E%E9%AA%8C%E3%80%81%E5%8E%86%E5%8F%B2%E8%B5%84%E6%96%99%E8%B0%83%E6%9F%A5%E7%AD%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（3）影响建筑体验的因素很多，如自然景观、建筑的历史、建筑之间的“协调感”等。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E4%BD%93%E9%AA%8C%E7%9A%84%E5%9B%A0%E7%B4%A0%E5%BE%88%E5%A4%9A%EF%BC%8C%E5%A6%82%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6%E6%99%AF%E8%A7%82%E3%80%81%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%9A%84%E5%8E%86%E5%8F%B2%E3%80%81%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E4%B9%8B%E9%97%B4%E7%9A%84%E2%80%9C%E5%8D%8F%E8%B0%83%E6%84%9F%E2%80%9D%E7%AD%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（4）室内空间的体验" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%884%EF%BC%89%E5%AE%A4%E5%86%85%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%93%E9%AA%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="1）空间的宽敞感" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1%EF%BC%89%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%BD%E6%95%9E%E6%84%9F%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="经验证明，行为特点对宽敞感的影响也不容忽视。宽敞感与人体尺度、动作、潜在的行为习性有关。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%BB%8F%E9%AA%8C%E8%AF%81%E6%98%8E%EF%BC%8C%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%BA%E7%89%B9%E7%82%B9%E5%AF%B9%E5%AE%BD%E6%95%9E%E6%84%9F%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%E4%B9%9F%E4%B8%8D%E5%AE%B9%E5%BF%BD%E8%A7%86%E3%80%82%E5%AE%BD%E6%95%9E%E6%84%9F%E4%B8%8E%E4%BA%BA%E4%BD%93%E5%B0%BA%E5%BA%A6%E3%80%81%E5%8A%A8%E4%BD%9C%E3%80%81%E6%BD%9C%E5%9C%A8%E7%9A%84%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%BA%E4%B9%A0%E6%80%A7%E6%9C%89%E5%85%B3%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="界面的特点对空间的围合感也具有重要影响。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%95%8C%E9%9D%A2%E7%9A%84%E7%89%B9%E7%82%B9%E5%AF%B9%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E7%9A%84%E5%9B%B4%E5%90%88%E6%84%9F%E4%B9%9F%E5%85%B7%E6%9C%89%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="建筑师还必须注意社会和文化因素对建筑体验的影响：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%88%E8%BF%98%E5%BF%85%E9%A1%BB%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E5%92%8C%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96%E5%9B%A0%E7%B4%A0%E5%AF%B9%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E4%BD%93%E9%AA%8C%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="2）空间的围合感" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2%EF%BC%89%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E7%9A%84%E5%9B%B4%E5%90%88%E6%84%9F%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="对象高度与观察距离之比，与围合感之间存在一定的经验关系：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%AF%B9%E8%B1%A1%E9%AB%98%E5%BA%A6%E4%B8%8E%E8%A7%82%E5%AF%9F%E8%B7%9D%E7%A6%BB%E4%B9%8B%E6%AF%94%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8E%E5%9B%B4%E5%90%88%E6%84%9F%E4%B9%8B%E9%97%B4%E5%AD%98%E5%9C%A8%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%9A%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%8F%E9%AA%8C%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="比例为1：1时，产生完全的围合感；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%AF%94%E4%BE%8B%E4%B8%BA1%EF%BC%9A1%E6%97%B6%EF%BC%8C%E4%BA%A7%E7%94%9F%E5%AE%8C%E5%85%A8%E7%9A%84%E5%9B%B4%E5%90%88%E6%84%9F%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="比例为1：2时，是围合感的临界值；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%AF%94%E4%BE%8B%E4%B8%BA1%EF%BC%9A2%E6%97%B6%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%AF%E5%9B%B4%E5%90%88%E6%84%9F%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%B4%E7%95%8C%E5%80%BC%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="比例为1：3时，具有最低程度的围合感；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%AF%94%E4%BE%8B%E4%B8%BA1%EF%BC%9A3%E6%97%B6%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%B7%E6%9C%89%E6%9C%80%E4%BD%8E%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%A6%E7%9A%84%E5%9B%B4%E5%90%88%E6%84%9F%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="比例为1：4时，失去围合感。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%AF%94%E4%BE%8B%E4%B8%BA1%EF%BC%9A4%E6%97%B6%EF%BC%8C%E5%A4%B1%E5%8E%BB%E5%9B%B4%E5%90%88%E6%84%9F%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="3）减少拥挤感的对策" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E3%EF%BC%89%E5%87%8F%E5%B0%91%E6%8B%A5%E6%8C%A4%E6%84%9F%E7%9A%84%E5%AF%B9%E7%AD%96%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="适当进行分隔，减少人们的互相接触，并降低环境信息的输入水平；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%80%82%E5%BD%93%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E5%88%86%E9%9A%94%EF%BC%8C%E5%87%8F%E5%B0%91%E4%BA%BA%E4%BB%AC%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%92%E7%9B%B8%E6%8E%A5%E8%A7%A6%EF%BC%8C%E5%B9%B6%E9%99%8D%E4%BD%8E%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E7%9A%84%E8%BE%93%E5%85%A5%E6%B0%B4%E5%B9%B3%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="减少刺激超载，人眼的边缘视觉会夸大眼角以外的运动，这种夸大的运动感会造成刺激超载，并可能进而引起拥挤感；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%87%8F%E5%B0%91%E5%88%BA%E6%BF%80%E8%B6%85%E8%BD%BD%EF%BC%8C%E4%BA%BA%E7%9C%BC%E7%9A%84%E8%BE%B9%E7%BC%98%E8%A7%86%E8%A7%89%E4%BC%9A%E5%A4%B8%E5%A4%A7%E7%9C%BC%E8%A7%92%E4%BB%A5%E5%A4%96%E7%9A%84%E8%BF%90%E5%8A%A8%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%99%E7%A7%8D%E5%A4%B8%E5%A4%A7%E7%9A%84%E8%BF%90%E5%8A%A8%E6%84%9F%E4%BC%9A%E9%80%A0%E6%88%90%E5%88%BA%E6%BF%80%E8%B6%85%E8%BD%BD%EF%BC%8C%E5%B9%B6%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E8%BF%9B%E8%80%8C%E5%BC%95%E8%B5%B7%E6%8B%A5%E6%8C%A4%E6%84%9F%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="减少相互间的眼睛接触也能减少刺激超载；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%87%8F%E5%B0%91%E7%9B%B8%E4%BA%92%E9%97%B4%E7%9A%84%E7%9C%BC%E7%9D%9B%E6%8E%A5%E8%A7%A6%E4%B9%9F%E8%83%BD%E5%87%8F%E5%B0%91%E5%88%BA%E6%BF%80%E8%B6%85%E8%BD%BD%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="对于同一量度的室内空间，不同地域的不同人群会有完全不同的空间开敞感。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%AF%B9%E4%BA%8E%E5%90%8C%E4%B8%80%E9%87%8F%E5%BA%A6%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%A4%E5%86%85%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E5%9C%B0%E5%9F%9F%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E4%BA%BA%E7%BE%A4%E4%BC%9A%E6%9C%89%E5%AE%8C%E5%85%A8%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E7%9A%84%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E5%BC%80%E6%95%9E%E6%84%9F%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="3.建筑认知概述" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E3.%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%AE%A4%E7%9F%A5%E6%A6%82%E8%BF%B0%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（1）建筑意象" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E6%84%8F%E8%B1%A1%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="建筑作为城市的重要标志物，自然会引起特别的关注，研究结果表明，人们首先记住建筑的使用特点及其意义，其次才是可见性和形式特点。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%BA%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%9A%84%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81%E6%A0%87%E5%BF%97%E7%89%A9%EF%BC%8C%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6%E4%BC%9A%E5%BC%95%E8%B5%B7%E7%89%B9%E5%88%AB%E7%9A%84%E5%85%B3%E6%B3%A8%EF%BC%8C%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%9C%E8%A1%A8%E6%98%8E%EF%BC%8C%E4%BA%BA%E4%BB%AC%E9%A6%96%E5%85%88%E8%AE%B0%E4%BD%8F%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E7%89%B9%E7%82%B9%E5%8F%8A%E5%85%B6%E6%84%8F%E4%B9%89%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%B6%E6%AC%A1%E6%89%8D%E6%98%AF%E5%8F%AF%E8%A7%81%E6%80%A7%E5%92%8C%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E7%89%B9%E7%82%B9%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（2）使用者的建筑综合意向" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E8%80%85%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%BB%BC%E5%90%88%E6%84%8F%E5%90%91%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="在日常生活中，人们对“需要什么样的建筑”所表达的意图称之为“建筑综合意向”，区别于记忆中的建筑形象。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9C%A8%E6%97%A5%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E4%B8%AD%EF%BC%8C%E4%BA%BA%E4%BB%AC%E5%AF%B9%E2%80%9C%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E6%A0%B7%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E2%80%9D%E6%89%80%E8%A1%A8%E8%BE%BE%E7%9A%84%E6%84%8F%E5%9B%BE%E7%A7%B0%E4%B9%8B%E4%B8%BA%E2%80%9C%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%BB%BC%E5%90%88%E6%84%8F%E5%90%91%E2%80%9D%EF%BC%8C%E5%8C%BA%E5%88%AB%E4%BA%8E%E8%AE%B0%E5%BF%86%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%BD%A2%E8%B1%A1%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（3）室内的认知距离" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E5%AE%A4%E5%86%85%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%A4%E7%9F%A5%E8%B7%9D%E7%A6%BB%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="人们认为距离相等的坡路路程比平坦路程更长，此外在不同场所中还存在烦恼距离。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BA%BA%E4%BB%AC%E8%AE%A4%E4%B8%BA%E8%B7%9D%E7%A6%BB%E7%9B%B8%E7%AD%89%E7%9A%84%E5%9D%A1%E8%B7%AF%E8%B7%AF%E7%A8%8B%E6%AF%94%E5%B9%B3%E5%9D%A6%E8%B7%AF%E7%A8%8B%E6%9B%B4%E9%95%BF%EF%BC%8C%E6%AD%A4%E5%A4%96%E5%9C%A8%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E5%9C%BA%E6%89%80%E4%B8%AD%E8%BF%98%E5%AD%98%E5%9C%A8%E7%83%A6%E6%81%BC%E8%B7%9D%E7%A6%BB%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（4）室内空间定向" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%884%EF%BC%89%E5%AE%A4%E5%86%85%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E5%AE%9A%E5%90%91%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="包括建筑的识别性、引导标志、建筑平面拓扑复杂性等。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%9A%84%E8%AF%86%E5%88%AB%E6%80%A7%E3%80%81%E5%BC%95%E5%AF%BC%E6%A0%87%E5%BF%97%E3%80%81%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B9%B3%E9%9D%A2%E6%8B%93%E6%89%91%E5%A4%8D%E6%9D%82%E6%80%A7%E7%AD%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="减少对行为的限制，使人的行为具有多种自由度，可能减少拥挤感带来的消极影响。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%87%8F%E5%B0%91%E5%AF%B9%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%BA%E7%9A%84%E9%99%90%E5%88%B6%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%BF%E4%BA%BA%E7%9A%84%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%BA%E5%85%B7%E6%9C%89%E5%A4%9A%E7%A7%8D%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E5%BA%A6%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E5%87%8F%E5%B0%91%E6%8B%A5%E6%8C%A4%E6%84%9F%E5%B8%A6%E6%9D%A5%E7%9A%84%E6%B6%88%E6%9E%81%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="" _mubu_text="" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="" _mubu_text="" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="" _mubu_text="" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
  </body>
